R Potion +5<br>MP +200<br>Applies 25% MPR in<br>heavy conditions</p>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                     <p align=\"center\"><font color=\"#ed1c24\">MP Recovery +5<br>MPR Potion +5<br>MP +200<br>Applies 25% MPR in<br>heavy conditions</font></p>\r\n                     <div><font color=\"#ed1c24\"><br></font></div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n            </tbody>\r\n         </table>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>', '/upload/2021\\09\\13/002_15.jpg', 'false', 'false');
