(4, 'World Siege', '<p style=\"color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif;\"><font style=\"font-size: 20px !important;\">There are six servers and one castle. Who will be the Holy Blood?</font></p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif;\"><br></p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif;\">Server-wide sieges between up to 6 servers for 1 castle.</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif;\">The World Siege begins&nbsp;at 20:00 on Sundays and lasts for one hour, and the clan that takes possession of the castle is rewarded with taxes collected in the area.</p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif;\"><br></p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif;\"><br></p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif;\"><br></p>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <h2>Feature</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif;\">\r\n   <p>-&nbsp;Normal Sieges (in-server sieges) and&nbsp;World Sieges alternate each week</p>\r\n   <p>-&nbsp;6 servers are randomly matched, and 4 servers are matched separately for specialized servers.</p>\r\n   <p>- The Deathknight, Valakas, and Pandora servers will only have regular sieges each&nbsp;week (World Siege will be updated at a later date)</p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n      <h2>Flow</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>The flow of world siege is as follow..</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n         <tbody>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td class=\"box1 width600\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p><br></p>\r\n                  <p>0. Ownership of the castle is transferred to NPCs before&nbsp;the siege begins.</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">&darr;<br></p>\r\n                  <p>1. From 19:30, use the&nbsp;Unknown Rift Portal to move to the siege&nbsp;area.</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">&darr;<br></p>\r\n                  <p>2. Pay Adena in the Siege Zone to buy World Siege exclusive consumables.</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">&darr;<br></p>\r\n                  <p>3. The siege begins at 20:00.</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">&darr;</p>\r\n                  <p>4. Defeat the boss monsters around the siege tower and gain ownership of the castle.</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">&darr;</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"left\">5. After that, you can defeat the Guardian Tower and take ownership of the castle.</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">&darr;</p>\r\n                  <p>6. The siege ends at 21:00.</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">&darr;</p>\r\n                  <p>7. Siege area available until 21:30.</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">&darr;</p>\r\n                  <p>8. At 21:30, as the siege zone closes, the character teleports to the mainland.<br></p>\r\n                  <p><br></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p>- The area around the castle has been renamed the Sigde&nbsp;Zone.</p>\r\n      <p>-&nbsp;Own server character, another server character, and three kinds of server marks of the Holy Blood character are displayed.</p>\r\n      <p>- All characters of the attacking and defending clans are marked with a clan crest.</p>\r\n      <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\"><br></span></p>\r\n      <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Differences from normal&nbsp;siege warfare</span><br></p>\r\n      <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">-</span>&nbsp;Before the siege begins, a boss monster will appear in the castle, and the clan that defeats it will take possession of the castle for the first time.</p>\r\n      <p>-&nbsp;You can only&nbsp;enter the castle where the World Siege takes place during the siege period (19:30~21:30).</p>\r\n      <p>-&nbsp;The castle where the World Siege takes place does not have any functional NPCs.</p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"14348-3\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n         <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n            <h2>Declare a Siege</h2>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n            <p>The Lord of the Darkness who wants to attack the castle&nbsp;&nbsp;\'<font color=\"#ed1c24\">/declare last name</font>\'&nbsp;When you enter a command,&nbsp;Declare a siege. If an alliance is formed, only the lord of the clan who is the subject of the alliance can declare a siege.</p>\r\n            <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n            <p>-&nbsp;Even if the monarch is in a transformerized state, a siege can be declared.</p>\r\n            <p>- Clans that have houses can also declare a siege.</p>\r\n            <p>- When a siege is declared, members of the clan will automatically teleport to the village.</p>\r\n            <p>- No full message when declaring a siege.</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"14348-4\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n         <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n            <h2>Win/Loss Conditions</h2>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n            <p>At&nbsp;the end of the siege, the clan that owns&nbsp;the castle will own the castle.</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>', '/upload/2021\\09\\13/002_13.jpg', 'false', 'false'),
(5, 'Lancer', '<p lucid=\"\" Gothic\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" jhenghei\",=\"\" meiryo,=\"\" \"ms=\"\" pgothic\",=\"\" arial,=\"\" dotum,=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: \"lucid Gothic\", \"Malgun Gothic\", AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, \"Noto Sans CJK KR\", Dotum, arial, \"Microsoft NeoGothic\", \"Droid sans\", sans-serif;\">Lancer is all rounded class that uses spear as it\'s main weapon covering both melee and range mode.<br>Anyone can easily operate with a variety of passive skills, and strategic fun can be maximized with powerful active skills with individual cooldowns.</p><p lucid=\"\" Gothic\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" jhenghei\",=\"\" meiryo,=\"\" \"ms=\"\" pgothic\",=\"\" arial,=\"\" dotum,=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: \"lucid Gothic\", \"Malgun Gothic\", AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, \"Noto Sans CJK KR\", Dotum, arial, \"Microsoft NeoGothic\", \"Droid sans\", sans-serif;\"><br></p><p lucid=\"\" Gothic\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" jhenghei\",=\"\" meiryo,=\"\" \"ms=\"\" pgothic\",=\"\" arial,=\"\" dotum,=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: \"lucid Gothic\", \"Malgun Gothic\", AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, \"Noto Sans CJK KR\", Dotum, arial, \"Microsoft NeoGothic\", \"Droid sans\", sans-serif;\"><br></p><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15234-1\" lucid=\"\" Gothic\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" jhenghei\",=\"\" meiryo,=\"\" \"ms=\"\" pgothic\",=\"\" arial,=\"\" dotum,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\" style=\"font-family: \"lucid Gothic\", \"Malgun Gothic\", AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, \"Noto Sans CJK KR\", Dotum, arial, \"Microsoft NeoGothic\", \"Droid sans\", sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n   <h2>Feature</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n   <p>&rarr; A fighter with Knight like HP with excellent melee abilities and mid-range attacks.<br>&rarr; In melee mode, you can attack enemies within 2 cells.<br>&rarr; In range mode, you can attack enemies between 5 - 8 cells.<br>&rarr; When attacking from a distance, it has the effect of reducing attack speed and damage reduction based on the distance from the target.<br>&rarr; Ranged damage is affected by weapon damage, and is not affected by DEX stats, equipment\'s ranged hits, or ranged damage.<br>&rarr; Spear is the primary weapon, and most armor/trinkets are shared with the Knight/Fencer.<br>&rarr; Potion of Valor can be used to increase the speed to 2nd speed.<br>&rarr; The Lancer skill is affected by the caster\'s fear hit and the target\'s fear resistance.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15234-2\" lucid=\"\" Gothic\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" jhenghei\",=\"\" meiryo,=\"\" \"ms=\"\" pgothic\",=\"\" arial,=\"\" dotum,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\" style=\"font-family: \"lucid Gothic\", \"Malgun Gothic\", AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, \"Noto Sans CJK KR\", Dotum, arial, \"Microsoft NeoGothic\", \"Droid sans\", sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n   <h2>Attack Mode</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n   <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; clear: both;\">\r\n      <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n         <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/22/63/8d74cb5ce5e4c9bac4898e3f.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n         <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">Melee Mode</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n         <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/22/63/aa2709fbe4da77549076ba32.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n         <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">Range Mode</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <p>The Lancer class can switch between two forms, melee and ranged forms.<br>For some skills, the effect is different depending on the melee/ranged form.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15234-3\" lucid=\"\" Gothic\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" jhenghei\",=\"\" meiryo,=\"\" \"ms=\"\" pgothic\",=\"\" arial,=\"\" dotum,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\" style=\"font-family: \"lucid Gothic\", \"Malgun Gothic\", AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, \"Noto Sans CJK KR\", Dotum, arial, \"Microsoft NeoGothic\", \"Droid sans\", sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n   <h2>Equipment</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n   <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; clear: both;\">\r\n      <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n         <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/99/76/7f982f5957d6349bc75915aa.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n         <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">There are skills which requires equipping a spear.</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n         <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/99/76/eda1c681448deb3d88162bb3.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n         <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">There is also a window for the lancer.</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <p>One of the most noteworthy pieces of lancer equipment is a skill that can only be used while equipping a spear.</p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Weapon</span><br>- Can wield both two handed spear and one handed spear.</p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Armor / Accessories</span><br>- Wear a similar type of armor to a knight/fencer. However, equipment specialized for a specific class is excluded.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15234-4\" lucid=\"\" Gothic\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" jhenghei\",=\"\" meiryo,=\"\" \"ms=\"\" pgothic\",=\"\" arial,=\"\" dotum,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\" style=\"font-family: \"lucid Gothic\", \"Malgun Gothic\", AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, \"Noto Sans CJK KR\", Dotum, arial, \"Microsoft NeoGothic\", \"Droid sans\", sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n   <h2>Lancer Skills</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n   <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; clear: both;\">\r\n      <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n         <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/20/88/9b5a852d2d44a5953391de02.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n         <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">It has a variety of ability-enhancing passive skills.</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n         <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/20/88/4fd4dd8355f1365e05a18cf0.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n         <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">In order to learn the art of a lancer, you need a spear book.</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <p>There are lancer skills that can only be used by lancers, and you can learn them by using them after obtaining a spear book through quests or hunting. When using skills, some skills require crystals <br>to be used, and some passive skills automatically consume crystals every time they are activated.</p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <p>Detailed information about each technology can be found on the Spear Knight technology page.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '/upload/2021\\09\\13/002_12.jpg', 'false', 'false'),
(6, 'Knight, Elf Reboot', '<div class=\"section-contents\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" applesdgothicneo-light,=\"\" \"noto=\"\" sans=\"\" cjk=\"\" kr\",=\"\" dotum,=\"\" 돋움,=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" neogothic\",=\"\" \"droid=\"\" sans\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"wrap-contents\">\r\n   <div class=\"section-wiki\" style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto;\">\r\n      <div class=\"section-wiki\">\r\n         <div class=\"wiki__group\" style=\"padding-top: 0px;\">\r\n            <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n               <div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15926-1\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" jhenghei\",=\"\" meiryo,=\"\" \"ms=\"\" pgothic\",=\"\" 돋움,=\"\" dotum,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">\r\n               <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n                  <h2>Skill Updates</h2>\r\n               </div>\r\n               <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n                  <p><font style=\"font-size: 18px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Knight</span></font></p>\r\n                  <p>Improved combat abilities that are lacking compared to the main combat class<br>&#11213 With the passiveization of various skills, the return of the simple but strong main combat class unique to the knight<br>&#11213 Renewal of existing skills and items to improve the ability to return to the battlefield at any time<br>&#11213 The new skills for the Knight class are as follows:<br></p>\r\n                  <p></p>\r\n                  <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n                     <tbody>\r\n                        <tr>\r\n                           <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\