(7, 'Elixirs', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"1453-0\" style=\"padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"맑은 고딕\", \"Malgun Gothic\", \"Microsoft JhengHei\", meiryo, \"MS PGothic\", 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n   <p><font style=\"color: rgb(195, 139, 97); font-size: 20px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Elixir </span></font><font style=\"font-size: 20px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">is an item that permanently increases a stat by 1</span></font></p>\r\n   <p> </p>\r\n   <p>The elixir has the effect of increasing the character stat corresponding to the type by 1. Starting at level 51, this is the only way to increase your stats directly, except for the bonus points you get every time you level up.</p>\r\n   <p> </p>\r\n   <p>Additionally, stats can be reset to redistribute them to the player\'s desired stats.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"1453-1\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"맑은 고딕\", \"Malgun Gothic\", \"Microsoft JhengHei\", meiryo, \"MS PGothic\", 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n   <h2>Features</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n   <p>- Regardless of class, you must be level 50 or higher to use it.<br>- Cannot be exchanged, traded, or stored in warehouses.\r\n   <br>- Unavailable when the maximum number of stats that can be raised with bonus points is reached. For example, if a character below level 90 raises their STR to 50, excluding equipment, Elixir (STR) will not be available.\r\n   <br>- However, the maximum stat that can be raised with bonus stats will be increased to 55 at level 90 and 60 at level 100, in which case the stat can be increased with elixir.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"1453-2\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"맑은 고딕\", \"Malgun Gothic\", \"Microsoft JhengHei\", meiryo, \"MS PGothic\", 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n   <h2>Distributing points in stat resets</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n   <p>When stats are reset, stats raised with elixir are awarded as bonus points.</p>\r\n   <p> </p>\r\n   <p>If a player who used <font color=\"#c38b61\">1 Elixir (STR)</font> resets their stats, they will get 1 bonus point, and the player can raise the stats they want. So, regardless of the type, once you\'ve earned an elixir, you\'ve earned 1 bonus point.</p>\r\n   <p> </p>\r\n   <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Number of elixir uses based on level</span></p>\r\n   <p>You can use 1 Elixir from level 50, and after that, the usage limit is lifted every time you level up by 2, and you can use 1 additional elixir when you reach level 52. In addition, you can use 2 Elixir at level 80 and 90, and in this way, you can use 27 Elixir until level 98 and 3 at level 100, for a maximum of 30 elixirs.</p>\r\n   <p> </p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n      <tbody>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td class=\"cel1 width50\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Character</p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Level</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td class=\"cel1 width150\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Using Elixir</p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Accumulated Amount</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><br></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">50<br>52<br>54<br>56<br>58<br>60<br>62<br>64<br>66<br>68<br>70<br>72<br>74<br>76<br>78<br>80<br>82<br>84<br>86<br>88<br>90<br>92<br>94<br>96<br>98<br>100</p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><br></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td class=\"cel_top\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><br></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">1<br>2<br>3<br>4<br>5<br>6<br>7<br>8<br>9<br>10<br>11<br>12<br>13<br>14<br>15<br>17<br>18<br>19<br>20<br>21<br>23<br>24<br>25<br>26<br>27<br>30</p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><br></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n      </tbody>\r\n   </table>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"1453-3\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"맑은 고딕\", \"Malgun Gothic\", \"Microsoft JhengHei\", meiryo, \"MS PGothic\", 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n   <h2>Crafting</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n   <p><font color=\"#c38b61\">Pure Elixir</font> can be crafted using the energy of monsters as materials.</p>\r\n   <p> </p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"1453-4\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \"맑은 고딕\", \"Malgun Gothic\", \"Microsoft JhengHei\", meiryo, \"MS PGothic\", 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n   <h2>Type</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <section class=\"list list-item\">\r\n      <table style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; width: 1260px;\">\r\n         <caption style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">Item List</caption>\r\n         <thead style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">\r\n            <tr style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">\r\n               <th scope=\"col\" class=\"list__header-label\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline