r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n            </tbody>\r\n         </table>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#11213 Priority in using Protective Buff to prevent death penalty</span></p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Normal Server: Pixie\'s Immortal Protection >>  Advanced Immortal Protection >> Event Protection Items >> Normal/Advanced Protection Item</p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Interserver : Event Protection Items >> Normal/Advanced Protection Item >> Advanced Immortal Protection</p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#11212; Einhassad\'s Protection</span></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">When playing PC Room if Einhasad\'s Blessing becomes 0%&nbsp;<font color=\"#ed1c24\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">EXP bonus +100% and Item Drop Rate +100%</font>&nbsp;is maintained.</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">If the protection is charged while receiving Einhassad\'s Protection, the effect disappears. Also, be aware that if you use the&nbsp;<font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Dragon\'s Amethyst, Dragon\'s Topaz, Dragon\'s Emerald</span></font>&nbsp;while you are protected, only the item will disappear and you will not be able to receive the effect!&nbsp;</div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"17165-3\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Purchase Buff Scroll</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"clear: both; margin-bottom: 30px; width: 724px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/613bb0edad2485e59a3058d3.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Buy 1 buff scroll for 50 Feathers</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/2c39ef4e5a953bd8670497f6.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Allows you to exert great power for 300s.</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">If you visit Koha, the NPC in the Mysterious Sky Garden, you can purchase 1 Buff Spellbook, the Decisive Battle Spellbook, for 50 Pixie\'s Golden Feathers.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">These scrolls can be used at the same time as the <font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Combat Enchant Scrolls or the Metis\' Combat Enchant Scrolls</span></font>, which is very helpful in battle.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">However, please note that it cannot be traded or stored in the warehouse.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"17165-4\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Sky Garden</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/02f008444ce88793ea64e4b4.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">A town where various NPCs related PC Room are gathered. If you go near the World Tree in the middle of the village, you will receive a mysterious buff that will speed up your HP and MP recovery.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">How to get there?</span></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"clear: both; margin-bottom: 30px; width: 707px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/35/40/d07cfb660446d804797d3c33.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Use Ctrl+D to bring up the action window and find the PC Room icon</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/35/40/129b8a9aee126569162b0c78.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Click the registered PC Room icon to teleport there.</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Press Ctrl + D to bring up the action window, and then drag the PC icon to register it as a shortcut. After that, click on the registered icon to go to Sky Garden. The number of times you can use it is unlimited, but if you click in a place other than the PC Room, it will consume 1 feather (if you don\'t have a feather, you can\'t move).</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"17165-5\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Special Hunting Grounds</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/2728b860d165dc89e0d7c47a.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">You can enter the hunting grounds of your choice.</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">If you investigate the Spirit Orb in the Sky Garden, you can enter the Special Hunting Ground.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">If you access from PC Room, you can hunt for an additional hour, and admission is free without the cost of feathers.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <tbody style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <td class=\"box1 width330\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                        <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></span></p>\r\n                        <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Tomb of Ancient Spirits</span></font></span></p>\r\n                        <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- Free Entry from PC Room / Normally requires 3 Feathers</p>\r\n                        <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- 2hrs per day/account + 1hr from PC Room</p>\r\n                        <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- Can use teleport scrolls</p>\r\n                        <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n                        <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Tomb of Ancient Giants</span></font></span></p>\r\n                        <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- Free Entry from PC Room / Normally requires 4 Feathers</p>\r\n                        <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- 2hrs per day/account + 1hr from PC Room</p>\r\n                        <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n                        <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">* Tomb of Anicent Spirits and Tomb of Anicent Giants has shared usage time.</p>\r\n                        <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">* Resets at 06:00</p>\r\n                        <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n               </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"17165-6\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">PC Room Polymorphs</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/10/42/caef7a3c095af750fc1108ac.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Exclusive polymporphs for PC Room via polymorph list</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n	  When playing in a PC Room, you can select a PC Room-specific polymorphs by using the polymorphs bar.\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">The polymorphs, which was prepared exclusively for PC Room, consists of monsters such as Black Wizards, Harpies, and other monsters.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <tbody style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td class=\"cel1\" colspan=\"3\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">PC Room Exclusive Polymorphs</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td class=\"width90\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div class=\"img_center\" style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                        <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                           <div class=\"img_center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                              <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                                 <div class=\"img_center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/95/84/cd82d64f9b6906a7e64229a7.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; width: auto; height: auto; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n                              </div>\r\n                           </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                     </div>\r\n                     <div class=\"img_center\" style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Harpy</div>\r\n                     <div class=\"img_center\" style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">(Movement Speed)</div>\r\n                  </div>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"width90\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div class=\"img_center\" style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                        <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                           <div class=\"img_center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                              <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                                 <div class=\"img_center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playn