e=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">-</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">-</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">-</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">-</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">-</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">PVP<br>Melee<br>Range<br>Damage</span></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">+2</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">+2</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">+1</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">-</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">-</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">-</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">-</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">-</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">-</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">-</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">-</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n      <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">1. Rank Polymorphs</span><br>&nbsp;- Rank polymorphs are also available for ranked 1st~40th characters<br>&nbsp;- You can check it by using the polymorph scroll and selecting the HERO item.<br>&nbsp;- Rank polymorps do not lose their transformation effect even when canceled, and their attack speed is also faster than level 85 polymorps.</p>\r\n      <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; clear: both;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/25/93/a379271c4e9a2533124e8635.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">Rank polymorphs can be found under \'Rank/Guard\' polymorphs.</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/25/93/83235e2f23a8e365959e2724.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">There are various transformations&nbsp;depending on the weapon used by each class.</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n      <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">2. Stat buff</span><br>- Characters ranked 1st ~ 20th receive a buff that increases certain stats by 1 depending on their class. The effect occurs immediately upon connection and is not affected by magic such as cancellation.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n         <tbody>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td class=\"box1 width600\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">Monarch / Knight / Dark Elf / Dragon Knight / Warrior / Fencer : STR +1<br>Elf : DEX +1<br>Wizard / Illusionist : INT +1</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n      <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">3. Access and Chat Window Rank Exclusive Mark</span><br>&nbsp;- Characters ranked 1~100 can enjoy the following services when connecting or chatting.<br>&nbsp;- On the character selection screen, a star will be added to the ranked character. The number of stars depends on the character\'s rank.<br>&nbsp;- Ranked characters can check the status of rank changes when they log in to the game.<br>&nbsp;- Rank characters have a star in front of their name when chatting. The number of stars depends on the character\'s rank.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>', '/upload/2021\\09\\13/002_111.jpg', 'false', 'false');
INSERT INTO `app_powerbook` (`id`, `title`, `content`, `mainImg`, `main`, `guideMain`) VALUES
(13, 'Ant Queen\'s Nest', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"14845-0\" style=\"padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, &quot;Noto Sans CJK KR&quot;, Dotum, 돋움, &quot;Microsoft NeoGothic&quot;, &quot;Droid sans&quot;, sans-serif;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p><font style=\"font-size: 20px !important;\">A server integrated hunting ground where&nbsp;characters from all servers gather</font></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p>A special hunting ground where characters from all servers can enter, regardless of whether they are on a regular or specialized server.</p>\r\n      <p>You can hunt powerful monsters in the hunting grounds prepared for each class, and&nbsp;characters who&nbsp;&nbsp;meet certain conditions can get various rewards by qualifying to participate in the Ant Queen&nbsp;hunt.</p>\r\n      <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\"><font color=\"#ed1c24\">* The contents of the Power Book may differ from actual&nbsp;game conditions.</font></span></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"14845-1\" style=\"color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, &quot;Noto Sans CJK KR&quot;, Dotum, 돋움, &quot;Microsoft NeoGothic&quot;, &quot;Droid sans&quot;, sans-serif;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Feature</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>- A unified server hunting ground where characters from all servers can enter.</p>\r\n      <p>- Available for up to 1 hour after entry.</p>\r\n      <p>- Only characters that meet certain conditions can attack boss monsters.</p>\r\n      <p>- PSS support.</p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"14845-2\" style=\"color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, &quot;Noto Sans CJK KR&quot;, Dotum, 돋움, &quot;Microsoft NeoGothic&quot;, &quot;Droid sans&quot;, sans-serif;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Flow</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>The play flow of Ant Queen\'s Nest is as follows.</p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n         <tbody>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td class=\"box1 width600\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><br></p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">1. Enter Hunting Ground/Waiting Room for each class</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">&#11107;</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">2. Hunt in the hunting grounds prepared for each class</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">&#11107;</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">3. Use the randomly appearing portal to enter the boss room</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">&#11107;</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">4. A positioning event occurs in&nbsp;a specific&nbsp;area of the&nbsp;boss room</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">&#11107;</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">5. Only characters who have passed the last position&nbsp;event will participate in the boss fight</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">&#11107;</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">6. Defeat the Ant Queen to get a reward</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><br></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p>* Even if the boss room opens, Ant Queen may not appear</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"14845-3\" style=\"color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, &quot;Noto Sans CJK KR&quot;, Dotum, 돋움, &quot;Microsoft NeoGothic&quot;, &quot;Droid sans&quot;, sans-serif;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Entrance</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; clear: both;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/53/94/92067eb27f091ab8c494572d.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">On the map</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/53/94/0eb6297abec98239e81c4dd0.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">The name of the entrance is an unknown rift</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>An entrance will appear in the lower right corner of the Desert Oasis\' General Goods NPC location (appearance time is random). In addition to this, when the entrance appears, a secondary teleporter will appear in each village, and you can enter by talking to them.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"14845-4\" style=\"color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, &quot;Noto Sans CJK KR&quot;, Dotum, 돋움, &quot;Microsoft NeoGothic&quot;, &quot;Droid sans&quot;, sans-serif;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Waiting Room</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/90/75/e801cdfe8512f264a61ce27a.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">There is no storage, so stock up on items in advance</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      When you enter through the entrance, you will find a waiting area (concealed garrison) prepared for each class, and you can use&nbsp;the functional NPCs prepared here to receive buffs or purchase items.\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p>- Enchant Wizard: Can receive village buffs.</p>\r\n      <p>- Supply Vendor: Purchase the same item for sale at the same price as the vendor at the start of the Tower of Domination.</p>\r\n      <p>- Teleporter: Go to the Hunting Grounds.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"14845-5\" style=\"color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, &quot;Noto Sans CJK KR&quot;, Dotum, 돋움, &quot;Microsoft NeoGothic&quot;, &quot;Droid sans&quot;, sans-serif;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Concealed Ant Cave</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/97/49/b3e1dabcfa67b1edbd8726df.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p>It is a hunting ground that can be entered by each class by talking to the teleporter in the waiting room (concealed garrison).</p>\r\n      <p>The number of monster is low.</p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; clear: both;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/73/43/97f426fbba56a8605adcef6c.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">It\'s powerful, but it\'s also rewarding</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/73/43/3bf84209f69746da172217c5.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">If you go outside the barrier, you will continue to take damage.</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p>In addition, there is a kind of barrier in the hunting grounds, and if you go beyond it, you will take damage continuously. This barrier changes in width depending on certain conditions, so&nbsp;care must be taken.</p>\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\">\r\n         <p></p>\r\n         <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\"></span></span></p>\r\n         <span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\"><br></span></span>\r\n         <p></p>\r\n         <p></p>\r\n         <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/92/21/e3a623272b80b0c1da6118bd.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">Entrance to Boss Room</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <p></p>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Boss Room Entrance</span></div>\r\n      <p>After short amount of time after the dungeon is open, the entrance to boss room (Ant Queen\'s Nest) opens.  At the same time a system message appears so be on the lookout.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p>However, the appearance is random and retention time is only 2 minutes, so you must move quickly.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"14845-6\" style=\"color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, &quot;Noto Sans CJK KR&quot;, Dotum, 돋움, &quot;Microsoft NeoGothic&quot;, &quot;Droid sans&quot;, sans-serif;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Ant Queen\'s Nest</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>This is where the Boss Ant Queen appears.</p>\r\n      <p>The structure itself is simple, but in order to meet the boss monster, you have to fight for position with other characters (even if the boss room is opened, Ant Queen may not appear</p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Positioning</span></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/21/30/555a8eb814745e4f270ac1a6.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">Only one character can stand in one place, so be fast!</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p>At the same time as the entrance to the nest opens, 20 special areas will be created throughout the nest. This area changes its location randomly, and characters who are standing in the area before the next change will receive Ant Queen\'s Chest as a reward.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p>A total of 5 random areas will be generated.  The player standing in the last generated spot will be eligible to fight the boss monster. All others will be teleported to the Waiting Room.</p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\"><br></span></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/74/73/a8c8e198939cf6ceead3a36c.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">Boss Monsters Appears!</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>', '/upload/2021\\09\\13/002_112.jpg', 'false', 'false'),
(14, 'Land of the Outcast (Inter)', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"16229-0\" style=\"padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p><font style=\"font-size: 20px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">A special hunting ground where you can run into players from other servers</span></font><br>&nbsp;<br>It is a hunting ground where players in the 90~93.99% range of each server level gather to hunt monsters as well as PVP with players from other servers.</p>\r\n      <p>It can be used for 3 hours every day between 18:00 and 24:00.</p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p>Oren Village Teleporter <span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">NPC Kelton</span> can be admitted by paying an entrance fee of 10,000 Adena, and can only be entered if you have Immortal Protection or Advanced Immortal Protection.</p>\r\n      <p>When entering the hunting ground, the character\'s ID is anonymous, and a dedicated boss monster appears. If you reach level 94, you will be teleported out.<br></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"16229-1\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Land of Outcast (Inter) Setting and Entry</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Land of Outcast (Inter) Default Settings</span></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n         <tbody>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Category</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Content</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Hunting Grounds</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">Land of Outcast (Inter)</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Zone</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"left\">Normal</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Usage Time</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">Every day at 06:00 / 3 hours per account per day (sharing time with local)</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Admission time</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">Every Day 18:00 ~ 24:00</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">How to enter</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">Enter via&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Teleporter NPC Kelton</span> in Oren Village</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Random Teleport</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">Possible</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Entry Level</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">90~93.99%</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Entrance Fee</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">10,000 Adena</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Matching</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"left\">All Servers</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Features</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">Character name will be anonymous<br>Can chat with both other servers and local<br>Can only enter if you have Immortal/Advance Protection</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">How to Enter</span></p>\r\n      <p><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/10/84/eed4c4ac124f5f395f59a880.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n      <p>- Entrance via&nbsp;<span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Teleporter NPC Kelton</span> located in Oren village<br>- To enter, you must have an entrance fee of 10,000 Adena and protection in your inventory (either Immortal or Advanced Immortal Protection).<br>- Use the Return Scroll and Clan Return Scroll to move to the safe zone.<br>- Entry is only possible between 18:00 and 24:00, and usage hours are reset at 06:00 every day.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"16229-2\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Boss Spawn and Rewards</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Land of Outcast (Inter) Boss and Rewards</span></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n         <tbody>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Boss</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Time</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Level</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">HP</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">MP</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Vulnerable</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/70/34/c29a366ee96806c2c88a3354.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Outcast Land Master</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Every<br>15 minutes</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">93</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">38,000</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">2,500</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Fire</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Rewards</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td colspan=\"5\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">Bladeless Weapon (Inter), Reincarnation Jewel, Monster Energy, Halfas Tenacity, Bless Weapon Scroll, Bless Armor Scroll, Bless Teleport Scroll, Mana Potion, Spellbook (Empire), Spellbook (Empire)(Revival), Tech Book (Razing Weapon), Tech Book (Razing Weapon)(Revival), Spirit Crystal (Burning Shot), Spirit Crystal (Burning Shot)(Revival), Spellbook (Master Accuracy), Dark Crystal (Moving Acceleration: Max), Dark Crystal (Moving Acceleration: Max)(Revival), Tablet (Solid Note), Memory Crystal (Bone Break: Rest), Memory Crystal (Bone Break: Rest)(Revival), Warrior\'s Seal (Berserk), Warrior\'s Seal (Berserk)(Revival), Fencer Book (Phantom Reaper), Fencer Book (Phantom Reaper)(Revival), Spear Book (Increase Range), Spear Book (Increase Range)(Revival)</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Monsters</span></p>\r\n    