(16, 'Character Growth', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"14421-0\" style=\"padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p><font style=\"font-size: 20px !important;\">Support stable growth for low level characters</font></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p>Various rewards are provided for rapid growth for low level characters</p>\r\n      <p>Above all, it is worth nothing that when you reach level 75, you can randomly obtain one of the following: +4~7 Dragon T-shirt, +3~6 Lumtis Shining Earring, and +3~6 Snapper Ring.</p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"14421-1\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Upon reaching level 30 you will receive Templar Weapon</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <section class=\"list list-item\">\r\n         <table style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; width: 1260px;\">\r\n            <caption style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">List</caption>\r\n            <thead style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">\r\n               <tr style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">\r\n                  <th scope=\"col\" class=\"list__header-label\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">Name</th>\r\n                  <th scope=\"col\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">Effect</th>\r\n                  <th scope=\"col\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">Detail</th>\r\n               </tr>\r\n            </thead>\r\n            <tbody style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">\r\n               <tr style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">\r\n                  <td class=\"list__header\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\"><img class=\"list__icon\" src=\"https://wstatic-cdn.plaync.com/powerbook/lineage/34/76/7b7db42428d8888cfd6883fd.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; display: inline-block; width: 40px; height: 40px; background-color: rgb(24, 20, 17);\"><span class=\"list__name\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"> Templar Weapon Box</font></span></td>\r\n                  <td align=\"center\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">Obtain Templar weapon based on class</td>\r\n                  <td align=\"center\" class=\"list__desc\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">Awarded at level 30</td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n            </tbody>\r\n         </table>\r\n      </section>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/11/57/78785bda2134dc03ffe84001.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">Requires level 30 to use Templar weapons.</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      When you reach level 30, you will be rewarded with a <font color=\"#c38b61\">Templar Weapon Box</font>, when you open the box, you will receive a Templar Weapon corresponding to your class (Weapon Boxes cannot be moved, traded, or stored).\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>As soon as you can get Templar weapons, you can now arrange Templar equipment more efficiently.<br></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"14421-2\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Slot expandable at level 60</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/52/82/5fcb47a8eaede41f01bc47c4.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">If you have enough Adena to unlock, you can do so starting at level 60!</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      Previously, you had to be level 83 to expand all equipment slots. However, after the Fencer update, all slots, including the scapula, have been expanded from level 60 onwards.\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n         <tbody>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td class=\"cel1 width150\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\">\r\n                  <p><br></p>\r\n                  <p>Earring Slots</p>\r\n                  <p>Insignia Slots</p>\r\n                  <p>Ring Slot (Left)</p>\r\n                  <p>Ring Slot (Right)</p>\r\n                  <p>Pauldron Slots</p>\r\n                  <p><br></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"width150\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p><br></p>\r\n                  <p>2,000,000 Adena</p>\r\n                  <p>2,000,000 Adena</p>\r\n                  <p>20,000,000 Adena</p>\r\n                  <p>20,000,000 Adena</p>\r\n                  <p>30,000,000 Adena</p>\r\n                  <p><br></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"14421-3\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Reach level 75 to receive a rare item</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <section class=\"list list-item\">\r\n         <table style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; width: 1260px;\">\r\n            <caption style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">List</caption>\r\n            <thead style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">\r\n               <tr style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">\r\n                  <th scope=\"col\" class=\"list__header-label\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">Name</th>\r\n                  <th scope=\"col\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">Effect</th>\r\n                  <th scope=\"col\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">Example</th>\r\n               </tr>\r\n            </thead>\r\n            <tbody style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">\r\n               <tr style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">\r\n                  <td class=\"list__header\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\"><img class=\"list__icon\" src=\"https://wstatic-cdn.plaync.com/powerbook/lineage/34/76/7b7db42428d8888cfd6883fd.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; display: inline-block; width: 40px; height: 40px; background-color: rgb(24, 20, 17);\"><span class=\"list__name\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"> Templar\'s Gift Box</font></span></td>\r\n                  <td align=\"center\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">+4~7 Dragon T-Shirt<br>+3~6 Rumtis Shining Earrings<br>+3~6 Random Snapper Rings</td>\r\n                  <td class=\"list__desc\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">Awarded at level 75</td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n            </tbody>\r\n         </table>\r\n      </section>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/11/70/a74906e0e1bd0ab0c817b4a0.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">If you\'re lucky, you might be able to get a better item.</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>', '/upload/2021\\09\\13/002_115.jpg', 'false', 'false');
