(17, 'Classes', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"31-0\" style=\"padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" jhenghei\",=\"\" meiryo,=\"\" \"ms=\"\" pgothic\",=\"\" 돋움,=\"\" dotum,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n   <p>Lineage started with only 3 classes; Monarch, Knights, and Elf.  Later added the following: Wizard, Dark Elf, Dragon Knight, Illusionist, Warror, and Fencer.</p>\r\n   <p>Each class has its own characteristics, and how you use the bonus points you receive when creating a character will greatly change the direction of your character\'s growth, recommended equipment, and how you play.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"31-1\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" jhenghei\",=\"\" meiryo,=\"\" \"ms=\"\" pgothic\",=\"\" 돋움,=\"\" dotum,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n   <h2>Class List</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n      <tbody>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td class=\"cel1 width80\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Class</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td class=\"cel1 width250\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Detail</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p></p>\r\n               <table align=\"center\" style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; width: 60px;\">\r\n                  <tbody>\r\n                     <tr>\r\n                        <td style=\"border: 0px; word-break: break-all; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/99/99/87f60883bfadd78e6247ce08.jpg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></td>\r\n                     </tr>\r\n                  </tbody>\r\n               </table>\r\n               <p></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><a href=\"/powerbook/search?searchType=4&amp;query=군주\">Monarch</a></font></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n               <p>The only class that can create a <font color=\"#c38b61\">clan/blood pledge</font></p>\r\n			   <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n               <p>Can start siege wars and have guild houses</p>\r\n               <p>However, hunting and combat are relatively&nbsp;weak</p>\r\n               <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <table align=\"center\" style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; width: 60px;\">\r\n                  <tbody>\r\n                     <tr>\r\n                        <td style=\"border: 0px; word-break: break-all; text-align: center;\">\r\n                           <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/90/46/73ba2c9f771dc02263274659.jpg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                     </tr>\r\n                  </tbody>\r\n               </table>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><a href=\"/powerbook/search?searchType=4&amp;query=기사\">Knight</a></font></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n               <p>A melee class with high HP and high attack power</p>\r\n			   <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n               <p>Relatively easy to control</p>\r\n               <p>The main weapon is a two-handed sword.</p>\r\n               <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <table align=\"center\" style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; width: 60px;\">\r\n                  <tbody>\r\n                     <tr>\r\n                        <td style=\"border: 0px; word-break: break-all; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/68/79/c9f4ae18e17be64ad7b2200c.jpg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></td>\r\n                     </tr>\r\n                  </tbody>\r\n               </table>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><a href=\"/powerbook/search?searchType=4&amp;query=요정\">Elf</a></font></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n               <p>A ranged class that uses a bow</p>\r\n			   <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n               <p>An all-rounder who also uses normal magic and elemental magic</p>\r\n               <p>Depending on the stats, and elemental magic can also be a melee class</p>\r\n               <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\">\r\n                  <div class=\"img_center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/87/14/aa1d7ef790bfad70e921365b.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; width: auto; height: auto;\"></div>\r\n                  <div class=\"img_center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><a href=\"/powerbook/search?searchType=4&amp;query=마법사\">Wizard</a></font></div>\r\n               </div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n               <p>A class to learn common magic up to level 11</p>\r\n			   <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n               <p>Specialty for hunting undead monster, by using Turn Undead and AoE Magic</p>\r\n			   <p>Only class with vast amount of magic to use</p>\r\n               <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <table align=\"center\" style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; width: 60px;\">\r\n                  <tbody>\r\n                     <tr>\r\n                        <td style=\"border: 0px; word-break: break-all; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/68/76/ad04498b28b53a3d9bf04e83.jpg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></td>\r\n                     </tr>\r\n                  </tbody>\r\n               </table>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><a href=\"/powerbook/search?searchType=4&amp;query=다크엘프\">Dark Elf</a></font></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n               <p>Melee class with high attack power and low HP</p>\r\n			   <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n               <p>Uses Claws and Edoryu as exclusive weapons, and uses dark spirit magic as dedicated magic</p>\r\n               <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <table align=\"center\" style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; width: 60px;\">\r\n                  <tbody>\r\n                     <tr>\r\n                        <td style=\"border: 0px; word-break: break-all; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/36/98/079b195db8b95425c046f4d3.jpg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></td>\r\n                     </tr>\r\n                  </tbody>\r\n               </table>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><a href=\"/powerbook/search?searchType=4&amp;query=용기사\">Dragon Knight</a></font></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n               <p>Melee class with the characteristics of Knight + Dark Elf</p>\r\n			   <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n               <p>It is a combination of the exclusive weapon, the Chain Sword, Dragon Knight Magic, and<br>Foe Slayer, which is famous for dealing high damage in a short time.</p>\r\n               <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <table align=\"center\" style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; width: 60px;\">\r\n                  <tbody>\r\n                     <tr>\r\n                        <td style=\"border: 0px; word-break: break-all; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/51/54/59e347db7314667fa14e3c21.jpg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></td>\r\n                     </tr>\r\n                  </tbody>\r\n               </table>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><a href=\"/powerbook/search?searchType=4&amp;query=환술사\">Illusionist</a></font></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n               <p>Magic Melee Class</p>\r\n               <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n               <p>The exclusive weapon, Kiringku, has an attack power determined by INT. Also uses<br>Illusionist magic with various buff effects.</p>\r\n               <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\">\r\n                  <div align=\"center\" class=\"img_center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/77/16/a9799de00e53a4cbc97b1ee0.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; width: auto; height: auto;\"></div>\r\n                  <div align=\"center\" class=\"img_center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><a href=\"/powerbook/search?searchType=4&amp;query=전사\">Warrior</a></font></div>\r\n               </div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n               <p>Melee Attack Class</p>\r\n               <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n               <p>Can equip two blunt weapons at the same time, features a passive skill that automatically<br>activates with a certain probabiliy.</p>\r\n               <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/38/11/256f58cbed4bc0057512fb64.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><a href=\"/powerbook/search?searchType=4&amp;query=검사\">Fencer</a></font><a href=\"https://rc-lineage.plaync.com/powerbook/wiki/%EA%B2%80%EC%82%AC%20%EA%B8%B0%EC%88%A0\" style=\"color: rgb(195, 139, 97);\"><br></a></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p><br></p>\r\n               <p>Speicalize in Melee Combat</p>\r\n               <p><br></p>\r\n               <p>It has a relatively high HP growth rate and has a skill that activates when wearing a<br>one-handed sword. By continuously using skills with individual cooldowns, you can<br>create a variety of plays during PVP.</p>\r\n               <p><br></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/43/56/aa6d0034c359431bbb2738da.png\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><a href=\"/powerbook/search?searchType=4&amp;query=창기사\">Lancer</a></font></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p>Melee and Mid-Range Attacks</p>\r\n               <p><br></p>\r\n               <p>It has relatively high HP, has a skill that activates when wearing a spear, has a different effect on the skill depending on the change in melee/ranged form, and has a number of passive<br>skills that enhance abilities, so it is characterized by high strategic use.</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n      </tbody>\r\n   </table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '/upload/2021\\09\\13/002_116.jpg', 'false', 'false');
INSERT INTO `app_powerbook` (`id`, `title`, `content`, `mainImg`, `main`, `guideMain`) VALUES
(18, 'Polymorphs', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15275-0\" style=\"padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: &quot;lucid gothic&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, &quot;Noto Sans CJK KR&quot;, Dotum, dotum, &quot;Microsoft NeoGothic&quot;, &quot;Droid sans&quot;, sans-serif;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\"><font style=\"font-size: 18px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Polymorph, transform into wide ranges of choices.</span></font></span>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p>A system in which the appearance of the character changes into various forms such as monsters.<br>No matter what form you transform into, the transformation efficiency increases depending on your character\'s level, so even if you transform into the same shape, you can demonstrate your abilities according to your level.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15275-1\" style=\"color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: &quot;lucid gothic&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, &quot;Noto Sans CJK KR&quot;, Dotum, dotum, &quot;Microsoft NeoGothic&quot;, &quot;Droid sans&quot;, sans-serif;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Feature</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">- When transforming, the character\'s attack speed and movement speed are faster than normal. This is called transformation efficiency.<br>- Some transformation are unique. Monster who are aggressive, become more friendly.<br>- The efficiency of transformation is determined by the level of the character. For example, if a level 70 character transforms, whether they transform into an orc or a death knight, they will have a transformation efficiency equivalent to level 70.<br>- 8.12.2020 With the update, a high-level transformation has been added up to level 98.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15275-2\" style=\"color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: &quot;lucid gothic&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, &quot;Noto Sans CJK KR&quot;, Dotum, dotum, &quot;Microsoft NeoGothic&quot;, &quot;Droid sans&quot;, sans-serif;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Polymorph Features</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">(1) Depending on the type of weapon, the transformation can bring out the maximum efficiency.</span><br>- The maximum speed level of transformation has been increased from 84 to 90.<br>- As the character\'s level increases, the number of monsters that can be transformed increases.<br>- Depending on the weapon type / rank / polymorph control ring equipped, there are transformations that can bring out the maximum efficiency.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n         <tbody>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/52/68/84e38cf8878c3a24278a8353.png\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Short Range (Sword/Spear)</span><br>- Can use all melee weapon<br>- Increased attack speed<br>- Chainswords/Spear can also be<br>transformed into melee range, but<br>the attack distance is changed to<br>1 cell radius<br>- You must transform into a close<br>range polymorph to maintain the<br>2 cell attack radius.</td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/69/55/9190a32d239c4048108c15d0.png\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Magic</span><br>- Increase magic cast speed<br>- Can use all melee weapons</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/51/30/b46071a48b91153c0394de19.png\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Ranged (Bow)</span><br>- Increase attack speed of range<br>weapons<br>- Must equip bow</td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/88/91/8d22ea3952cc7948efd67731.png\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Movement</span><br>- Increase walk speed</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/54/87/37abbe0fed54d9ca5a2b8743.png\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Rank Poly</span><br>- Avaialble from 3rd - 40th rank<br>- Provides PvP Damage +2</td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/30/48/457e10d21671d05635857d78.png\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Polymorph Domination Ring</span><br></p>\r\n                  <p>- Only when ring is equipped<br>- Provides PvP Damage +2<br>- Cancellable<br>- Safe Change<br>- Polymorph Immunity Bar</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right;\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/67/81/744b26e2a83a56123389e4ee.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\"></div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">(2) Running Motion</span><br>- In the remastered update, the character\'s movement speed has been increased.<br>- In particular, the running motion, which was only applied when using the Rank Polymorph and Polymorph Control Ring, will also be applied to the level 80 polymorphs + 3 speed acceleration states.<br>- In other words, in the remaster, the running motion is added when transforming, as follows.\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p><font color=\"#ed1c24\">After transforming over level 80, 3 speed acceleration states.<br>After transforming into a rank, gain 3 accelerations.<br>Guardian / Shadow star 2-stage acceleration after transformation. (Requires Polymorph Domination Ring)</font></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right;\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/32/16/7b8f3fb9c1c71247d3f1a645.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\"></div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">(3) Attractive Special Transformation – Polymorph Domination Ring<br></span>- While wearing the Polymorph Domination Ring, you can choose an exclusive transformation.<br>- The exclusive transformation of the Polymorph Domination Ring has the effect of +2 additional PVP damage.<br>- All transformations have the effect of Cancellation / Safe Change / Transformation Bar immunity, which is a great advantage in PVP.\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p><br><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">[Notice]</span><br>- Cannot be worn at the same time as the Polymorph Control Ring.<br>- Polymorph Scrolls and Blessed Polymorph Scrolls are excluded from exclusive effects.<br>- Other player characters are excluded from exclusive effects.</p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n         <tbody>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Name</span></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Detail</span></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/38/86/33ef580790a7cb3b6080989a.gif\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><font color=\"#c38b61\">Polymorph Domination Ring</font></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">- Use ID Scroll to unmark the ring, otherwise it will show up at maple ring<br>- To use, just double click and select your desire polymoprh, transformation last 1hr<br>- Transformation by double-clicking will not work with the effects of Cancel,<br>Change Shape, or Transformation Bar, regardless of the type of transformation,<br>HP +200 and +1 Stat will be applied<br>- Polymorph effects only apply when the Polymorph Domination Ring is in your<br>inventory<br>- Some transformations can only be selected by double-clicking on the<br>Polymorph Domination Ring<br></td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15275-3\" style=\"color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: &quot;lucid gothic&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, &quot;Noto Sans CJK KR&quot;, Dotum, dotum, &quot;Microsoft NeoGothic&quot;, &quot;Droid sans&quot;, sans-serif;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Polymorph List</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p style=\"font-family: &quot;lucid gothic&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, dotum, Dotum, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">(1) Transformation list by weapon/level</span></p>\r\n      <p style=\"font-family: &quot;lucid gothic&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Mic