(19, 'Stats', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"1378-0\" style=\"padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p><font style=\"font-size: 18px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Factors that determine a character\'s abilities</span></font></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>Factors that determine a character\'s attack, defense, magic attack, and other stats.</p>\r\n      <p>There are general stats (STR, DEX, INT, WIS, CON, CHA) that are raised with stat points, and special stats (BLS, LUC, VIT) that are raised with Einhassad points.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"1378-1\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Feature</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>&#8594; Each stat has a set stat associated with it, and as the stat increases, the related stat also increases.<br>&#8594; Bonus points given when creating a character can be distributed to each stat, and the character\'s abilities change accordingly.<br>&#8594; The pure stat that can be raised through elixir and level up is limited to level 50, but it can be raised up to 55 at level 90.<br>&#8594; By resetting the stats, you can redistribute the character\'s stats.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n         <tbody>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td class=\"box1 width600\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\"></span></p>\r\n                  <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">How to raise stats</span></p>\r\n                  <p>&#10003; Once you reach level 51 or higher, you will receive 1 bonus point for every 1 level you level, which can be distributed to any stat.<br>&#10003; When you use an elixir, the corresponding stat increases by 1.<br>&#10003; Equip equipment with stat options. However, if you remove the equipment, the stats will return to their original state.<br>&#10003; Use buff magic and consumable items that increase stats. However, after a certain period of time, the stats return to their original state..</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"1378-2\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Effect</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>A total of 6 stats are related to the following stats:</p>\r\n      <p>For example, increasing STR increases Melee Damage, Melee Hit, etc.</p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <font face=\"굴림\" color=\"#000000\"></font><font face=\"굴림\" color=\"#000000\"></font><font face=\"굴림\" color=\"#000000\"></font><font face=\"굴림\" color=\"#000000\"></font><font face=\"굴림\" color=\"#000000\"></font><font face=\"굴림\" color=\"#000000\"></font><font face=\"굴림\" color=\"#000000\"></font><font face=\"굴림\" color=\"#000000\"></font><font face=\"굴림\" color=\"#000000\"></font><font face=\"굴림\" color=\"#000000\"></font><font face=\"굴림\" color=\"#000000\"></font><font face=\"굴림\" color=\"#000000\"></font><font face=\"굴림\" color=\"#000000\"></font><font face=\"굴림\" color=\"#000000\"></font><font face=\"굴림\" color=\"#000000\"></font><font face=\"굴림\" color=\"#000000\"></font><font face=\"굴림\" c