border-style: none solid none none; border-color: black windowtext black black; width: 67pt; height: 22.05pt; background-color: black;\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\" size=\"2\" color=\"#000000\">　</font></td>\r\n               <td style=\"border-width: 0px 0.5pt 0.5pt 0px; border-style: none solid solid none; border-color: rgb(68, 68, 68) windowtext windowtext rgb(68, 68, 68); width: 271pt; background-color: transparent;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><font face=\"맑은 고딕\" size=\"2\" color=\"#444444\">Number of pets you can take with you</font></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"1378-3\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Determining Stats When Creating a Character</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>If you select a class when creating a character, you can determine the character\'s stats.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>Each class has a set base stat, and players also earn bonus points that can be freely allocated to each stat.</p>\r\n      <p>At this time, depending on which stat you allocate bonus points to, the character\'s stats will vary greatly.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>The maximum number of points that can be distributed to a stat when creating a character cannot exceed 20.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">ex) Stats for the Monarch class</span></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img_center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/56/28/1626bfd61952fe9f90a411c0.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\"></div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>1. Bonus points that can be distributed to each stat. The number of bonus points that can be used varies depending on the class.</p>\r\n      <p> Here, bonus points were allocated to STR.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>2. The character\'s detailed abilities on the right display the abilities related to each stat.</p>\r\n      <p> As a result of distributing STR, Melee Damage and Melee Hit were increased by 1 each.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"1378-4\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Stats after 51</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; clear: both;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/25/20/acf63c66327b5e4336f2cbd9.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">When you level up, you will see a red arrow like this.</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/25/20/354c9d15fbf3cb5f8e18d3eb.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">Select the stat you want to raise, and a confirmation message will appear.</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>Once you reach level 51 or higher, you gain 1 bonus point for every 1 level you advance, which can be distributed to any stat.</p>\r\n      <p>These points are also freely distributed to the desired stats, and the stats change accordingly.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"1378-5\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Use of Elixir</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>There are a total of 6 types of Elixirs for each stat, and using them can permanently increase the stat by 1.</p>\r\n      <p>As such, elixir is a difficult item to obtain and make</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"1378-6\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Stat Equipment and Buffs</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; clear: both;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/60/16/4c6a4616a680f050b4b30adb.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">Equipment with stat options</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/60/16/727798fbd042f9e6bd73c767.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">Buff that increases stats</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>Some weapons and armor have the option to increase STR or CON.</p>\r\n      <p>While wearing these items, their stats will increase by the corresponding options, and their related stats will also improve.</p>\r\n      <p>또한<font color=\"#c38b61\">드레스 마이티</font>In addition, buff spells such as Dress Mighty will increase their stats for the duration of their effect, increasing their related stats.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>However, some stats are based on pure stats (stats that are not equipped with equipment and buff magic), so they are not affected.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"1378-7\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Pure Stat Bonuses</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>Raising a character\'s pure stats - stats without equipment or buffs - to 25 / 35 / 45 / 55 / 60 will give you the bonus stats in the following table. In other words, the more you raise a certain stat intensively, the stronger your character will become.</font></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n         <tbody>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Points</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">25</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">35</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">45</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">55</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><font color=\"#000000\">60</font></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">STR</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Melee Damage +1<br>Melee Hit +1</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Melee Damage +1<br>Melee Hit +1</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Melee Damage +3<br>Melee Hit +3<br>Melee Crit +1%</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Melee Damage +5<br>Melee Hit +5<br>Melee Crit +2%</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><font color=\"#000000\">Melee Damage +5<br>Melee Hit +5<br>Melee Crit +2%</font></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">DEX</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Range Damage  +1<br>Range Hit +1</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Range Damage  +1<br>Range Hit +1</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Range Damage  +3<br>Range Hit +3<br>Range Crit +1%</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Range Damage  +5<br>Range Hit +5<br>Range Crit +2%</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><font color=\"#000000\">Range Damage  +5<br>Range Hit +5<br>Range Crit +2%</font></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">INT</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Magic Damage +1<br>Magic Hit +1</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Magic Damage +1<br>Magic Hit +1</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Magic Damage +3<br>Magic Hit +3<br>Magic Crit +1%</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Magic Damage +5<br>Magic Hit +5<br>Magic Crit +2%</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><font color=\"#000000\">Magic Damage +5<br>Magic Hit +5<br>Magic Crit +2%</font></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">CON</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">HPR +1<br>HP +50</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">HPR +1<br>HPR Pots +1%<br>HP +100</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">HPR +3<br>HPR Pots +2%<br>HP +150<br>Apply 50% HP Recovery while heavy</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">HPR +5<br>HPR Pots +4%<br>HP +200<br>Restores 25% HP while heavy</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><font color=\"#000000\">HPR +5<br>HPR Pots +4%<br>HP +200<br>Restores 25% HP while heavy</font></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">WIS</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">MPR +1<br>Increase MP Potion Recovery(tick)+1<br>MP +50</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">MPR +1<br>Increase MP Potion Recovery(tick)+1<br>MP +100</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">MPR +3<br>Increase MP Potion Recovery<br>(tick) +3<br>MP +150<br>Restores MP in heavy conditions 50%</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">MPR +5<br>Increase MP Potion Recovery(tick)+5<br>MP +200<br>Restores MP in heavy conditions 25% Applied</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><font color=\"#000000\">MPR +5<br>Increase MP Potion Recovery(tick)+5<br>MP +200<br>Restores MP in heavy conditions<br>25% Applied</font></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p>*If you raise STR to 35, you will receive the effect of STR 25 + the effect of STR 35, ultimately gaining bonus abilities of Melee Damage +2 / Melee Hit +2.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>*Increasing STR 25 /CON 25 will give you each bonus effect, ultimately giving you Melee Damage +1 / Melee Hit +1 / HPR + 1 / HP +50.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>* If you increase CON to 45, HP will be recovered as much as 1/2 of the existing HPR even if the weight gauge rises to a level where recovery of health is impossible.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>* When WIS is raised to 45, even if the weight gauge rises to a level where physical recovery is impossible, MP is recovered as much as 1/2 of the existing MPR.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>', '/upload/2021\\09\\13/002_118.jpg', 'false', 'false');
INSERT INTO `app_powerbook` (`id`, `title`, `content`, `mainImg`, `main`, `guideMain`) VALUES
(20, 'PVP', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"2332-0\" style=\"padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>PvP is an abbreviation for Player VS Player, which refers to battles between characters.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>In Lineage, when you press the Ctrl key, the mouse pointer changes into a sword shape, allowing you to forcibly attack another character. You can also use the /PK command to cast an attack spell on a character.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"2332-1\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Find PvP Options</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; clear: both;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/66/74/a77e74fd985599fbd074c4f1.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">Click this to set up PvP mode.</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/66/74/d2460687f7398ed6d9b35170.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">If you don\'t see the PvP mode option, check it in preferences!</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>By default, the PvP option to turn PvP mode on or off is located in the lower left corner of the game screen.</p>\r\n      <p>If not visible press \'CTRL + V\' to bring up the options and set PVP mode.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"2332-2\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Differences by Zone</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>PvP is affected by Zone.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>&#8594; Safety Zone not possible to PVP<br>\r\n	  &#8594; Combat Zone fight freely without losing your EXP/Items<br>&#8594; Normal Zone you are allowed to fight each other, but a self-defense system will apply. In this zone, if you die, some EXP will be lost, and PK count increases making you chaotic.<br>&#8594; During a siege, the siege area becomes a Free PvP Zone. Therefore, you do not receive any penalties (experience reduction, item destruction) that occur when you die from a PC. However, if you die by an NPC, you receive the same penalty.<br>&#8594; When a siege is not taking place, the siege area becomes a Normal Zone.<br></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"2332-3\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Self-Defense Systems</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>The player character who attacks another character first will have their name turn purple for 15 seconds, and their cursor will become like a sword, allowing anyone to attack without having to press Ctrl (force attack key).</p>\r\n      <p>If you attack a character with a purple name (aka purple), you will also become a purple character, and if you kill a purple character, the result of the PvP will not be reflected in your disposition. This is to prevent them from deliberately harassing the other person in order to cause inconvenience. However, self-defense does not apply to chaotic characters who are already disorderly.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"2332-4\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Duel</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>The duel system refers to a battle between characters conducted with mutual consent.</p>\r\n      <p>If you use the \'/duel\' command while the characters are facing each other, a pop-up window will appear, and if you agree by pressing Yes, the duel will begin. The duel ends when one character dies, teleports, returns, or restarts. Even in duels, if a character dies in the Normal Zone, there will be a loss of experience. However, the character you kill does not change its alignment or PK count, and if you lose a duel, there is a very small chance that your item will be transferred to your opponent.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"2332-5\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>PK Count & Penalty</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>If you kill a non-Chaotic player in the Normal Zone, it will be considered an actual PK (Player Kill) and your PK count will increase by 1. However, if a character with the alignment of 32767 performs the same act, the PK count will not increase. This is a consideration for PKs that can occur due to momentary mistakes compared to usual good deeds.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>If you kill another character in a normal area and the PK count is changed, you will be attacked by the Guard NPCs located in the town and field for 24 hours in real time. In addition, you cannot trade with some NPCs, and if you are attacked by another character, the attacker will not change into a purple state</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"2332-6\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Atonement System</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>How to reduce the number of PKs. For more details, please refer to the next page.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>', '/upload/2021\\09\\13/002_119.jpg', 'false', 'false'),
(21, 'Tendency', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"70-0\" 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" jhenghei\",=\"\" meiryo,=\"\" \"ms=\"\" pgothic\",=\"\" 돋움,=\"\" dotum,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\" style=\"padding-top: 0px; font-family: \" applesdgothicneo-light,=\"\" \"noto=\"\" sans=\"\" cjk=\"\" kr\",=\"\" neogothic\",=\"\" \"droid=\"\" sans\",=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);\"=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"17379-0\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n      <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important; font-size: 18px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">A figure that signifies the good or evil of a character</span></font></p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">It drops when a character kills an NPC with a PK or low pull alignment, and it gradually rises when you hunt monsters.</p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Depending on the propensity, it is divided into lawfull - neutral - chaotic, and if you become a chaotic character, you will receive various penalties.</p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">On March 22, 2023, a change in the alignment value reduction method and a reorganization of the scope of self-defense application in party status were made.</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"17379-1\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n      <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Variance</h2>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Behavior that lowers alignment</span><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; Attacking and killing another player. Value is based on level differences<br>&#8594; Killing a villager -1000<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; Kill Cow/Hen -40<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594;  Kill Pigs/Duck -20<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; Kill Elder -200<br>&#8594; Use Chaotic Magic</p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Action increases alignment</span><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; Hunt monsters, value is very low<br>&#8594; Use Atonement Bible, when you want to quickly recover, 3000 points per Bible</p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"text-align: -webkit-center; font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">March 22, 2023 - Alignement Value Reduction Change</span></p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- Before: Immediately change to -32,768 status on PK</p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- After: PK reduces current alignment by -30,000 (Chaotic max: -32,768)</p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">During PK, the alignment value changes to the minus maximum at once.</p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">The improvement has been made in the direction of reducing -30,000 from the current alignment value.</p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Example) A character with a propensity value of 10,000 changes to (10,000-30,000) -20,000 during PK.</p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/dec563c6b80279a3853dcc63.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"text-align: -webkit-center; font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Improved Self-Defense (purple character name)</span></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- If any party member enters Self-Defense status, all other party members in line of sight will also be placed in Self-Defense status.</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- When a party member performs a one-sided PK, the party member who does not attack will not have their alignment value decreased, but will be changed to Self-Defense state.</div>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"17379-2\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n      <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Neutral Character</h2>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">The state of not having any alignment</p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">When the propensity value is between 0 and 500, it becomes a neutral character and has no special features other than its name being displayed in white.</p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">If you die during battle, items drop randomly, so it is safer to move to a lawfull status as quickly as possible.</p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Additionally, the effect of recovery magic is reduced by about 50%.</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"17379-3\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n      <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Lawful Character</h2>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Alignment value greater then 500</p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Characters with a lawful value have their names displayed in blue.</p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">If you die after being attacked by a monster or player character, the chance of dropping an item is very low.</p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">In the lawful state (alignment value 32767), the item drops with a very slim probability.</p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Additionally, the higher the lawful value, the better the effect of heal-type magic.</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"17379-4\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n      <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Chaotic Character</h2>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">A state in which the alignment value has dropped to negative</p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Characters with chaotic alignment have their names displayed in red.</p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">The lowest alignment value is -32767, and a character who reaches this value is sometimes called a full chaotic character.</p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Penalties for becoming a chaotic character<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></span></p>\r\n         <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; clear: both; width: 1180px; table-layout: fixed; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <tbody style=\"border: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <tr style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#215; Name displayed in Red<br><br>&#215; After becoming a chaotic character with a alignment value of less than 30000, you will be attacked by a guard for 24 hours in real time. However, the guard will not attack a character who became chaotic due to an action other than PK, a character who died and was revived by a guard, or a character who became a chaotic character after 24 hours due to PK.<br><br>&#215; Can not trade with most NPCs. However, you can trade with a few (Balsim on Talking Island, Ashur in the Oasis, and Jackson in Fire-Field Village)<br><br>&#215; If you are attacked by an NPC such as a monster in the normal zone and die, an item will drop.<br><br>&#215; If you are attacked and killed by another player character in the normal zone, the dropped item evaporates.<br><br>&#215; The effect of recovery magic is reduced by about 50%.</p>\r\n                  </td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n            </tbody>\r\n         </table>\r\n         <br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Because it has this fatal risk, if you become a chaotic character, it is important to somehow increase your alignment level.\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">For combat specialized servers</span></p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">In the case of combat-specialized servers that prioritize PvP between players, the penalty for becoming a chaotic character is relatively small, and there are special buffs that can only be received if you are a chaotic character.</p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">A weapon that becomes stronger when used by a Chaotic character.</span></p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Some weapons have the effect of increasing attack power as the alignment value becomes negative.</p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <section class=\"list list-item\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <table style=\"vertical-align: middle; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; width: 1180px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <caption style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></caption>\r\n               <thead style=\"border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <tr style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <th scope=\"col\" class=\"list__header-label\" style=\"border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; border-image: initial; vertical-align: middle; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Name</th>\r\n                     <th scope=\"col\" style=\"border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; border-image: initial; vertical-align: middle; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Type</th>\r\n                     <th scope=\"col\" style=\"border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; border-image: initial; vertical-align: middle; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Small</th>\r\n                     <th scope=\"col\" style=\"border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; border-image: initial; vertical-align: middle; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Large</th>\r\n                     <th scope=\"col\" style=\"border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; border-image: initial; vertical-align: middle; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Class</th>\r\n                     <th scope=\"col\" style=\"border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; border-image: initial; vertical-align: middle; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">One/Two</th>\r\n                     <th scope=\"col\" class=\"list__option-label\" style=\"border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; border-image: initial; vertical-align: middle; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Stats</th>\r\n                     <th scope=\"col\" style=\"border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; border-image: initial; vertical-align: middle; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Info</th>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n               </thead>\r\n               <tbody style=\"border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <tr style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <td class=\"list__header\" style=\"border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; border-image: initial; vertical-align: middle; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img class=\"list__icon\" src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/36/80/400d296e217f7c47b318ca67.gif\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; display: inline-block; width: 40px; height: 40px; background-color: rgb(24, 20, 17); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"list__name\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"outline-style: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"> Girtas\'s Sword</span></font></span></td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; border-image: initial; vertical-align: middle; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Sword</td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; border-image: initial; vertical-align: middle; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">42</td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; border-image: initial; vertical-align: middle; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">42</td>\r\n                     <td class=\"list__class\" style=\"border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; border-image: initial; vertical-align: middle; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; width: 120px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"outline-style: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/img/class2.gif\" style=\"border-style: none; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; margin-bottom: 4px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></span></font><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"outline-style: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/img/class6.jpg\" style=\"border-style: none; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; margin-bottom: 4px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></span></font><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"outline-style: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/