(22, 'Protection System', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"12897-0\" style=\"padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" jhenghei\",=\"\" meiryo,=\"\" \"ms=\"\" pgothic\",=\"\" 돋움,=\"\" dotum,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"17374-0\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n      <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important; font-size: 18px !important;\">The best safeguards to protect your experience and items</font></p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">The protection system applied to all servers.</p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">The protection system means that if you die while a certain item is in your inventory, you won\'t receive a death penalty, but the item will disappear. As a result, you can no longer worry about experience drops and item drops.</p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Above all, the protection system is also applied to PvP, making it possible to play more actively. However, if you PK a character who is not in self-defense, you will not drop protection, so you will not be able to get protection with indiscriminate PK.</p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">On March 22, 2023, a free protection system was introduced along with a new UI and feature improvements.</p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">In addition, a system has been added that gives TAM users up to 2 free Immortal Protections every day.</p>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br></div>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"17374-1\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n      <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Features</h2>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- If you have a protection item in your inventory, the effect will automatically activate upon death.</p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- Protective items are obtained by crafting, and can only be crafted if you have at least 30,000 disposition points in addition to materials.</p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- If you already have a Blessing item, you can\'t craft it. However, you can carry up to 3 of each type (see explanation below).</p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- If you die in self-defense, your protection item will turn into an item that can be converted into Adena and then drop.</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"17374-2\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n      <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Protective Items</h2>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <section class=\"list list-item\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <table style=\"vertical-align: middle; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; width: 1180px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <caption style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">List</caption>\r\n               <thead style=\"border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <tr style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <th scope=\"col\" class=\"list__header-label\" style=\"border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; border-image: initial; vertical-align: middle; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Name</th>\r\n                     <th scope=\"col\" style=\"border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; border-image: initial; vertical-align: middle; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Effect</th>\r\n                     <th scope=\"col\" style=\"border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; border-image: initial; vertical-align: middle; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Detail</th>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n               </thead>\r\n               <tbody style=\"border: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <tr style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <td class=\"list__header\" style=\"border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; border-image: initial; vertical-align: middle; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img class=\"list__icon\" src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/99/99/8599.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; display: inline-block; width: 40px; height: 40px; background-color: rgb(24, 20, 17); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"list__name\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"outline-style: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"> Advance Immortal Protection</span></font></span></td>\r\n                     <td style=\"border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; border-image: initial; vertical-align: middle; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></td>\r\n                     <td class=\"list__desc\" style=\"border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; border-image: initial; vertical-align: middle; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">If you die while in possession, it prevents experience loss and item drop penalties and disappears.<br style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">If you die in self-defense, it turns into Burnt High-Grade Immortal Protection and drops.</td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <td class=\"list__header\" style=\"border-right: 0px; border-bottom: 0px; border-image: initial; vertical-align: middle; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img class=\"list__icon\" src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/4