text-align: left; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">While in possession of a protection item, there is no experience loss penalty</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">If you have the above items in your inventory, you will not receive a death penalty.</p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">If you have both types of items, the penalty applied upon death determines which item will disappear.</p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">For example, if you are in a situation where you are penalized for dropping an item that decreases experience points, your Advance Immortal Protection will disappear, and if you are in a situation where you are penalized for dropping experience points, your Immortal Protection will disappear.</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"17374-3\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n      <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Incase of Self Defense</h2>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n            <section class=\"list list-item\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <table style=\"vertical-align: middle; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; width: 1180px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <caption