rgb(162, 168, 178); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; width: 35px; height: 35px; z-index: 2; top: -6px; left: 10px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"object__name\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 18px; font-size: 14px; min-height: 50px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"outline-style: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Adena </span></font>300,000</span></li>\r\n                  <li style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; position: relative; text-align: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img class=\"object__icon\" src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/06/06/8206.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-color: rgb(162, 168, 178); outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; width: 35px; height: 35px; z-index: 2; top: -6px; left: 10px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"object__name\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; padding-bottom: 18px; font-size: 14px; min-height: 50px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"outline-style: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Rebirth Jewel </span></font>5</span><span class=\"bullet plus\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; position: absolute; left: -29px; top: -1px; content: &quot;&quot;; display: inline-block; width: 20px; height: 20px; z-index: 2; background-image: url(&quot;../img/powerbook/icon-plus.png&quot;); background-size: 20px 20px; background-position: center center; background-repeat: no-repeat; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></span></li>\r\n               </ul>\r\n               <button class=\"btn-toggle off\" style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.15; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; background-position: 0px 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(234, 234, 234); width: 121px; height: 37px; border-radius: 100px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></button>\r\n            </div>\r\n         </section>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">* 5 Rebirth Jewel<font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">, Bible of Atonement</span></font> or 5 <font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Burnt Immortal Protection</span></font> Can be replaced with two.</p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">In addition to materials, the character must have an alignement of 30,000 or greater, and Chaotic characters cannot be crafted.</p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; clear: both; width: 1180px; table-layout: fixed; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <tbody style=\"border: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <tr style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td class=\"box2 width600\" style=\"padding: 22px 25px 20px 50px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(254, 251, 246); background-image: url(&quot;../img/powerbook/icon-noti.png&quot;); background-size: 23px 23px; background-position: 20px 23px; background-repeat: no-repeat; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">It\'s convenient to make several at once!?</span></p>\r\n                     <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Basically, if you have a protection item in your inventory, you can\'t craft more.</p>\r\n                     <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">However, if you take advantage of the fact that you can make up to 3 of them at a time, you can carry multiple protection at once.</p>\r\n                     <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n                     <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- When crafting 1: Store 1 in inventory.</p>\r\n                     <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- When crafting 3: Store 3 in inventory.</p>\r\n                     <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n                     <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">In other words, if you craft 1 at a time, you can only carry 1, but if you craft 3 at a time, you can carry 3.</p>\r\n                     <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">This will allow you to have up to 3 Immortal Protections + 3 Advance Immortal Protections.</p>\r\n                     <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n                  </td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n            </tbody>\r\n         </table>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"17374-5\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n      <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Free Protection System</h2>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#ed1c24\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Along with a new UI and improvements, a free protection system has been introduced.</font></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Immortal Protection UI can be accessible through MENU.</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">You can check detailed information regarding status of Immortal Protection and how to obtain through the UI.</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">The new Immortal Protection System is expected to help you quickly judge and respond to the situation quickly.</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Learn more about the Immortal Protection System window and its improvements below.</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">(In regards to PC Room Advanced Immortal Protection (except for Pixie\'s Immortal Protection buff), the display window in the PC Room UI has been removed and changed to be viewable in the Immortal Protection UI)</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/630027dd8f7d62abea4081ec.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">You can check the Immortal Protection Status via UI (see icon above)</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"text-align: -webkit-center; font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Immortal Protection UI Details</span></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/0b01dd1bf8f2ed4edbae7bce.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; clear: both; width: 1180px; table-layout: fixed; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <tbody style=\"border: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <tr style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                        <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&lt;Details&gt;</div>\r\n                        <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- There are three tyes of protections given out, depending on how you acquire them.</div>\r\n                        <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- The daily PC Room and Immortal Protection obtained by using coverted fruit will reset at 06:00.</div>\r\n                        <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- It has consumption priority according to the type; consumed in order, Free, PC Room, Events.</div>\r\n                        <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n                        <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&lt;Feature Improvements&gt;</div>\r\n                        <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- The cooldown time of the free PC Room protection during PK has been changed to run on an absolute time basis regardless of whether you are connected or not.</div>\r\n                        <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- If you or a party member goes into self-defense (purple name), you will temporarily stop using free protection.</div>\r\n                        <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- If you or a party member starts PK first, you will not be able to use protection for 30 minutes.</div>\r\n                        <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"> (If PK starts again during blackout time, the cooldown will be reapplied for 30 minutes, regardless of how much time remains.)</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n               </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n            <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"text-align: -webkit-center; font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Immortal Protection Mini UI</span></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/aece137e89845e2ed4c76d7d.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">A mini UI window has also been added, so you can conveniently and quickly check the status of free protection and usage restrictions while playing.</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">You can move freely to the desired location, and you can turn on/off at the top right of the Immortal Protection UI window.</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"17374-6\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n      <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Free protection merit added for TAM users</h2>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">With the introduction of free protection, benefits for the coveted fruit of growth are added!</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">If you are using the coveted fruit from now on, you will receive up to two free blessings every day equal to the number of accounts connected to Mobile Haste.</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">The free protection is paid out according to the number of accounts connected when logging in after 06:00 every day. It is maintained only until 06:00 the next day, and any unused protection disappears and is reset.</div>\r\n            <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Even if the coveted fruit usage period ends in the middle of play, the free protection given on that day will be maintained until it is reset.</div>\r\n            <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n            <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">If you are a TAM user, it seems that the part that players suffered from one-sided pk will be resolved to some extent.</div>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; clear: both; width: 1180px; table-layout: fixed; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <tbody style=\"border: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <tr style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                        <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Connected Characters</span></div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                        <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Free Protection Provided</span></div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                        <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Payout Time</span></div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                        <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Reset Time</span></div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                        <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">1~2</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                        <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">1</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                        <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Online After 06:00 Every Day</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                        <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Next day 06:00</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                        <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">3~5</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                        <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">2</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                        <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Online After 06:00 Every Day</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                        <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Next day 06:00</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n               </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n            <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"17374-7\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n      <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Post Recovery (Exp & Evaporation Items)</h2>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">A system that allows you to recover from looses (EXP & Items Evaporated). The Post Recovery system can be found by clicking on the \'Deanth Penalty\' icon displayed at the time of death, or by talking to Agatha, Goddess of Restoration at the Aden Cathedral.</p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; clear: both; width: 1180px; table-layout: fixed; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <tbody style=\"border: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <tr style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td class=\"box1 width600\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n                     <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- EXP loss and items evaporated can be checked and restored in a list of up to 20 per day<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- Up to 24hrs of stroage (deleted after 24hrs)<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- Items only apply to evaporated items (dropped items do not apply)<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- The cost of XP recovery fluctuates depending on the player\'s level upon death.<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- The cost of restoring an item fluctuates depending on the item\'s grade and enchantment value.</p>\r\n                     <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n                     <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n                  </td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n            </tbody>\r\n         </table>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"clear: both; margin-bottom: 30px; width: 707px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/80/62/930152e09a658a568ba7ea32.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">List of Evaporated Items</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/80/62/ee2d65fef6bb5618704997d4.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">List of Lost EXP</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Protection items are more advantageous in terms of cost then regular items when recovering.<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Because the cost of restoring items/exp in Post Recovery is dependent on the players level, it may be not worth it to restore.  The player will spend more money recovering instead of crafting the item again.  And there is a possibility that one or more items may evaporate upon death.</p>\r\n         \r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"17374-8\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n      <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">ETC</h2>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- Protection system is applied to all servers.</p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- After the update on October 25, 2017, the Succubus server-exclusive protection items, Succubus\' Contract and Succubus Queen\'s Contract, do not receive the protection effect.</p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- After the update on October 25, 2017, the Ancient Protection item used on the Forgotten Island does not receive the protection effect.</p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">-The contract for the succubus is 100,000 Adena, and the contract for the Succubus Queen is 300,000 Adena.</p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">-Ancient Divine Protection can be purchased at the top of Aden for 500,000 Adena.</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '/upload/2021\\09\\13/002_121.jpg', 'false', 'false');
INSERT INTO `app_powerbook` (`id`, `title`, `content`, `mainImg`, `main`, `guideMain`) VALUES
(23, 'Survival Cry', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"7089-0\" style=\"padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\">\r\n         <p>It is a system that allows you to use your character\'s satiety to restore HP.</p>\r\n         <p></p>\r\n         <p>HP recovery amount increases in proportion to the character\'s level. Additionally, since it restores the character\'s HP separately from the health recovery potion, it can be very useful in special situations such as boss battles.</p>\r\n         <p></p>\r\n         <p>As a bonus, it can be used in states such as paralysis, silence, stun, hold, and decay potion.</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"7089-1\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>How to use</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; clear: both;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/25/12/0b4ec012c42d0b4ae31225a5.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">Click on this part to use Survival Cry</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/25/12/be511d6536b603c8a7662c38.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">It can also be used with the shortcut Ctrl + E</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      \r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>When Survival Cry is 100% charged, click on the guage or use CTRL + E to activate the skill.</p>\r\n      <p>Alternatively, you can use the call icon in the action window that appears by pressing Ctrl+D.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"7089-2\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Charge</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>In order to use Survival Cry, it needs to be charged 100%</p>\r\n      <p>The following conditions will charge the guage.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>&#8594; Fills the gauge to 100%<font color=\"#ed1c24\"> Survival gauge is only charged when saturation guage is at 100%</font></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>&#8594; The basic cooldown time for Survival Cry is 180 minutes and if the character\'s level is above level 90, it is reduced by 10 minutes per level.</p>\r\n      <p> (Ex. If you are level 91, the cooldowns time decrease by 10 minutes per level starting from level 90, resulting in cooldown time of 170 minutes)</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"7089-3\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Feature</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>&#8594; When using the Survival Cry, the saturation gauge changes to 0%, and the Survival Cry skill is recharged only when it filled to 100% using revoery items.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>&#8594; Survival Cry can be used even when suffering from status abnormalities (poison, hold, etc). Therefore, it can be very useful in PVP.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>&#8594; Survival Cry is a type of heal-type magic and when used in the state of Fafuion Death Heal, which is one of Fafurion\'s sayings, HP decreases.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"7089-4\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Amount of Recovery</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>As explained above, the Survival Cry restores a certain amount of HP depending on the character level.</p>\r\n      <p>The following amount of HP recovery according to character\'s level.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n         <tbody>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td class=\"box1 width260\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">HP recovered according to character level.</span></p>\r\n                  <p></p>\r\n                  <p>Below Lv.87: 800 HP<br>Lv. 88~89: 1000 HP<br>Lv. 90: 1200 HP</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>', '/upload/2021\\09\\13/002_122.jpg', 'false', 'false'),
(24, 'Party Assist', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"14320-0\" style=\"padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" jhenghei\",=\"\" meiryo,=\"\" \"ms=\"\" pgothic\",=\"\" 돋움,=\"\" dotum,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"17381-0\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n      <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <font style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important; font-size: 18px !important;\">A function that supports efficient one-shot firing when playing in a party</font>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">A function that allows party members to visually check the attack target selected by the party leader and automatically attack with one click.</p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">The player does not select the target with the mouse, but simply presses the specified hotkey to attack the target automatically, which is a great help during melee.</p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">On March 22, 2023, the inconveniences of the existing targeting, such as targeting dead people, have been significantly revised.</p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Detailed information can be found in \'Update\' in the table of contents.</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"17381-1\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n      <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Update</h2>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/7f26053c6b54663bed879f81.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"text-align: -webkit-center; font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">1. Fixed the ability to direct members of the same clan as party assist targets - Avoids situations where mistaken attacks reduce alignment</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/a8b8d6753616a6ead11b33ba.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"text-align: -webkit-center; font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">2. If the target instructed by the party assist disappears from the party leader screen, the instruction will be automatically dismissed- If the target is off-screen for various reasons (precious/teleported/moved/killed), the instruction will be automatically dismissed.</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/3d5e731b5aff8a95655224f8.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"text-align: -webkit-center; font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">3. Party assist target indication is not possible when the party leader is dead - Modified so that party assist target indication is not possible when the party leader is dead.div>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"17381-2\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n      <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">How to Use</h2>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">The following will show you how to use party assist.</p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; clear: both; width: 1180px; table-layout: fixed; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <tbody style=\"border: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <tr style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td class=\"box1 width600\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n                     <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Select the Party Assist function in the action window, and then register it in the shortcut window.</p>\r\n                     <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8595;</p>\r\n                     <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">The party leader clicks the party window and toggles Target Display OFF to Target Display ON.</p>\r\n                     <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8595;</p>\r\n                     <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">When the party leader attacks the target or clicks on the target assist icon, the target is shared with the party members.</p>\r\n                     <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8595;</p>\r\n                     <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">When a target is shared, party member clicks the assist icon to attack the shared target.</p>\r\n                     <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n                     <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#ed1c24\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">*To remove the target mark, the party leader can click on their character.</span></font></p>\r\n                     <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n                  </td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n            </tbody>\r\n         </table>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"clear: both; margin-bottom: 30px; width: 724px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/18/20/a16a00ea52fd617fee7da98d.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#333333\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Targeting status. If you click the assist icon here, you will be in attack mode.</font></p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/18/20/37889593771a9795b6b986eb.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#333333\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Attack status. All party members enter an attack state.</font></p>\r\n            </div>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">In other words, in a melee state, party members can attack the target attacked by the party leader by clicking the assist icon. In addition, the control method is slightly different depending on the PvP mode and click auto-attack ON/OFF. Note that the click auto-attack can be set in the action (Ctrl+D).</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"17381-3\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n      <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">PvP ON + Auto Attack ON</h2>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 9pt; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">When the party leader selects a target, it immediately goes into attack mode, and party members enter a targeting state where they share the target.</span></p>\r\n         <p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 9pt; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">As shown in the image below, the party leader is exposed to a red mark and attacks, and the target is shared among party members.</span></p>\r\n         <p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 9pt; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></span></p>\r\n         <p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 9pt; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></span></p>\r\n         <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"clear: both; margin-bottom: 30px; width: 724px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/30/53/e0fe6077e95ea0aa649815f8.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">A red mark is displayed at the party venue.</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/30/53/66adcb6f789c961213e01972.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Party members are exposed to a green marker + share the target.</p>\r\n               <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n            </div>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"17381-4\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n      <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">PvP or auto-attack is either OFF.</h2>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">If the party leader selects a target, only the party leader will be targeted, and no indication will be visible to the party members. Here, when the party leader clicks on the assist icon, the target will be attacked, and at the same time, the party member will be in a targeted state where the target is shared. For more information, see the following image.</p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"clear: both; margin-bottom: 30px; width: 707px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/72/18/6bb9dbe9d43845ffac6a32b7.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">1. When the party leader clicks on the target, a green mark is displayed.</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/72/18/8defc48da77dfd0a628056d9.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">2. In this state, party members do not show any markings.</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"clear: both; margin-bottom: 30px; width: 707px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/33/32/01cb794d98270f454c140cfd.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">3. Party leader clicks party assist</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/33/32/049c3f5b1a8e77e59b874eb2.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">4. Party members will see the Noxec mark and share their targeting</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"17381-5\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n      <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Skill Linking Function</h2>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"clear: both; margin-bottom: 30px; width: 724px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/62/17/c49bb33a076bab41c9ff2087.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Hitting the Quick Slot twice in a row with the keyboard activates the skill on the target.</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/62/17/f0484f7b17ff4c6969f1cec9.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Skill linking is now easy for anyone to use</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">When the quick slot where the magic or skill is registered is pressed twice while the target is marked, the registered skill is activated (only possible with the keyboard). Also, it only applies when in PvPON or when the opponent is in self-defense (puradori).</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"17381-6\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n      <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Monster Unlock Function</h2>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/20/67/aa8cdb56bef6d884e74abb00.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">It is very convenient to apply the monster selection function</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"14320-5\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" jhenghei\",=\"\" meiryo,=\"\" \"ms=\"\" pgothic\",=\"\" 돋움,=\"\" dotum,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\"></div>\r\n</div>', '/upload/2021\\09\\13/002_123.jpg', 'false', 'false');
INSERT INTO `app_powerbook` (`id`, `title`, `content`, `mainImg`, `main`, `guideMain`) VALUES
(25, 'Einhasad\'s Blessing', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"14579-0\" style=\"padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" jhenghei\",=\"\" meiryo,=\"\" \"ms=\"\" pgothic\",=\"\" 돋움,=\"\" dotum,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n   <p><font style=\"font-size: 18px !important;\">Buff with Experience Bonus</font></p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p>If you hunt monsters while having Einhasad Protection (hereinafter referred to as Blessing) buff, you will gain more experience than usual and the chance of getting items will also increase.</p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p>Blessings are consumed in proportion to the amount of experience gained, and when they reach 0%, Adena and other items do not drop (except for event items). However, if you have Einhasad Protection buff, even if the blessing reaches 0%, items and Adena will drop when hunting.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"14579-3\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" jhenghei\",=\"\" meiryo,=\"\" \"ms=\"\" pgothic\",=\"\" 돋움,=\"\" dotum,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n   <h2>Feature</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n   <p>&#8594; It takes effect from level 1 and is shared by all characters in the account.<br>&#8594; Einhasad Protection can be charged by using certain items.<br>&#8594; Each time you gain experience by hunting a monster, the blessing value decreases.<br>&#8594; When the blessing value reaches 0%, the monster will not drop items and Adena.<br>&#8594; The experience bonus effect from Einhasad Protection stacks with the effect of experience related items.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"14579-4\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" jhenghei\",=\"\" meiryo,=\"\" \"ms=\"\" pgothic\",=\"\" 돋움,=\"\" dotum,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n   <h2>Effect</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n   <p>When Einhasad Protection is applied, it has the following effects:</p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n      <tbody>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td class=\"cel1 width150\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">State</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td class=\"cel1 width150\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">EXP</p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Item Drop</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td class=\"cel1 width150\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Additional</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/35/26/87a52ec8ed25b3352a4f7814.png\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Blessing Charge</p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">0</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Unable to Obtain Items</p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">(Excluding Event Items & Quest Items)</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">-</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/13/81/8256f96e2edeba424dc2fffc.png\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Blessing Charge</p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">1~8000%</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><br></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Einhasad Protection<br></span></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">EXP +200%</p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Blessing EXP +100%</p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Drops +150%</p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Blessing Consumption Efficiency<br></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><br></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n               <span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><br></p>\r\n               </span>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n               <span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Dragon Blessing<br></p>\r\n               </span>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Damage Reduction +4</p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">All Immunity +5</p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">PVP Damage Reduction +5</p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Weight +500</p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><br></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n      </tbody>\r\n   </table>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p>If you play Lineage in PC room with an account that has Einhasad Protection, the Dragon Protection buff will overlap.</p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; clear: both;\">\r\n      <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n         <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/12/25/3412c9c1caaa789859649fa8.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n         <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">Dragon\'s Blessing buff applied!</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n         <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/12/25/d7a8c892711352b4bc61d365.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n         <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">PC Room buff overlaps</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p>Blessing Consumption Efficiency is a meter that counts the usage of Einhasad Protection, blessing consumption is reduced during hunts. Since this is applied at level 1, you may begin with 0%.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"14579-5\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" jhenghei\",=\"\" meiryo,=\"\" \"ms=\"\" pgothic\",=\"\" 돋움,=\"\" dotum,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n   <h2>Einhasad\'s Protection</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n      <tbody>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td class=\"cel1 width150\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">State</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td class=\"cel1 width150\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">EXP</p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Drops</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td class=\"cel1 width150\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Additional</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/59/48/1122eeeb1423a1d10dc1040f.png\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Einhasad Protection</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><br></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Einhasad Protection</span><br></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">EXP +100%</p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Drops 100%</p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><br></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\"><br></span></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Dragon Protection</span><br></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Damage Reduction +2</p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Weight +100</p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><br></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/78/63/ce8d657dd881290c2b53e9aa.png\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Einhasad Protection (PC)</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><br></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Einhasad Protection (PC)</span><br></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">EXP +100%</p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Drops 100%</p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><br></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\"><br></span></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Dragon Protection (PC)</span><br></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Damage Reduction +2</p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Weight +100</p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><br></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n      </tbody>\r\n   </table>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p>A buff that maintains <font color=\"#ed1c24\">EXP Bonus +100% Drops +100% </font>even when protection becomes 0%</p>\r\n   <p>When Einhasad\'s Protection is applied, the Dragon\'s Protection buff is automatically added. When the protection reaches 0% while receiving protection, protection is automatically activated, and when the protection becomes more than 0% due to charging, etc., protection is deactivated.</p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p><font color=\"#000000\"><br></font></p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Using Items</span>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p>If you use Einhasad Protection-related items sold in the Lineage NShop, you will gain a protection effect for a certain period of time (only the character who used the item will receive the protection effect). Please note that the protection time will be consumed regardless of whether you are connected or not.</p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <section class=\"list list-item\">\r\n      <table style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; width: 1260px;\">\r\n         <caption style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\"></caption>\r\n         <thead style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">\r\n            <tr style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">\r\n               <th scope=\"col\" class=\"list__header-label\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">Name</th>\r\n               <th scope=\"col\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">Effect</th>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </thead>\r\n         <tbody style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">\r\n            <tr style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">\r\n               <td class=\"list__header\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\"><img class=\"list__icon\" src=\"https://wstatic-cdn.plaync.com/powerbook/lineage/75/24/631e5e55b9fde7c69e110211.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; display: inline-block; width: 40px; height: 40px; background-color: rgb(24, 20, 17);\"><span class=\"list__name\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"> Einhasad\'s Protection Box</font></span></td>\r\n               <td style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">Obtain 1 Einhasad’s Protection (30d)</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">\r\n               <td class=\"list__header\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\"><img class=\"list__icon\" src=\"https://wstatic-cdn.plaync.com/powerbook/lineage/97/41/ac31567cf7e745d5a58309da.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; display: inline-block; width: 40px; height: 40px; background-color: rgb(24, 20, 17);\"><span class=\"list__name\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"> Einhasad\'s Protection Package</font></span></td>\r\n               <td style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">Obtain 3 Einhasad’s Protection (30d)</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">\r\n               <td class=\"list__header\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\"><img class=\"list__icon\" src=\"https://wstatic-cdn.plaync.com/powerbook/lineage/20/82/3fe0c7f04809332eae72e5b3.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; display: inline-block; width: 40px; height: 40px; background-color: rgb(24, 20, 17);\"><span class=\"list__name\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"> Einhasad Protection (30d)</font></span></td>\r\n               <td style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">Applies Einhasad\'s Protection for 30 days</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n   </section>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\"></span></p>\r\n   <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\">\r\n      <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right;\">\r\n         <span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/20/83/b7a3f0ead80638403d8fb53f.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\"></span>\r\n         <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">When playing in a PC room, a dedicated buff is applied.</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">When playing in a PC room</span>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p>If you play at the Lineage PC Room, you will receive Einhasad Protection (PC) buff. If you play in a PC Room while receiving Einhasad Protection, Einhasad Protection time will be reduced, and the Dragon\'s Protection (PC) buff will be applied.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"14579-6\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" jhenghei\",=\"\" meiryo,=\"\" \"ms=\"\" pgothic\",=\"\" 돋움,=\"\" dotum,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n   <h2>Blessing Charge</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n   <p>Blessings are charged when you use Dragon\'s Diamond type items. Additionally, you can recharge blessings by using various contents or clearing events.</p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Content Rewards</span></p>\r\n   <p>- Participate in <font color=\"#c38b61\">Infinite War (Giran) </font>and receive 100% charge when defeating boss monsters Balrog and Grim Reaper.</p>\r\n   <p>- When killing <font color=\"#c38b61\">Sand Worm</font> receive 300% charge</p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\">\r\n      <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right;\">\r\n         <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\">\r\n            <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right;\">\r\n               <img src=\"https:/