c=\"https://wstatic-cdn.plaync.com/powerbook/lineage/36/36/7836.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; display: inline-block; width: 40px; height: 40px; background-color: rgb(24, 20, 17);\"><span class=\"list__name\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"> Dragon Diamond (High)(Engraved)</font></span></td>\r\n               <td align=\"center\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">600 Charge</td>\r\n               <td class=\"list__desc\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">EXP bonus only applies if you have remaining blessing<br></td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">\r\n               <td class=\"list__header\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\"><img class=\"list__icon\" src=\"https://wstatic-cdn.plaync.com/powerbook/lineage/21/21/3721.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; display: inline-block; width: 40px; height: 40px; background-color: rgb(24, 20, 17);\"><span class=\"list__name\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"> Dragon Diamond</font></span></td>\r\n               <td align=\"center\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">100 Charge</td>\r\n               <td class=\"list__desc\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">EXP bonus only applies if you have remaining blessing</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">\r\n               <td class=\"list__header\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\"><img class=\"list__icon\" src=\"https://wstatic-cdn.plaync.com/powerbook/lineage/27/27/3727.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; display: inline-block; width: 40px; height: 40px; background-color: rgb(24, 20, 17);\"><span class=\"list__name\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"> Dragon Sapphire</font></span></td>\r\n               <td align=\"center\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">50 Charge</td>\r\n               <td class=\"list__desc\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">EXP bonus only applies if you have remaining blessing</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">\r\n               <td class=\"list__header\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\"><img class=\"list__icon\" src=\"https://wstatic-cdn.plaync.com/powerbook/lineage/25/25/3725.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; display: inline-block; width: 40px; height: 40px; background-color: rgb(24, 20, 17);\"><span class=\"list__name\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"> Dragon Ruby</font></span></td>\r\n               <td align=\"center\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">30 Charge</td>\r\n               <td class=\"list__desc\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">EXP bonus only applies if you have remaining blessing</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n   </section>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <p>When using gems to recharge, Dragon Emerald has a delay for 1800s before re-use.  All others can be re-used with no delay.</p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\">\r\n      <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\"><br></span></div>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Auto-Use Re-Charge Items</span></p>\r\n   <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\">\r\n      <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right;\">\r\n         <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/18/88/7c73f27c5003e752f0630815.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n         <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">You can set-up auto use</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <p>If you turn on Auto Take Dragon\'s Diamond in the action window (Ctrl + D), the item will be automatically used so that the phase at the time of turning it on is maintained.</p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <p>For example, if you turn on at level 3, you will use Dragon\'s Diamond as soon as you drop to level 2 to maintain level 3 (use priority is set to highest &#8594; advanced &#8594; normal).</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"14579-8\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" jhenghei\",=\"\" meiryo,=\"\" \"ms=\"\" pgothic\",=\"\" 돋움,=\"\" dotum,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n   <h2>Items increase additional EXP</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n   <p>An item that increases the amount of experience gained from Einhasad Protection.</p>\r\n   <p>As you gain more experience, the amount of blessing consumed increases, but you can gain more experience in the same amount of time, which is very effective if you hunt intensively for a certain amount of time.</p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <section class=\"list list-item\">\r\n      <table style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; width: 1260px;\">\r\n         <caption style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\"></caption>\r\n         <thead style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">\r\n            <tr style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">\r\n               <th scope=\"col\" class=\"list__header-label\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">Name</th>\r\n               <th scope=\"col\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">Info</th>\r\n               <th scope=\"col\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">Effect</th>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </thead>\r\n         <tbody style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">\r\n            <tr style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">\r\n               <td class=\"list__header\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\"><img class=\"list__icon\" src=\"https://wstatic-cdn.plaync.com/powerbook/lineage/26/26/3926.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; display: inline-block; width: 40px; height: 40px; background-color: rgb(24, 20, 17);\"><span class=\"list__name\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"> Dragon Amethyst</font></span></td>\r\n               <td class=\"list__desc\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">Characers between level 1~69<br style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">Varies depending on level<br style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">EXP bonus only applies if you have remaining blessing</td>\r\n               <td style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">Einhasad Protection increase for 1800s<br style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\"><br style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">Level 1~54: 153%<br style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">Level 55~59: 143%<br style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">Level 60~64: 133%<br style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">Level 65~69: 123%<br style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\"></td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">\r\n               <td class=\"list__header\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\"><img class=\"list__icon\" src=\"https://wstatic-cdn.plaync.com/powerbook/lineage/18/18/5918.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; display: inline-block; width: 40px; height: 40px; background-color: rgb(24, 20, 17);\"><span class=\"list__name\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"> Dragon Topaz</font></span></td>\r\n               <td class=\"list__desc\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">EXP bonus only applies if you have remaining blessing</td>\r\n               <td style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">EXP +50% for 1800s, Einhasad Protection +150%</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n   </section>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p>Using these items will prevent you from using Dragon\'s Emerald for 1800s (you can use other Einhasad Protection Items).</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"14579-9\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" jhenghei\",=\"\" meiryo,=\"\" \"ms=\"\" pgothic\",=\"\" 돋움,=\"\" dotum,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n   <h2>Protection Charge + Effect Increase Item</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n   <p>The <font color=\"#c38b61\">Dragon Emerald </font>is the only item that recharges Einhasad Protection and increase EXP.</p>\r\n   <p>However, as the amount of experience gained increases, so does the time it takes for Einhasad Protection to be consumed.</p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <section class=\"list list-item\">\r\n      <table style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; width: 1260px;\">\r\n         <caption style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\"></caption>\r\n         <thead style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">\r\n            <tr style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">\r\n               <th scope=\"col\" class=\"list__header-label\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">Name</th>\r\n               <th scope=\"col\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">Effect</th>\r\n               <th scope=\"col\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">Info</th>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </thead>\r\n         <tbody style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">\r\n            <tr style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">\r\n               <td class=\"list__header\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\"><img class=\"list__icon\" src=\"https://wstatic-cdn.plaync.com/powerbook/lineage/66/66/4766.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; display: inline-block; width: 40px; height: 40px; background-color: rgb(24, 20, 17);\"><span class=\"list__name\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"> Dragon Emerald</font></span></td>\r\n               <td style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">Einhasad\'s Protection 100% charged.<br style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">Einhasad Protection for 154% XP for 1800s.</td>\r\n               <td class=\"list__desc\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">EXP bonus only applies if you have remaining blessing</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n   </section>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Feature</span></p>\r\n   <p>- Charges 100% of Einhasad Protection and gains 154% EXP for 1800s.</p>\r\n   <p>- After use, you cannot use any items that recharge Einhasad Protection for 1800s.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"14579-10\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" jhenghei\",=\"\" meiryo,=\"\" \"ms=\"\" pgothic\",=\"\" 돋움,=\"\" dotum,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n   <h2>Dragon\'s Alchemy Solution</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n   <p>If you go to the <font color=\"#c38b61\">Dragon Statue in Giran Village</font>, you can use 1 Dragon Amethyst to craft 2 Dragon Alchemy Solution.</p>\r\n   <p>And if you use the Dragon Alchemy Solution on the Dragon Diamond or the Dragon Emerald, it will turn into the Dragon Topaz.</p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <section class=\"list list-item\">\r\n      <table style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; width: 1260px;\">\r\n         <caption style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\"></caption>\r\n         <thead style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">\r\n            <tr style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">\r\n               <th scope=\"col\" class=\"list__header-label\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">Name</th>\r\n               <th scope=\"col\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">Effect</th>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </thead>\r\n         <tbody style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">\r\n            <tr style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">\r\n               <td class=\"list__header\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\"><img class=\"list__icon\" src=\"https://wstatic-cdn.plaync.com/powerbook/lineage/16/16/5916.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; display: inline-block; width: 40px; height: 40px; background-color: rgb(24, 20, 17);\"><span class=\"list__name\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"> Dragon Alchemy Solution</font></span></td>\r\n               <td style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">When used on Dragon Diamond or Dragon Emerald, it is converted into 2 Dragon Topaz.</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n   </section>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p>The Dragon\'s Alchemy Solution can be stored, traded, and exchanged in a normal warehouse, so it is worth considering handing it over to a sub-character and using it for diamonds or emeralds.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"14579-11\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" jhenghei\",=\"\" meiryo,=\"\" \"ms=\"\" pgothic\",=\"\" 돋움,=\"\" dotum,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n   <h2>Cooldown</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n   <p>If you use items such as Dragon Diamond, Dragon Emerald, Dragon Sapphire, Dragon Ruby and Dragon Amethyst, there will be a cooldown period where you can\'t use certain items for a certain period of time.</p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n      <tbody>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td class=\"box1 width 600\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n               <p>&#8594; If you use Dragon Topaz or Dragon Amethyst, you cannot use Dragon Emerald for 1800s.</p>\r\n               <p>&#8594; Dragon Diamond (Highest), Dragon Diamond (High), Dragon Diamond, Dragon Sapphire, Dragon Ruby, Dragon Emerald can not be used for 1800s.</p>\r\n               <p></p>\r\n               <p>&#8594; When using Dragon Emerald, you cannot use any Dragon Gem items for 1800s.</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n      </tbody>\r\n   </table>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p>This cooldown time is also the time to use the Dragon\'s Emerald to receive additional experience effects.</p>\r\n   <p>The cooldown time is 1800s from the time of use, and it is depleted even if you do not log in.</p>\r\n   <p>However, during periodic, temporary, and emergency maintenance, the cooldown time is not exhausted.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"14579-12\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" jhenghei\",=\"\" meiryo,=\"\" \"ms=\"\" pgothic\",=\"\" 돋움,=\"\" dotum,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n   <h2>Protection Consumption Efficiency</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n   <p>An option that reduces the consumption of Einhasad Protection when hunting monsters.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '/upload/2021\\09\\13/002_124.jpg', 'false', 'false');
INSERT INTO `app_powerbook` (`id`, `title`, `content`, `mainImg`, `main`, `guideMain`) VALUES
(26, 'Einhasad Point', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"17163-0\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <font style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important; font-size: 20px !important;\">Points gained by using Einhasad Protection</font>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">If you consume Einhassad Protection by hunting or other actions, you will automatically earn points.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Players can use these points to purchase special items or obtain special stats to increase their abilities.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#ed1c24\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">* The contents of PowerBook may be slightly different from actual game situations.</span></font></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"17163-1\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">How to get</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/49/66/e39477fea9ec5f14b782a2a3.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Click on the Adena icon to see Einhasad Points</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      If you consume Einhasad Protection by hunting or other actions, you will automatically earn Einhasad points based on the amount consumed.\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; You can accumulates up to 100 million points, and if the limit is exceeded, the surplus points will disappear.<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; Points are not accumlated when using Dragon Diamonds or by Weekly Quest or Events<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; If only Einhasad\'s Protection or Einhasad Protection (PC) is applied, no points will be accumulated.<p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <tbody style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td class=\"box2 width600\" style=\"padding: 22px 25px 20px 50px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(254, 251, 246); background-image: url(&quot;../img/powerbook/icon-noti.png&quot;); background-size: 23px 23px; background-position: 20px 23px; background-repeat: no-repeat; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Recharge Protection by Participating in Events</span><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">In addition to Dragon Diamonds, you can recharge protection with various game contents</p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#10003; Infinity War (Giran)<br>&#10003; Ant Queen - Hunt & Collect Rewards<br>&#10003; Sand Worm - Hunt & Collect Rewards<br>&#10003; Attendance Check & Other Events</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"17163-2\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !impor