(27, 'TAM', '<p style=\"color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, &quot;Noto Sans CJK KR&quot;, Dotum, 돋움, &quot;Microsoft NeoGothic&quot;, &quot;Droid sans&quot;, sans-serif;\"><span 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" jhenghei\",=\"\" meiryo,=\"\" \"ms=\"\" pgothic\",=\"\" 돋움,=\"\" dotum,=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\">현재</span><font color=\"#c38b61\" face=\"맑은 고딕, Malgun Gothic, Microsoft JhengHei, meiryo, MS PGothic, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif\">Giran Village</font><span 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" jhenghei\",=\"\" meiryo,=\"\" \"ms=\"\" pgothic\",=\"\" 돋움,=\"\" dotum,=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\">의 NPC,</span><font color=\"#c38b61\">Kruna</font><span 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" jhenghei\",=\"\" meiryo,=\"\" \"ms=\"\" pgothic\",=\"\" 돋움,=\"\" dotum,=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\">를 찾아가면 TAM으로 다양한 아이템을 구입할 수 있다.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, &quot;Noto Sans CJK KR&quot;, Dotum, 돋움, &quot;Microsoft NeoGothic&quot;, &quot;Droid sans&quot;, sans-serif;\"><span 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" jhenghei\",=\"\" meiryo,=\"\" \"ms=\"\" pgothic\",=\"\" 돋움,=\"\" dotum,=\"\" sans-serif;\"=\"\"><br></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"10119-1\" 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" jhenghei\",=\"\" meiryo,=\"\" \"ms=\"\" pgothic\",=\"\" 돋움,=\"\" dotum,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\" style=\"font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, &quot;Noto Sans CJK KR&quot;, Dotum, 돋움, &quot;Microsoft NeoGothic&quot;, &quot;Droid sans&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n   <h2>Feature</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n   <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; clear: both;\">\r\n      <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n         <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/94/94/b146beb561b48f0ac3f69ceb.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n         <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">If you click on Adena guage you can see the cumulative TAM</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\">\r\n      <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right;\"></div>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p>Your TAM guage is accumulated when you hunt monsters.  When your TAM gauge is full, it is settled into your TAM gauge.  When purchasing items with TAM thereafter, the calculation is based on TAM you have acquired.</p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\"></div>\r\n   <p>&#8594; TAM can be collected by playing the Haste App.</p>\r\n   <p>&#8594; You can earn more TAM by defeating boss monster while playing the Haste App.</p>\r\n   <p>&#8594; TAM cannot be traded or exhcanged.</p>\r\n   <p>&#8594; TAM can be used regardless of server or character as long as it is a character within the same account.</p>\r\n   <p>&#8594; You can check the amount of TAM by clicking the Adena icon at the bottom left of the screen.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"10119-2\" 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" jhenghei\",=\"\" meiryo,=\"\" \"ms=\"\" pgothic\",=\"\" 돋움,=\"\" dotum,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\" style=\"font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, AppleSDGothicNeo-Light, &quot;Noto Sans CJK KR&quot;, Dotum, 돋움, &quot;Microsoft NeoGothic&quot;, &quot;Droid sans&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki_