(28, 'Fishing', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"24-0\" style=\"padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>A mini-game to enjoy in Gludin Village</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>Players level 30 or higher can enter fishing area.  Fishing Rod, and Fishing Bait are required which can be purchased by the Fishing Merchant in Gludin Village.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>The fishes you catch can be sold to NPC in exchange for \"Berries\" which can be used to purchase various equipment and items.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"24-1\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Objective</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n         <tbody>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td class=\"box1 width600\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Fishing Flow</span></p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">1. Catch Fish</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">&#8595;</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">2. Exchange for Berries</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">&#8595;</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">3. Purchase Equipment & Items</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>The key to fishing to collect Berries</p>\r\n      <p>Various items can be purchased with Berries like the Magic Doll (Lich)</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"24-2\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Buy Rod & Bait</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <section class=\"list list-item\">\r\n         <table style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; width: 1260px;\">\r\n            <caption style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\"></caption>\r\n            <thead style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">\r\n               <tr style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">\r\n                  <th scope=\"col\" class=\"list__header-label\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">Name</th>\r\n                  <th scope=\"col\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">Effect</th>\r\n                  <th scope=\"col\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">Info</th>\r\n               </tr>\r\n            </thead>\r\n            <tbody style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">\r\n               <tr style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">\r\n                  <td class=\"list__header\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\"><img class=\"list__icon\" src=\"https://wstatic-cdn.plaync.com/powerbook/lineage/90/90/5690.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; display: inline-block; width: 40px; height: 40px; background-color: rgb(24, 20, 17);\"><span class=\"list__name\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"> Fishing Rod</font></span></td>\r\n                  <td style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">Catch fish every 240s</td>\r\n                  <td class=\"list__desc\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">Types of fish will vary depending on rod and reel used</td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n               <tr style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">\r\n                  <td class=\"list__header\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\"><img class=\"list__icon\" src=\"https://wstatic-cdn.plaync.com/powerbook/lineage/29/29/9529.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; display: inline-block; width: 40px; height: 40px; background-color: rgb(24, 20, 17);\"><span class=\"list__name\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"> Pauls Growth Reel (50)</font></span></td>\r\n                  <td style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">When used on Fishing Rod, becomes Paul\'s Growth Fishing Rod<br style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\"></td>\r\n                  <td class=\"list__desc\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">-</td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n               <tr style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">\r\n                  <td class=\"list__header\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\"><img class=\"list__icon\" src=\"https://wstatic-cdn.plaync.com/powerbook/lineage/58/58/4958.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; display: inline-block; width: 40px; height: 40px; background-color: rgb(24, 20, 17);\"><span class=\"list__name\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"> Bait</font></span></td>\r\n                  <td style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\"></td>\r\n                  <td class=\"list__desc\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">Bundle of 50 baits which is needed for Fishing. One bait is used for one fish caught</td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n            </tbody>\r\n         </table>\r\n      </section>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; clear: both;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/87/62/aa48bf34fda1ba32a211fb6f.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">Buy fishing gear in Gludin Village</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/87/62/e213f65e95ddc744ca1db639.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">NPC Marco deals with item related to Fishing</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>NPC Macro in Gludin Village sells fishing rods, reels, and bait.</p>\r\n      <p>Fishes that can be caught varies depending on the type of reel used.  Better the reel, better the fish caught.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"24-3\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Fishing Entrance</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; clear: both;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/17/31/5c7bb4a60839c588cbafd3db.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">Talk to NPC Paul to enter fishing area</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/17/31/307ac7f9dcad3cb8608746f3.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">Stand on appropirate spot and start fishing!</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>Talk with NPC Paul in Gludin Village, select \"Go Fishing\" to enter fishing area.  Once there, you can start fishing in the central area, if you want to change location, you either walk around or talk to Paul to teleport you around.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>Walk towards the lake, click on your fishing rod, a circular cursor will appear, clicking anywhere on the water will start the fishing.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"24-4\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Fishing Screen</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img_center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/15/83/5d0e349da0710aba1a7ff641.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\"></div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>When you start fishing, a dedicated fishing screen appears as shown in photo above.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>On this screen, you can check the reel status and the amount of bait, and if you click on the fishing item icon, you can see the items and bait you have caught so far. If you want to stop fishing, click the End Fishing button. (Existing right-click is not available)</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"24-5\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Fishing Rod Modification using Reel</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\">\r\n         <p>Reels are consumable items that increase the power of the fishing rod.</p>\r\n         <p></p>\r\n         <p>Using a reel can be considered a necessity for fishing because it reduces the time it takes to fish and increases the types of items that can be caught.</p>\r\n         <p>Reels can be purchased from fishing Merchant in Gludin Village, for adena or through events.</p>\r\n         <p></p>\r\n         <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; clear: both;\">\r\n            <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n               <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/47/11/1913ad3f6ee63e1156db5677.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n               <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">Reel on Fishing Rod</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n               <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/47/11/d514bf69fa3cd4b6561ceb6c.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n               <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">Changed to a new fishing rod</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <p></p>\r\n         <p></p>\r\n         <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\">\r\n            &#8594; The number of uses can be increased by repeatedly using the same type of reel.\r\n            <p>&#8594; If you use a reel on a fishing rod and the number of uses remains, you cannot replace it with another reel.</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"24-6\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Items that be obtain through fishing</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>Type of items that you can catch vary depending on what reel you use.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n         <tbody>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td class=\"cel1 width130\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Fishing Rod Types</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"cel1 width180\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\">Reward Item</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239)