(29, 'Siege', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"14347-0\" style=\"padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>Siege warfare is a game system introduced for the first time in the world by Lineage, and is a large-scale battle between clans to take the throne within the game.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>A clan that wins a siege in which numerous players participate and takes possession of a castle receives taxes collected from the territory belonging to that castle as compensation. Additionally, a crown appears on the character\'s head as a sign that the clan\'s monarch has become the lord of the castle and can freely use the castle\'s facilities.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"14347-2\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>How to proceed</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/15/30/5eef3b2848172f7efb6deebe.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">The siege is so chaotic that it is impossible to distinguish between faction and faction.</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p>Once every two weeks, at 8:00 PM (20:00) on Sunday, a siege start notification message appears and the siege begins.</p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p>&#8594; The area around the castle has been changed to the Combat Zone.</p>\r\n      <p>&#8594; All characters of the attacking and defending clans are marked with a clan crest.</p>\r\n      <p>&#8594; Switch to automatic PVP state (where you can attack without using CRTL keys).</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>The siege takes place between 20:00 and 21:00 on Sundays in real time, but it may differ slightly from the actual time because it is based on the server setting time.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"14347-3\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Declaration of Siege</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>A siege will be declared if the Monarch who wants to attack a castle enters \'/declare [castlename]\' command.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>&#8594; Siege can be declared in polymorph state</p>\r\n      <p>&#8594; A clan that owns a house can also declare a seige</p>\r\n      <p>&#8594; When a siege is declared, members of the clan will automatically teleport to the village.</p>\r\n      <p>&#8594; Regardless of whether the siege is won or lost, the ownership of the house is retained, and if you own the castle, the house is automatically exempted from taxes.</p>\r\n      <p>&#8594; No full message when declaring a siege.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"14347-4\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Win/Loss Conditions</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>At the end of the siege, the clan wins will own the caslte.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"14347-5\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Order of Progression</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>Each castle is slightly different, but basically the castle consists of an outer castle, an inner castle, and a guard tower.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>In the case of attack, you must break through the castle gate, destroy the guard tower, and take the crown to obtain ownership of the castle. The crown can only be obtained by the Monarch of each clan, and the crown cannot be obtained while polymoprh. Of course, defense involves defeating the attacking characters. You have to protect the guard tower while attacking.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; clear: both;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/35/76/0b61817e240bb969db60135e.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">First, you have to break down the outer castle gate to get inside.</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/35/76/da2d00b26e5dd706fc2dbf8f.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">Destroy the guardian tower and take the crown!</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>Afterwards, if the guardian tower is destroyed and the clan lord takes the crown, player characters other than the clan are automatically teleported to the starting point. After fighting back and forth in this way, at the end of the siege, the clan that holds the crown is determined to be the owner of the castle.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"14347-6\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Compenstation</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/63/65/851cbb9200261ba080ff593b.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">Click on the castle on the map to see the accumulated taxes</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>', '/upload/2021\\09\\13/002_128.jpg', 'false', 'false'),
(30, 'Hunting Ground Guide', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15236-0\" style=\"padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\"><div class=\"wiki__body\"><p><font style=\"font-size: 18px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">사냥터 네비게이션 + 토벌 퀘스트<br></span></font></p><p>자신에게 맞는 사냥터부터 몬스터 드롭 아이템까지 한눈에 확인!<br>자신에게 맞는 사냥터를 등록하고, 사냥터에서 몬스터 토벌 퀘스트 완료 시 경험치와 아이템 보상을 얻는 재미까지 갖추었다.</p></div></div><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15236-2\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\"><div class=\"wiki__h2\"><h2>사냥터 도감</h2></div><div class=\"wiki__body\"><p></p><p>사냥터 도감은 [메뉴 – 도감] Or [Ctrl + B] 단축키를 통해서 확인이 가능하다.<br>각 사냥터별 등장하는 몬스터 정보 및 드랍 아이템을 확인 할 수 있도록 제공되며, 원하는 사냥터를 직접 선택 및 알림 창에 등록하여 토벌 퀘스트를 진행할 수 있다.<br>토벌 퀘스트가 완료하면 경험치 보상이 지급되며, 드래곤의 최고급 다이아몬드 소모 시 경험치 이외에도 아인하사드 축복 및 토벌품 상자를 추가 획득할 수 있다.</p><p></p><p><br></p><p></p><table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\"><tbody><tr><td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\"><p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">[사냥터/아이템 네비게이션]</span></p><p align=\"center\">사냥터에 등장하는 몬스터 및 드랍 아이템 정보를 한눈에 확인</p></td><td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\"><p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">[사냥터 토벌 퀘스트]</span><br>원하는 사냥터를 직접 선택하여 토벌 퀘스트를 진행하고 주요 보상을 획득</p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\"><div align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/70/38/9b6c2b0861cef4187a76c44d.png\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></div></td><td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\"><p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/91/17/30b5ad9426d246a3c232737c.png\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p></p></div></div><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15236-3\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\"><div class=\"wiki__h2\"><h2>사냥터 및 아이템 정보 확인</h2></div><div class=\"wiki__body\"><p></p><div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\"><div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/72/67/0909e6daf6edcb6ce8125182.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\"></span></div></div><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">사냥터 네비게이션<br></span>사냥터에 등장하는 몬스터 정보 및 드랍 아이템 정보를 한눈에 확인할 수 있다.<p></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">① 사냥터 검색</span><br>&nbsp;- 자신에 맞는 원하는 사냥터를 검색할 수 있다.</p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">② 사냥터 맵</span><br>&nbsp;- 선택하신 사냥터의 맵 정보를 확인할 수 있니다.</p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">③ 서식 몬스터</span><br>&nbsp;- 선택하신 사냥터에 서식하는 몬스터 정보를 확인할 수 있다.</p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">④ 드랍 아이템</span><br>&nbsp;- 서식 몬스터 별 또는 해당 사냥터에서 드랍하는 아이템 정보를 확인할 수 있다.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p></p><div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\"><div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right;\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/91/48/2d0ce1cca6b3170f90dbf71b.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\"></div></div><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">아이템 네비게이션</span><br>아이템을 검색하여, 드랍하는 몬스터 정보 및 해당 사냥터 정보를 확인할 수 있다.<p></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">① 아이템 검색</span><br>&nbsp;- 몬스터가 드랍하는 아이템 정보를 검색할 수 있다.</p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">② 관련 아이템</span><br>&nbsp;- 검색어와 연관된 아이템 정보가 노출된다.</p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">③ 소지하는 몬스터</span><br>&nbsp;- 관련 아이템 클릭 시, 아이템을 드랍하는 해당 몬스터 정보가 노출된다.</p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">④ 서식 사냥터</span><br>&nbsp;- 소지하는 몬스터 클릭 시, 해당 몬스터가 출몰하는 사냥터 리스트가 출력된다.<br>&nbsp;- 서식사냥터 클릭 시, 사냥터 정보를 안내하며 토벌 퀘스트로 즉시 등록 및 사냥터 이동을 통해 퀘스트 진행이 가능하다.<br></p></div></div><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15236-4\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\"><div class=\"wiki__h2\"><h2>토벌 퀘스트</h2></div><div class=\"wiki__body\"><p>일 1회 원하는 사냥터를 등록하여, 입장한 뒤 사냥터의 몬스터 150마리를 토벌하면 일일 퀘스트가 완료된다.<br>퀘스트가 완료되면, 보상을 지급받으며, 드상을 소모하여 추가 보상을 획득할 수 있다.</p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p></p><div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\"><div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right;\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/87/52/fe1251a9d58a7355060e3614.png\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\"></div></div><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">토벌 퀘스트 등록/변경 방법</span><br>자신에 맞는 원하는 사냥터 토벌 퀘스트를 추가 or 변경 할 수 있도록 제공된다.<p></p><p><br></p><p>⑤ 사냥터 리스트 중 자신에게 맞는 사냥터를 [+]버튼을 클릭하여 토벌리스트에 추가하거나,<br>퀘스트 UI의&nbsp; [사냥터 도감] → [+] 버튼을 통해 사냥터 리스트를 추가할 수 있다.<br>(단, 초보존 퀘스트 지역인 말하는 섬은 지역 리스트에서 제공되지 않는다.)</p><p><br></p><p>⑥ 사냥터 리스트 추가 시, 완료까지 남은 몬스터 개수가 출력된다.</p><p><br></p><p>⑦ 등록한 사냥터는 ①번 방식과 마찬가지로 [-]버튼을 통해 사냥터 리스트 제거가 가능하다.<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 단, 리스트 변경 시 해당 몬스터 처치수도 함께 초기화된다.</p><p><br></p><p></p><p></p><div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\"><div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/21/64/b540f9ba6d818d28b7009b61.png\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\"></span></div></div><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">토벌 보상<br></span>토벌 퀘스트가 완료되면 경험치 보상이 제공되며, 최고급 드래곤의 다이아몬드 소모 시 추가보상을 받을 수 있다.<p></p><p></p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">① 일반 보상</span><br>&nbsp;- 경험치 2% (52레벨 기준)</p><p><br></p><p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">② 최고급 다이아몬드 보상</span><br>&nbsp;-&nbsp;경험치 55% (52레벨 기준)<br>&nbsp;- 아인하사드 축복 EXP 보너스 : +300%<br>&nbsp;- 토벌품 상자 1개&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p><br></p><p></p><table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\"><tbody><tr><td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\"><p align=\"center\">아이템명</p></td><td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\"><p align=\"center\">주요 획득 보상 (확률)</p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\"><p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/86/56/b2d5ef2234ec6731f8880e83.png\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p><p align=\"center\"><font color=\"#c38b61\">토벌품 상자</font></p></td><td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">수룡 비늘, 지룡 비늘, 화룡 비늘, 풍룡 비늘, 안타라스의 숨결, 린드비오르의 숨결, 파푸리온의 숨결,<br>드래곤의 진주 7개, 드래곤의 진주 77개, 퓨어 엘릭서(EXP), 엘릭서(EXP)</td></tr></tbody></table><p></p><p></p></div></div><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15236-5\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\"><div class=\"wiki__h2\"><h2>사낭터 도감 부스터 효율 UP</h2></div><div class=\"wiki__body\"><p><br></p><p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">획득 경험치</span><br></p><p></p><table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\"><p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/82/12/93a5dfe27c1290452014b96f.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p></td><td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">사냥터 토벌 퀘스트 완료 시<br>사냥터 도감 부스터 아이템을 소지하면 추가 경험치 보상을 획득 가능</td></tr></tbody></table><p></p><p></p><p><font color=\"#ed1c24\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">* 90레벨 이상 적용 불가</span></font></p><p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\"><font color=\"#ed1c24\"><br></font></span></p><p><font color=\"#333333\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">획득 경험치(52레벨 기준)</span></font></p><p></p><table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\"><p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/73/92/8107cf86c2a0a4e7b84f2d00.png\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p><p align=\"center\">드래곤의 최고급 다이아몬드</p></td><td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">70%&nbsp;경험치 획득<br></td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\"><p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/87/39/9e1bbfc8113d5aa692dd85b2.png\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p><p align=\"center\">드래곤의 고급 다이아몬드</p></td><td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">45% 경험치 획득</td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\"><p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/85/77/b784cc05391afed033196740.png\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p><p align=\"center\">5만 아데나</p></td><td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">5% 경험치 획득</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div>', '/upload/2021\\09\\13/002_129.jpg', 'false', 'false');
INSERT INTO `app_powerbook` (`id`, `title`, `content`, `mainImg`, `main`, `guideMain`) VALUES
(31, 'Warrior', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"10207-0\" style=\"padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" jhenghei\",=\"\" meiryo,=\"\" \"ms=\"\" pgothic\",=\"\" 돋움,=\"\" dotum,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n   <p>The warrior is a class that boasts HP growth rate and physical attack power that surpass that of the knight. In particular, it is an essential class that can act as a tank in group battles with powerful HP.<br> <br>They specializes in axes, and compared to other classes, their speed with blunt weapon is faster.<br><br>In addition, the warrior class has various passive skills that activate automatically, allowing you to use more efficient tactics in hunting and PVP.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"10207-1\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" jhenghei\",=\"\" meiryo,=\"\" \"ms=\"\" pgothic\",=\"\" 돋움,=\"\" dotum,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n   <h2>Feature</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\">&#8594; It boasts the highest HP growth rate in all classes.<br>&#8594; Main weapon is an axe, unleashing a high attack speed.<br>&#8594; Various passive skills and individual cooldowns are applied to enable efficient hunting and battle.<br>&#8594; Just like the Knight, you can use the Potion of Courage to increase it to Haste2.<br>&#8594; Learn a special skill that only a Warrior can use and a level 1 of normal magic.<br>&#8594; Starting at Level 60, PVP Damage Reduction +1 every 3 levels (Starting at level 92, PVP Damage Reduction increase by +1 every level)</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"10207-2\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" jhenghei\",=\"\" meiryo,=\"\" \"ms=\"\" pgothic\",=\"\" 돋움,=\"\" dotum,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n   <h2>Equipment</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n   <p>One of the most noteworthy pieces of Warrior\'s equipment is blunt weapons.</p>\r\n   <p>Compared to other classes, there are many benefits from wearing blunt weapons.</p>\r\n   <p> </p>\r\n   <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Weapon</span></p>\r\n   <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\">\r\n      <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right;\">\r\n         <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/55/31/e9c0c09b192f6a77fc09a28f.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n         <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">An Axe specifically for Warriors</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <p>An Axe specifically for warriors are available.<br>&#8594; Warriors can only equip blunt weapons and spears.<br>&#8594; If you learn exclusive skill \'Slayer\' your attack speed increases when wearing one-handed axe, making the attack speed the fastest amongst all the classes.<br>&#8594; There also special Axes that are only available to Warriors.</p>\r\n   <p> </p>\r\n   <p> </p>\r\n   <p> </p>\r\n   <p> </p>\r\n   <p> </p>\r\n   <p> </p>\r\n   <p> </p>\r\n   <p> </p>\r\n   <p> </p>\r\n   <p> </p>\r\n   <p> </p>\r\n   <p>2021. 9. Update 15 has significantly improved the performance of some Warrior Axes.</p>\r\n   <p> </p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n      <tbody>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Axe</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Before</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">After</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/97/43/76dee7167d106825f0876cc6.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Titan\'s Wrath</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Attack: 39 / 42 (Small/Large)</p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">STR +2<br>Melee Damage +14<br>Melee Crit +1<br>Melee Hit +7<br>Fear Hit +3<br>Melee Crit +1%<br>Fear Hit +1</p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Melee Damage +2 every +1 Enchant</p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Titan Ability Triggers HP Area increased by 5%</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Attack: 39 / 42 (Small/Large)</p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">STR +2<br><font color=\"#ed1c24\">Melee Damage +18<br>Melee Crit +3<br>Melee Hit +13<br>Fear Hit +7</font><br>Melee Crit +1%<br>Fear Hit +1</p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Melee Damage +2 every +1 Enchant</p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><font color=\"#ed1c24\">Titan\'s ability triggers depending on<br>enchant value (+1 = 1%)</font></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/96/75/d41b3f28365ec81e3a1b60f3.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Antharas Axe</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Attack: 33 / 36 (Small/Large)</p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">STR +1<br>WIS +1<br>Melee Hit +5<br>Melee Damage +9<br>Fear Hit +2<br>Magic Trigger: Spirit of Antharas</p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Enchant +8 (Fear Hit +1)<br>&#8595;<br>Enchant +10 (Fear Hit +3</p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Cast Magic at +10: Spirit of Antharas</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Attack: 33 / 36 (Small/Large)</p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><br></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">STR +1<br>WIS +1<br><font color=\"#ed1c24\">Melee Hit +10<br>Melee Damage +10</font><br>Fear Hit +2<br>Magic Trigger: Spirit of Antharas</p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Enchant +8 (Fear Hit +1)<br>&#8595;<br>Enchant +10 (Fear Hit +3</p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Cast Magic at +10: Spirit of Antharas</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/78/29/2cceea85f95aad13cee06b27.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Typhoon Axe</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Attack: 29 / 31 (Small/Large)</p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><br></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Melee Damage +5<br>Melee Hit +4<br>STR+1<br>HP +100<br>Magic Trigger: Hell</p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Enchant +8 (Fear Hit +1)<br>&#8595;<br>Enchant +10 (Fear Hit +3)</p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Cast Magic at +10: Add Maw</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Attack: 29 / 31 (Small/Large)</p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><br></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><font color=\"#ed1c24\">Melee Damage +6<br>Melee Hit +8</font><br>STR+1<br>HP +100<br>Magic Trigger: Hell</p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><br></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Enchant +8 (Fear Hit +1)<br>&#8595;<br>Enchant +10 (Fear Hit +3)</p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Cast Magic at +10: Add Maw</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n      </tbody>\r\n   </table>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p> </p>\r\n   <p>In addition, one new warrior axe has been added.</p>\r\n   <p> </p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n      <tbody>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n               <p al