-height: 100%;\">\r\n         <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">Exclusive Warrior specific armor</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <p>Warrior-specific armor is available<br>&#8594; Wears a similar type of armor to a Knights<br>&#8594; You cannot wear a shield, but you can wear a guarder<br>&#8594; Special armor that only warriors can wear is also available.</p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p> </p>\r\n   <p> </p>\r\n   <p> </p>\r\n   <p> </p>\r\n   <p> </p>\r\n   <p> </p>\r\n   <p> </p>\r\n   <p> </p>\r\n   <p> </p>\r\n   <p> </p>\r\n   <p> </p>\r\n   <p> </p>\r\n   <p> </p>\r\n   <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Accessories</span></p>\r\n   <p>&#8594; Same as other classes</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"10207-3\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" jhenghei\",=\"\" meiryo,=\"\" \"ms=\"\" pgothic\",=\"\" 돋움,=\"\" dotum,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n   <h2>Warrior Skills</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n   <p>There are warrior skills that only warriors can use, you can learn them after obtaining the Warrior\'s Seal through quests or hunting.</p>\r\n   <p>However, crystals are required to be used, and some passive skills automatically consume crystals every time they are activated.</p>\r\n   <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\"></span> </p>\r\n   <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Passive Skill</span></p>\r\n   <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\">\r\n      <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right;\">\r\n         <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/34/22/da59928effb24f1c4db3d198.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n         <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">Titan (Rock), which counterattacks the opponent\'s melee attacks and inflicts damage</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <p>Titan (Rock), which counterattacks the opponent\'s melee attacks and inflicts damage.<br>Warriors have passive Elemental skills that are activated automatically once learned. The Slayer Info mentioned above is also a passive skill that can be applied at any time as long as you learn it.</p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p> </p>\r\n   <p> </p>\r\n   <p> </p>\r\n   <p> </p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\"></div>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\"> </div>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\"> </div>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\"> </div>\r\n   <p>2021. 9. Update 15 adds new abilities and makes various other warrior skills even more powerful.</p>\r\n   <p> </p>\r\n   <p>The newly added skills are as follows.</p>\r\n   <p> </p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n      <tbody>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Skill</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Info</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Note</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/18/87/43d02fdfe20e754b534e3848.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"> Tempest</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Deals powerful damage to all targets within 1 cell <br>around the caster and stuns (probability)</p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Damage increases based on caster\'s HP</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Active</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/84/70/b87b91aec3a97dad157789f1.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"> Titan (Beast)</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">When attacked by multiple directions<br>overlapping damage is greatly reduced</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Passive</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/64/55/c7db20061