.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"> Demolition</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Equip One-Hand Blunt<br>Unable to return for up to 4s<br>+ damage for the duration</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Passive<br>The warrior\'s innate beast nature is revealed<br>and he instinctively counterattacks even when stunned.<br>Reduces the chance of being pierced by<br>the Fencer skill Paradox</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/33/28/98f40c043f7715a3311a77f7.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Desperado</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Damage + Stun<br>The recovery rate of recovery items decreases,<br>and the higher the level of the caster, the higher<br>the deterioration effect. Items cannot be worn or removed.</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Individual Cooldown<br>Makes target unable to do anything exept drink potions.<br>Higher your level, the lower the target\'s recovery rate</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"cente