mg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Titan (Rock)</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">When HP below 40%, if attacked by <b>melee,</b><br>triggers counterattack and deal damages.</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">- Consumes crystals only when HP below 50%<br>If damaged by melee, triggers counterattack<br>and deals damage.</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/29/19/061581ab11ed29d78df27506.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Titan (Magic)</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">When HP below 40%, if attacked by <b>magic,</b><br>triggers counterattack and deal damages.</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">- Consumes crystals only when HP below 50%<br>If damaged by magic, triggers counterattack<br>and deals damage.</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/74/77/96d7317d9619075b1bd01bc3.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Titan (Bullet)</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">When HP below 40%, if attacked by <b>range,</b><br>triggers counterattack and deal damages.</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">- Consumes crystals only when HP below 50%<br>If damaged by range, triggers counterattack<br>and deals damage.</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/94/64/4844bb45c2fce4a4576619d6.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Titan (Rising)</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Activation of Titan-type skill increses by 5%<br>Starting at Lv80, increase +1% every<br>level (max +10% at Lv85)</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Increases the chance of Titan-type<br>skills at less than 50% HP.</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/73/88/ff5ac8e5210427fc2525bfd1.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Slayer</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Equip two one-handed blunt<br>weapons and attack alternately.</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Attack speed increases when<br>equipped with one-handed axe</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/45/57/b52e4b475cb52c5d68272a7a.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Power Grip</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Root for the duration</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Individual Cooldown<br>- Root for the duration</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/65/76/4e39389ec7eac544f91eac77.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Crash</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">In melee, chance to do additional damage,<br>based on target\'s level.</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Increase proc chance</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/86/66/d31decc5269295f57f95f682.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Fury</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">When activated, there is a chance<br>that 3 times the damage of<br>Crash will be applied.</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">When activated, there is a chance<br>that 4 times the damage of<br>Crash will be applied.</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n      </tbody>\r\n   </table>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p> </p>\r\n   <p> </p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\">\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right;\">\r\n         <span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/88/39/07f446422e1f5f7ca82f3940.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\"></span>\r\n         <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">Power Grip to block your opponent\'s movement</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Status Abnormality Skills</span></p>\r\n   <p>Unique skills such as the \'Power Grip\', which binds the opponent\'s feet and prevents them from moving, and \'Howl\', which draws the eyes of multiple monsters and induces them to attack target.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"10207-4\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" jhenghei\",=\"\" meiryo,=\"\" \"ms=\"\" pgothic\",=\"\" 돋움,=\"\" dotum,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n   <h2>Warrior Magic</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n   <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\"> </div>\r\n   <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\"> </div>\r\n   <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\">\r\n      <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right;\">\r\n         <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/25/10/a672c4b4ba957684dd3425e1.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n         <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">You can use additional magic by wearing a magic helmet.</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '/upload/2021/09/16/POWERBOOK_31_1f1754a6-54a2-4639-8afe-419ca8181b21e455001 (1).jpg', 'false', 'false'),
(32, 'Mirror War', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"16302-0\" style=\"padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" jhenghei\",=\"\" meiryo,=\"\" \"ms=\"\" pgothic\",=\"\" 돋움,=\"\" dotum,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n   <p><font style=\"font-size: 18px !important;\">Stop the Dark Forces that invade each server unexpectedly and take control of the area!</font></p>\r\n   <p><br>Everyday the Dark Forces invaded Giran Prison 2F. Join together and defeat the forces for various rewards<br></p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Feature</span></p>\r\n   <p>&#8594; Everyday from 12:00 - 24:00 there is a chance that Giran Prison 2F will be invaded by Dark Forces<br>&#8594; The Dark Forces may or may not invade, but they if they invade, they won\'t leave until they are defeated<br>&#8594; When attacking the Dark Forces, you have a chance to various items, including Burnt Immortal Protection<br>&#8594; When all the Dark Forces are defeated, a message will be displayed throughout the map<br></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"16302-1\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" jhenghei\",=\"\" meiryo,=\"\" \"ms=\"\" pgothic\",=\"\" 돋움,=\"\" dotum,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n   <h2>Mirror War</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n   <p>&#8594; Everyday from 12:00 - 24:00 there is a chance that Giran Prison 2F will be invaded by Dark Forces<br>&#8594; A message will be displayed in the center of the screen as well as bottom right</p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; clear: both;\">\r\n      <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n         <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/53/79/6f08cab3ff97f0709c6e9c4d.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n         <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">Message is displayed in the center of screen</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n         <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/53/79/02f8e9d67c59158e7d050d7a.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n         <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">Message displayed on bottom right</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n      <tbody>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td class=\"box1 width600\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">- The Dark Forces that invade Giran Prison 2F features<br>1.  Rank Polymorph<br>2. Use magic item<br>3. Same combat as regular playstyle<br>4. Hunt nerby monsters when event monsters not around<br>5. Chance to drop Burnt Immortal Protection<br>6. Items drop on ground<br>7. Different types of monster invades</td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n      </tbody>\r\n   </table>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p>- After the Dark Forces invades there is a visual difference from other floors<br>- Dark Forces monsters move in groups, and additional blessing items can be dropped</p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; clear: both;\">\r\n      <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n         <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/49/15/49969d2ce60f75de8872f6dc.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n         <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">Unique Name to ID Dark Forces</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n         <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/49/15/f1fcc554de2aac6279688011.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n         <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">Message when all are defeated</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">[Reward Items]</span></p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n      <tbody>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Class</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Info</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">All Classes</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">Burnt Immortal Protection<br>Burnt Immortal Protection (Advance)<br>Laia\'s Ring (Revival)<br>Laia\'s Ring</td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Wizard | Illusionist</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">Lich Ring (Revival)<br>Lich Belt (Revival)<br>Lich Ring<br>Lich Belt</td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Monarch</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">Magic Book (Empire: Overload)<br>Reaper\'s Ring<br>Ancient Giant\'s Ring</td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Knight</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">Tech Book (Counter Barrier: Master)<br>Reaper\'s Ring<br>Ancient Giant\'s Ring</td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Elf</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">Spirit Crystal (Burning Shot)<br>Reaper\'s Ring<br>Ancient Giant\'s Ring</td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Wizard</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">Spellbook (Disintegrate: Nemesis)</td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Dark Elf</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">Dark Crystal (Moving Acceleration: Max)<br>Reaper\'s Ring<br>Anicent Giant\'s Ring</td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Dragon Knight</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">Tablet (Foe Slayer: Brave)<br>Reaper\'s Ring<br>Ancient Giant\'s Ring</td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Illusionist</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">Memory Crystal (Bone Break: Last)</td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Warrior</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">Seal (Desperado: Absolute)<br>Reaper\'s Ring<br>Ancient Giant\'s Ring</td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Fencer</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">Fencerbook (Phatom Requiem)<br>Reaper\'s Ring<br>Ancient Giant\'s Ring</td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Lancer</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">Spearbook (Recovery)<br>Reaper\'s Ring<br>Ancient Giant\'s Ring</td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n      </tbody>\r\n   </table>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '/upload/2021\\09\\13/002_131.jpg', 'false', 'false');
