(33, 'Auracia Purification', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"16306-0\" style=\"padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p><font style=\"font-size: 18px !important;\">Raid content that anyone can easily enjoy</font><br></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p>Clearling this Dungeon within the time-limit will result in getting Aurakia\'s Gift, which randomly gives you top end gear when opened. Do you think you can free Aurakia from her restraint within the time limit?</p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"16306-1\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Feature</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">- Characters of level 83 or higher can participate<br>- Up to 8 players can play at the same time<br>- <b>Time limit:</b> 30 minutes<br>- Upon clearing, all participants will receive <font color=\"#c38b61\"><b>Aurakia\'s Gift</b></font> and <font color=\"#c38b61\"><b>Purified Fragment</b></font><br>- Can be challenged once a week per character (cannot enter with Purified Fragment in possession)<br></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"16306-2\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>How to enter</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/86/31/0820adfb2271b70597363d56.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">Create Aurakia\'s Purification Dungeon Room</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      1. Prepar with 1x Dungeon Key. <br>2. After entering dungeon waiting room, create Aurakia\'s Purification room<br>3. Recruit players, and then enter dungeon<br>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"16306-3\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>How does it work?</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n         <tbody>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Defeal all monsters coming through the gate<br>&#8595;<br>Dark Warden will appear after all monsters defeated<br>&#8595;<br>Defeat the Dark Warden<br>&#8595;<br>Aurakia\'s restrains will be revealed<br>&#8595;<br>Activate the statue to receive special skill to break Aurakia\'s restrains<br></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/44/95/b678f76dd4c48461d6eea59c.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">The party may be wiped out when Dark Meteor is casted.</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <br>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>In the case of the Dark Wardens, they cast physical/magical attacks according to certain HP conditions. In particular, Dark Meteor, wide area damage is inflicted on the entire map, which can lead to situations where the party can be wiped out in an instant.</p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p>If you are in the range of the light shield generated during the Dark Meteor casting, you will be temporarily invulnerable, so the key point of the strategy is to use this to proceed. &nbsp;</p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\">\r\n         <p></p>\r\n         <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/31/48/eb7fdf0709bcdb66bd2b3691.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">Destroy Aurakia\'s restraints by using special skill</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <p></p>\r\n         <p><br></p>\r\n         <p><br></p>\r\n         <p><br></p>\r\n         <p><br></p>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p><br>When Aurakia appears, destory the restraints to end the raid.</p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p>In order to destroy the restraints, you need to use special skills, which can be obtained by clicking on the active statues that appears in the four surrounding corners. &nbsp;</p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p>When using the skill, it last for 15s and disappears if move or attack.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"16306-4\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>구성</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/79/32/438d21f06295c7171d25689c.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p>The raid starts at the raid progression point, and the party member has 30 minutes to destroy the Aurakia\'s restraint.<br>As such, it\'s a good idea to decide in advance who will kill the incoming monsters and who will the use special skills to carry out purification.</p>\r\n      <p>If the rescue is successful within the time limit, all participants will receive an Aurakia\'s Gift and a Purified Fragment that can used to obtained new armor, such as Purified Boots.</p>\r\n	  <p>If you possess a Purified Fragment, you will not be able to re-enter the Aurakia Purification Dungeon, and it will be removed during maintenance every Wednesday.</p>\r\n      <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">If you fail to rescue within the time limit, you will automatically be returned to the village.</p>\r\n      <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Death of Party</span></p>\r\n      <p>Restart is only possible when all party members are dead, if nobody restarts for a certain period of time, all party members will be teleported back to the village.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"16306-5\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Related Items</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n         <tbody>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Name</span></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Detail</span></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/90/63/6d218b47b82f9bcf960add48.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Aurakia\'s Gift</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">You can get one of the following items randomly.</span><br></p>\r\n                  <p><br></p>\r\n                  <p>Boots of Purity, Boots of Purity (Revival), Pure Elixir, Pure Elixir (EXP)<br>Rebirth Jewel, Monster Energy, Halfas Tenacity, Armor Enchant Scroll, Armor Enchant Scrolls (Bless)<br>Weapon Enchant Scroll, Weapon Enchant Scroll (Bless), Duke Defil\'s Sword, Nightvald\'s Two-Handed Sword,</p>\r\n                  <p>Nightmare Longbow, Wrath Claw, Zeroth Staff, Typhoon Axe, Annihilator Chainsword, Living Kiringku<br>Duke Defil\'s Sword (Revival), Nightvald\'s Two-Handed Sword (Revival), Zeroth Staff (Revival), Living Kiringku (Revival)</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/55/27/dd8db5661ab4c570c3507bb1.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Purified Fragment</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">- Automatically obtained when clearing Aurakia\'s Purification<br>- While in your possession, you cannot re-enter the Aurakia\'s Purification<br>- Deleted during weekly maintenance</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>', '/upload/2021\\09\\13/002_132.jpg', 'false', 'false');
INSERT INTO `app_powerbook` (`id`, `title`, `content`, `mainImg`, `main`, `guideMain`) VALUES
(34, 'Medal of Valor', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"16314-0\" style=\"padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p><font style=\"font-size: 18px !important;\">Earn Medal of Valor by playing in-game contents.</font></p>\r\n      <p><br>Players can purchase various crafting items, and consumeable items using Medal of Valor.</p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"16314-1\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>How to Earn</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>You can earn Medal of Valor by hunting boss monsters in the area below</p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n         <tbody>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Location</span></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">How</span></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Orim\'s Secret Lab</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">Obtain from Warlock Chest</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">The Secret of Crocodile Island</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">On Rossus Island</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Dream Island</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">Obtain from Nightmare Chest</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Clan Gathering Place</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">Atuba King<br>Ice Golem King<br>Hell Watcher<br>Stellaria<br>Dark Dragon Reaper</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Unicorn Temple (Normal/Boos)</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">Nine-Tailed Fox<br>Avish Azomdan</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Temple of Extreme Cold (Normal/Hard)</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">Ice Queen<br>Ice Demon<br>Ice Mambo Rabbit</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Infinite War</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">Atuba King<br>Enraged Balrog</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Auracia\'s Purification</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">Obtain from Auracia\'s Gift Box</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"16314-2\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Purchasing Items</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; clear: both;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/49/18/fb7844361279b6b6ea28583b.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">NPC Warga/Varga\'s located in Gludin Village</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/49/18/2d33303140438771484e4ce0.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">Items for Sale</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p>Varga, NPC in Gludin Village sells items that can be purchased with Medal of Valor</p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n         <tbody>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Name</span></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Effect</span></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Exchange Amount</span></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Info</span></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n    