(35, 'Battle of Windawood', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"16250-0\" style=\"padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" jhenghei\",=\"\" meiryo,=\"\" \"ms=\"\" pgothic\",=\"\" 돋움,=\"\" dotum,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n   <p><font style=\"font-size: 20px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">A fierce battle unfolds! <br>Huge tax and exclusive raids for the winning team.</span></font></p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <p>The Battle of Windawood last 40 minutes, players who take ownership of the Guardian Tower will be rewarded with tax revenue and exclusive raids in the area.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"16250-1\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" jhenghei\",=\"\" meiryo,=\"\" \"ms=\"\" pgothic\",=\"\" 돋움,=\"\" dotum,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n   <h2>Features</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n   <p>- Characters of level 85 or higher can participate.<br>- 6~7 servers are matched, and the character is placed as one of the 3 knights when entering.<br>- When entering, the character name will be displayed anonymously, and exclusive transformations according to normal/ranker and combat enhancement buffs will be provided according to the level.<br>- At 20:00, the Battle of Windawood begins, and the capture will be judged based on the destruction of the central guard tower.<br>- When determining whether or not to occupy, the knight group with the most alive characters within the five occupied zones succeeds in occupying the area.<br>- All four buff towers placed around the central area will be taken over by the Knights who destroyed the buff towers last.<br>- After the end of the conquest battle, a dedicated raid will be opened that only the final winning team\'s camp can enter.<br>- Taxes are distributed differentially to knights who win the occupation war according to the number of medals, and they are provided with the opportunity to acquire legendary weapons and skills through exclusive raids.</p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"16250-2\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" jhenghei\",=\"\" meiryo,=\"\" \"ms=\"\" pgothic\",=\"\" 돋움,=\"\" dotum,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n   <h2>Battle of Windawood Rules</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n   <p>When you enter, regardless of the server you belong to, you will be randomly assigned among the three knights and fight for the victory of the knights.</p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n      <tbody>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/64/30/68676c867c5da9cc6661ae84.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/52/63/aca97542bd614a9aa9ad369f.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/89/10/3cc1728b1a02f85bfa84a412.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Black Knights</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Red Knights</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Gold Knights</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n      </tbody>\r\n   </table>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <p>Battle of Windawood is conducted in the same manner as the Heine Guard Tower for active combat.</p>\r\n   <p><br><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">1.  Anonymous System</span>: All character names are anonymous<br><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">2. Polymorph System</span>: All characters will be played as unique transformations for each class, and some rankers will be given the opportunity to transform into rankers.<br>(Even if you are currently a ranker on your own server, you may not be eligible for the Ranker forced transformation condition because the criteria are different in Heine Guard Tower .)<br><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">3. Enchantments</span>: Exclusive enchantments will be provided so everyone can participate in the battle together.<br></p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; clear: both;\">\r\n      <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n         <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/94/87/52c188bce43d8bcb839b32d3.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n         <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">All partpicators names are named anonymous</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n         <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/94/87/108668b3f99a63c87bea2ba5.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n         <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">Unique polymorph is provided according to characters rank.</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <br>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"16250-3\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" jhenghei\",=\"\" meiryo,=\"\" \"ms=\"\" pgothic\",=\"\" 돋움,=\"\" dotum,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n   <h2>How to Enter</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n   <p>Starting at 19:30 every Sunday, anyone level 85 or higher can enter the Windowood Conquest Battleground.<br>Possible to also teleport via event notification or rifts.</p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; clear: both;\">\r\n      <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n         <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/62/65/2cc82aa134fa045071de59df.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n         <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">You can teleport to entry area through the event notifications.</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n         <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/62/65/7507032f75e76b88b34ef566.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n         <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">You can enter Battle of Windawood via rift/crack.</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <br>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"16250-4\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" jhenghei\",=\"\" meiryo,=\"\" \"ms=\"\" pgothic\",=\"\" 돋움,=\"\" dotum,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n   <h2>Forming Party</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n   <p>As with the Heine Guard Tower , characters who are assigned to the same \"Knight Corps\" can form a party with each other.<br>You can not join a party anonymously, when inviting a party, you must directly invite using the target\'s character name such as /invite XXX.<br>Characters from other servers can also join a party if they belong to the same Knight Corp. In this case, the person to be invited can be invited using ‘/invite (first 2 letters of server) character name’.</p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n      <tbody>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td class=\"box1 width600\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n               <p>Example: When inviting the \'Lamaba\' character from the Depologge server who is in the same Knight Corp as yourself.</p>\r\n               <p><br></p>\r\n               <p>/invite (depo)lamaba</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n      </tbody>\r\n   </table>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <p>However, if the setting is set to \'Auto Distribution\' when inviting a party, it may be automatically distributed when raid rewards are dropped later, so be careful when joining a party.<br><br></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"16250-5\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" jhenghei\",=\"\" meiryo,=\"\" \"ms=\"\" pgothic\",=\"\" 돋움,=\"\" dotum,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n   <h2>Battlefield Structure</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n   <p>When you enter the Battle of Windawood, you will start from each faction of the Knight Corp.<br>There is a total of 1 central area in the capture area, but in addition to the guard tower, there are 4 buff towers that provide useful buffs for occupying the control area.<br>However, unlike the Heine Guard Tower , the Knight\'s camp is adjacent to each other, and in order to advance to the Guardian Tower and the Buff Tower, you need to move through a passage that consists of a single path.<br>In addition, there are various terrains/features in the passage, so various strategies and tactics are required before entering the occupied area.</p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <p><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/81/53/631ebebb17eeaba080c45651.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"16250-6\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" jhenghei\",=\"\" meiryo,=\"\" \"ms=\"\" pgothic\",=\"\" 돋움,=\"\" dotum,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n   <h2>Capturing Windawood</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n   <p>When you enter the Battle of Windawood, you will start from each faction of the Knights Corp.</p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <p>The battle begins at 8pm and last for 40 minutes.<br>The moment the Guardian Tower is destroyed, the Knights with the most surviving players in the Guardian Tower control area will succeed in capturing it, and the Knights will be rewarded with \"Battlefield Loot\" that can obtain up to 100 Dragon Diamonds.</p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; clear: both;\">\r\n      <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n         <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/58/33/3151a5a61b0b9a6f99f9de3b.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n         <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">You can see which Corp is dominant via global chat.</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n         <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/58/33/c8cc3d18fcd46a447c3259d9.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n         <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">When the Guardian Tower is destroyed, additional missions are assigned based on Win/Lose.</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <p>[Capture Rewards]</p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n      <tbody>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Name</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Usage Effect</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/67/97/fe2308a23992e047b675482c.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Spoils of Battle</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p>When used, obtain 10~100 Dragon Diamonds (Engraved)(Probability)</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n      </tbody>\r\n   </table>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p>When the Guardain Tower is destroyed, additional mission is given: Winning side needs to complete within 3 minutes, and lossing side complete within 10 minutes.<br>If you complete the mission, you can get a \"Loot Box\" which contains EXP Pure Elixir.</p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <p>[Mission Rewards]<br></p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n      <tbody>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Name</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Mission</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Usage Effect</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/10/66/e32df1c0b3167ae1c9768193.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Usurper\'s Spoils<br>Guardian\'s Trophy</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Siege: Attack within 3 minutes.<br>Defend: More than 10 minutes.</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p>When used,<br>Pure Elixir(EXP)</p>\r\n               <p>200 Guardian Health Potions<br>20 Eden\'s Mana Potion<br>10 Guardian Red Pearls</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n      </tbody>\r\n   </table>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <br>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"16250-7\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" jhenghei\",=\"\" meiryo,=\"\" \"ms=\"\" pgothic\",=\"\" 돋움,=\"\" dotum,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n   <h2>Buff Top Strategy</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n   <p>4 Buff Towers are placed around the central area are very important, which can create a siege variable.  The buff towers can only be attacked by besieging side and the moment the buff tower is destoryed by the Knight fraction obtains the buff.<br>Once broken, the buff tower will be rebuilt together after the central guard tower is destroyed, so it\'s important to use it strategically.</p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; clear: both;\">\r\n      <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n         <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/67/81/d992b94e40c58760e2490256.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n         <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">Buff towers are located in 4 places in the east, west, north, and south around the Guardian Tower control area.</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n         <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/67/81/5961fa1498d69f4b8ae5e142.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n         <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">The moment you occupy the buff tower, a message is displayed on the screen.</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <p>When buff tower is destoryed a message will appear on the screen, <br>the buff is applied to the fraction that destroyed it.<br></p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n      <tbody>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">North Tower</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">East Tower</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">South Tower</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">West Tower</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">HP +1000, MP +200<br>Ememy fraction AoE Damage</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">AoE debuff to enemey fraction<br>(reduce melee damage)</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Speed Increase<br>Random return of enemey fraction in the centeral area</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Ignore PVP Damage Reduction</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n      </tbody>\r\n   </table>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"16250-8\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" jhenghei\",=\"\" meiryo,=\"\" \"ms=\"\" pgothic\",=\"\" 돋움,=\"\" dotum,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n   <h2>Knight\'s Medal</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n   <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">1. Preoccupation Taxes</span><br>During the battle, medals are awarded to the fractions in the occupied area every minute as basis for distribution.<br>The winning fraction will be awarded 1.2 billion adena, depending on the number of medals they hold.</p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n      <tbody>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/71/27/0afbf1ed1a0d715548c4b0fe.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/71/45/530066d2a3656f018a08faec.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/61/12/01fab4872da1babe525aee72.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Black Knight Medal</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Red Knight Medal</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Gold Knight Medal</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n      </tbody>\r\n   </table>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <p>Fraction medals can only be obtained in three cases:</p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n      <tbody>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Knight\'s Medal Heist</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Capture Zone Keeper</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Capture Buff Towers</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">When you kill enemy in the battlefield, <br>1 medal is awarded to the killer, <br> defeated player will lose 1 medal.</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Every minute a medal is awarded,</p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">to the fraction controlling the Guardian Tower.<br></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">3 medals are awarded to the fraction player</p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">who destroys the buff tower and to nearby allies.</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n      </tbody>\r\n   </table>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <p>You can not earn medals by defeating the same fraction twice, nor defeating a player with only 0-1 medals.<br></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"16250-9\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" jhenghei\",=\"\" meiryo,=\"\" \"ms=\"\" pgothic\",=\"\" 돋움,=\"\" dotum,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n   <h2>Diving Penalty</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\">\r\n      <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right;\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/64/14/d955c704b014cc31240dd258.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\"></div>\r\n      <br>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p>The diving penalty is a penalty that reduces the amount of Medals that you earned if you do not actively play after participating in the Battle of Windawood.</p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <p>Penalties are awarded at each fractions\'s starting area after the start of Battle of Windawood, and are counted before the penalty is applied.</p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <p><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/77/39/101234feba8d4f1dc16dc731.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <p><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/40/67/0f873107ac0892b2ee298410.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <p>The penalty timer is given a total of 2 minutes, as shown in the figure above, and 1 penalty is reduced after 2 minutes.<br>From then on, the time remaining until the penalty is continuously added by 1 minute, and each minute that passes is reduced by 1 medal.</p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <p>However, if a user does not have any medals, the number of medals will not be reduced even if the penalty is applied, and the penalty timer will be reset if the player leaves the fraction waiting area.<br><br></p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"16250-10\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" jhenghei\",=\"\" meiryo,=\"\" \"ms=\"\" pgothic\",=\"\" 돋움,=\"\" dotum,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n   <h2>Exclusive Raids</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n   <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">1. Exclusive Raid Entry</span><br>Starting at 20:40, the victorious fraction with at least one Medal will be granted access to Azur, Lord of Windawood.<br>You can enter the Windawood Castle through the portal at 11 o\'clock based on the central area and proceed with the raid.<br>For 20 minutes, the winning fraction can move freely, and when attacking Azur, the lord of the castle, they will have a chance to obtain legendary weapons and skills, including Adena.</p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; clear: both;\">\r\n      <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n         <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/81/94/adba126d3d4203bb8f533e9f.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n         <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">You can enter through the portal located at 11 o\'clock in the central area.</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n         <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/81/94/d2c791c795f00e55aac70958.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n         <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">When capturing, you can get legendary items, including Adena.</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">2. Boss Monster Reward</span></p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n      <tbody>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Boss</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Major Rewards</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/73/99/ca2a6b4a9e0380e00c45242f.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Windawood Castle Lord Azur</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\">Red Shadow Edoryu</font><br><font color=\"#c38b61\">Spearbook (Pressure Death Recall)</font><br><font color=\"#c38b61\">Spearbook (Cruel Conviction)</font><br><font color=\"#c38b61\">Spearbook (Recovery)</font><br><font color=\"#c38b61\">Spearbook (Maelstrom)</font><br><font color=\"#c38b61\">Spearbook (Increment Range)</font><br><font color=\"#c38b61\">Fencerbook (Phantom Death)</font><br><font color=\"#c38b61\">Fencerbook (Pantera Shock)</font><br><font color=\"#c38b61\">Fencerbook (Phantom Requiem)</font><br><font color=\"#c38b61\">Fencerbook (Phantom Reaper)</font><br><font color=\"#c38b61\">Black Spirit Crystal (Avenger)</font><br><font color=\"#c38b61\">Technical Book (Counter Barrier Master)</font><br><font color=\"#c38b61\">Technical Book (Raging Weapon)</font><br><font color=\"#c38b61\">Technical Book (Shock Attack)</font><br><font color=\"#c38b61\">Black Spirit Crystal (Moving Acceleration Max)</font><br><font color=\"#c38b61\">Black Spirit Crystal (Shadow Armor Destiny)</font><br><font color=\"#c38b61\">Black Spirit Crystal (Armor Break Destiny)</font><br><font color=\"#c38b61\">Spirit Crystal (Burning Show)</font><br><font color=\"#c38b61\">Spirit Crystal (Soul Barrier Armor)</font><br><font color=\"#c38b61\">Spirit Crystal (Striker Gale Shot)</font><br></td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n      </tbody>\r\n   </table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '/upload/2021\\09\\13/002_134.jpg', 'true', 'true');
