\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Changes in STR values and stats</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>The following is a table of changes in the character\'s stats according to STR.</p>\r\n      <p>This table does not apply the pure STR bonus value of the character, so you need to be careful when applying it to each character.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>ex)</p>\r\n      <p>If the character has a total STR of 51 with pure STR of 39 + equipment STR of 13, the final ability value can be obtained by adding the pure STR bonus to the STR value of 51 in the table below.</p>\r\n      <p>Therefore, if you add the bonus for exceeding pure STR 35 (close range damage +2, Melee Hit +2) to the basic ability value of STR 51 (close range damage 23, Melee Hit 34, Melee Crit 2%), the final ability value is close range damage 25, Melee Hit. 36, Melee Crit 2% effect.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img_left\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/27/84/69e5878de427aaf4e353260a.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\"></div>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"5890-3\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Related Abilities</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>As STR increases, the following abilities increase.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>&#8594;<font color=\"#c38b61\">Melee Damage </font>: Damage when melee attack is preformed.  The higher the value, the more damage you will do.</p>\r\n      <p>&#8594;<font color=\"#c38b61\">Melee Hit </font>: Probability of hitting your opponent.  The higher the value, the better chance of landing a blow.</p>\r\n      <p>&#8594;<font color=\"#c38b61\">Melee Crit </font>: Inflicting bonus damage, the higher the value the better chance of landing a critical blow.</p>\r\n      <p>&#8594;<font color=\"#c38b61\">Carrying Weight</font>: Maxium weight you can carry.  Higher the value, more you can carry.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"5890-4\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>STR Magic</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>In Lineage, there is magic that increases STR.</p>\r\n      <p>Through these spells, players can increase their melee attack power by increasing the STR of themselves or their party members or clan members.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>The following are magic you can use to increase you STR</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <section class=\"list list-item\">\r\n         <table style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; width: 1260px;\">\r\n            <caption style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\"></caption>\r\n            <thead style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">\r\n               <tr style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">\r\n                  <th scope=\"col\" class=\"list__header-label\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">Name</th>\r\n                  <th scope=\"col\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">Type</th>\r\n                  <th scope=\"col\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">MP</th>\r\n                  <th scope=\"col\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">HP</th>\r\n                  <th scope=\"col\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">Magic Mat</th>\r\n                  <th scope=\"col\" style=\"outline-style: 