ss=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Change in stats based on INT</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>The following is a table of the changes in the character\'s stats according to INT.</p>\r\n      <p>This table does not apply the pure INT bonus value of the character, so you need to be careful when applying it to each character.</p>\r\n      <p>Also, please note that wizards and illusionists receive a magic bonus +1 when creating characters.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>ex)</p>\r\n      <p>If the character has a total INT of 51 with pure INT 39 + equipment INT 13, the final ability value is obtained by adding the pure INT bonus to the INT 51 value in the table below.</p>\r\n      <p>Therefore, if you add the bonus (Magic Damage +2, Magic Hit +2) for exceeding pure INT 35 to the basic ability value of INT 51 (Magic Damage 8, Magic Hit 10, Magic Crit 1%), the final ability value is Magic Damage 10, Magic Hit. 12, obtains a magic critical hit effect of 1%.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\">\r\n         <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\">\r\n            <div class=\"img_left\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/99/35/2e378c73ae30fbad10a11488.png\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\"></div>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"5893-3\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Related Stats</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>As INT increases, the following stats increase:</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>&#8594;<font color=\"#c38b61\">Magic Bonus</font> (MB): Higher value means higher damage from spells and higher regenration rate.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>&#8594;<font color=\"#c38b61\">Magic Damage </font>: Higher value more damage from spells</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>&#8594;<font color=\"#c38b61\">Magic Hit </font>: Rate of which magic hits, higher the value, the higher chance of magic will succeed (Ex. Turn Undead)</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>&#8594;<font color=\"#c38b61\">Magic Crit </font> : Higher chance of applying 1.5x spell damage</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>&#8594;<font color=\"#c38b61\">MP Usage</font> : Reduces the cost of mana required to use the spell.  Higher value, the less mana required.  </p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>', '/upload/2021\\09\\13/001_12.jpg', 'false', 'false');
INSERT INTO `app_powerbook` (`id`, `title`, `content`, `mainImg`, `main`, `guideMain`) VALUES
(39, 'WIS', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"5892-0\" style=\"padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>Stats that affect the character\'s MP growth, MP recovery, and MR.</p>\r\n      <p>Classes that mainly use magic often increase their WIS to a certain level from the low level to gain MP when resetting their stats.</p>\r\n      <p>It is also a stat that affects the growth of MR, which reduces the damage of attack magic.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>Meanwhile, in the case of the Dark Elf class, it is also a factor that determines the success rate of the Bring Stone, which creates Obsidian, a catalyst needed to use magic. For this reason, there are cases where you create a sub-character that only makes obsidian by raising WIS.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"5892-1\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Related Stats</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>As the WIS increases, the following stats increase:</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>&#8594;<font color=\"#c38b61\">Increase Mana Points</font>: As you level up the amount mana points increases.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>&#8594;<font color=\"#c38b61\">Mana Recovery </font>: The ability to restore mana points naturally</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>&#8594;<font color=\"#c38b61\">Mana Potion Recovery</font>: The ability to increase the amount of mana points recovered when using mana potions.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>&#8594;<font color=\"#c38b61\">Magic Resistances (MR)</font>: The ability to reduce incoming magic attacks</p>\r\n   </div