(40, 'DEX', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"5895-0\" style=\"padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>Stats that relates to range attacks, AC, and Evasion (ER)</p>\r\n      <p>Elfves who mainly use range weapons are consider the main class</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"5895-1\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Abilites</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>As DEX increases, the following abilities increases</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>&#8594;<font color=\"#c38b61\"><b>Range Damage</b> </font>: Damage from range attacks such as bows or throwing swords.  The higher the number, the more damaage you can inflict to your target.</p>\r\n      <p>&#8594;<font color=\"#c38b61\"><b>Range Hit</b> </font>: Chance of hitting your target with range attack such as bow or throwing swords.  The higher the value, the higher the chance that range attacks will hit.</p>\r\n      <p>&#8594;<font color=\"#c38b61\"><b>Range Crit</b> </font>: Chance of inflicting maximum damage to opponent with range attack.  The higher the value, the higher chance to crit.</p>\r\n      <p>&#8594;<font color=\"#c38b61\"><b>AC</b> </font>(Melee Defense): Chance of avoiding an opponent\'s attack.  The lower the value, the higher the chance of avoiding the opponent\'s melee attack.</p>\r\n      <p>&#8594;<font color=\"#c38b61\"><b>ER</b> </font>(Evasion): Probability of avoiding an opponent\'s range attack.  The higher the value, the higher the chance of avoiding an opponent\'s range attack.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"5895-2\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Stat Bonus</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>If you grow your DEX to 25, 35, or 45 with pure stats, you will get the following stat bonuses:</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>For example, if you raise your DEX to 36 with pure stats, you will get the stat bonus of DEX 25 + the stat bonus of DEX 35 at the same time, and finally you will get Range Damage +2 and Range Hit +2.</p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n         <tbody>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td class=\"cel1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Stat</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"cel1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">12</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"cel1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">25</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"cel1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">35</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"cel1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rg