(42, 'Monarch', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"6-0\" style=\"padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      The monarch is the only class that can create a clan, which is Lineage\'s guild system, and has differentiated rights such as participating in siege wars and auctions through the clan they created. On the other hand, monster hunting and PvP skills, which are essential for leveling up, are the worst.</font>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p><font color=\"#000000\"></font></p>\r\n      <p><font color=\"#000000\">In fact, when compared to a Knight with a similar hunting pattern at the same level and wearing the same equipment, the hunting speed is much slower. So, it is common to prepare +6~7 level weapons, +4~5 (6~7) level armor, and sufficient potion costs before selecting it as the second or third character.</font></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"6-1\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Feature</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>&#8594; The only class that can create a clan, clan wars, and house auctions can be used<br>&#8594; Among all classes, hunting and PvP skills are the worst.<br>&#8594; Recommended to prepare weapon, armor, and potions in advance before playing this class<br>&#8594; Starting at level 60, PVP Damage Reduction +1 every 3 levels</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"6-2\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Equipment</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>&#8594; You can wear most daggers, one-handed swords, blunt spears, and some bows as ranged weapons.<br>&#8594; They wear armor almost similar to that of a knight, and can also use shields and guarder<br>&#8594; Monarch-exclusive helmet: When you wear the popular Horseback Helmet, you will be on horse and your movement speed will increase. However, only spears can be worn as weapons.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"6-3\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Monarch Magic</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>Monarch can use up to level 2 of normal magic along side their own magic used for clans. In addition to this, you can also use certain magic by wearing helmets, similar to the knight class.</font></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"6-4\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Clans</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n         <tbody>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td class=\"box1 width600\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p>Monarch can create a clan starting at level 15, and with this, they will have access to clan warehouse.</p>\r\n                  <p>With this, you can create a level 15 monarch, and solo use it for clan warehouse.</p>\r\n                  <p></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <table style=\"margin-left: 10px; float: right;\">\r\n         <tbody>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/55/89/1c6be9d4eea26bb9f31fede0.jpg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>A monarch can create a clan when he or she reaches level 15. After talking to the clan executive in each village, pay 30,000 adena and click “Create a clan.”</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>Once you create a clan, you can recruit members by encouraging people who have not yet joined the clan to join the clan or by promoting it.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>', '/upload/2021/09/16/POWERBOOK_42_51902765-b3f0-4d64-ad38-fcdfdb0e5f30447b162ab9f4fbb25439ee57.jpg', 'false', 'false'),
(43, 'Knight', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"20-0\" style=\"padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>The knight is the class with the most HP among all classes in Lineage, and can have above-average attack and defense power through a variety of equipment.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>In addition, compared to other classes, leveling up is also advantageous as you can use Haste2 (speed-up potion potion) relatively cheaply. Additionally, the controls are relatively easy, so it is a class often chosen by beginners who are just starting out with Lineage.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"20-1\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Feature</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>&#8594; Overwhelming HP.<br>&#8594; Able to wear the widest variety of items among all classes.<br>&#8594; Inexpensive Haste2 (Potion of Speed, Potion of Courage).<br>&#8594; Uses various skills specialized for two-handed swords.<br>&#8594; Highly dependent on equipment and potions.<br>&#8594; From level 60, PvP Damage Reduction increases by +1 per level +2.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"20-2\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Equipment</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>&#8594; Can wear almost any weapon.<br>&#8594; However, there are many skills that can only be used when wearing a two-handed sword, such as Counter Barrier, so two-handed swords are the trend<br>&#8594; As for armor, most types of armor can be worn, including shields and guarder.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"20-3\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Skills</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>&#8594; Starting at level 50, Knights can learn normal magic level 1, and Knight\'s exclusive skills<br>&#8594; Can equip magic helmet\'s to get magic before level 50<br>&#8594; Please see Knight\'s Skill for details</font></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>', '/upload/2021/09/16/POWERBOOK_43_0197971a-8cd4-4a33-8982-421eadb992c4b7f2570d832fafe2ae6ca0ea.jpg', 'false', 'false'),
(44, 'Elf', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"34-0\" style=\"padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>Elves are the class with the most variety among all classes. To put it in one word, it can be said to be an all-round class. It is also the easiest class to level up in the early stages as it specializes in long-distance attacks using a bow.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>In addition, it has features such as elven magic, which is a elven magic system, and elven creation.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"34-1\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Feature</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>&#8594; Main stat is DEX that focuses on long range and bow attack speed which is fastest from other classes<br>&#8594; You can play in different playstyle depending on how you spend you STAT points and selected Spirit Magic<br>&#8594; Using up to level 6 normal magic and Elf\'s unique Elemental Magic, various roles are possible, such as Recovery, Attack or Support<br>&#8594; There are certain items that only the Elf class can craft<br>&#8594; From level 60, PVP Damage Reduction increases by +1 every 4 levels</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"34-2\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Elemental Magic</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/84/97/5f188081184957d9b16f70eb.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">If you remove elemental magic, all magic will disappear!!</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p>A unique magic used by Elves</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>You can learn them from level 10 and can be classified into a total of 5 elementals: Common, Earth, Water, Fire, and Wind</p>\r\n      <p>Depending on which elemental you select, the magic you will use vary and futhermore, the choice of weapon and armor will be different</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>For more information see Elemental Magic page</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"34-3\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Normal Magic</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>Elves can learn normal magic every 10 levels, and can ultimately use it up to level 6 (level60)</p>\r\n      <p>Since spell power is on the lower end, magic will not is very efficient, unless you specialize in INT Elf</p>\r\n      <p>Therefore in normal magic, buff-type magic are mainly used such as Holy Weapon, and Enchant DEX</p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"34-4\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Item Crafting</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <table style=\"margin-left: 10px; float: right;\">\r\n         <tbody>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/84/87/10394a2bf9990680b8ba7985.jpg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td class=\"caption\">\r\n                  <p><font color=\"#000000\">&#8593; Nerupa, who crafts</font><br><font color=\"#000000\"> final elven items</font></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>Only Elves can craft certain items, and this is called \"Elven Crafting\"</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>You can also use the Forest Guardians to craft items for you such as Pan, Arachne, Fairies, and Neruffa.  They are found throughout the Elven Forest, and can help you with crafting items such as Elm\'s Blessing, and Timble Power Glove.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>', '/upload/2021/09/16/POWERBOOK_44_da71fe60-2713-45fb-b482-ee0d562e34216c292695834ae506c0005320.jpg', 'false', 'false'),
(45, 'Wizard', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"35-0\" style=\"padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>The wizard of Lineage is slightly different from the traditional wizard class that uses flashy and powerful magic to wipe out monsters.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>If I had to describe the wizard of Lineage in one word, it would be a \'magic swordsman\'. Understanding it as a mix of offensive magic and physical attacks will help you understand this class.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"35-1\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Feature</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>&#8594; Because it has high INT and SP, its magic effects are superior to other classes.</p>\r\n      <p>&#8594; On the other hand, it has low HP and a lot of restrictions on the armor you wear, so it is difficult to raise the AC.</p>\r\n      <p>&#8594; Can use up to 10 levels of normal magic.</p>\r\n      <p>&#8594; Depending on how you distribute your base stats, your play pattern will vary greatly.</p>\r\n      <p>&#8594; From level 60, PvP Damage Reduction increases by +1 every 4 levels.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"35-2\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Equipment</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>&#8594; Main weapons: Staff and Daggers</p>\r\n      <p>&#8594; Compared to other class, wears less armor</p>\r\n      <p>&#8594; Since you will be using alot of magic, MP recovery items are very important</p>\r\n      <p>&#8594; In safe zone, you can equiped MP recovery items to regen mana</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"35-3\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Magic</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/65/89/4840391199348b823abd89bc.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">The only class to use best offensive and recovery magic skils</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p>Only class that can learn all 10 level or normal magic.  Can learn magic every 8 levels.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>Two common ways to play the Wizard class is either by \"Turn Undead\" (killing undead monsters with single blow by using spell \"Turn Undead\") or by luring serveral monsters into one place and then attacking them with a ranged spell like Fireball.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"35-4\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Hunting Style - Turn Undead</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/23/54/b561a00de550d9fce081aa74.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">One way to play the Wizard</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p>Wizard Hunting - Using Turn Undead Magic</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>When undead monster are hit with spell \"Turn Undead\" it has a certain probability to die in one hit, regardless of remaining HP.  Using this playstyle, you can hunt area where undead monsters spawn.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>Since the spell is casted from a distance, there is low risk of being attacked, and it works on relatively high level monsters.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"35-5\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Hunting Style - Sheepdog</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/17/39/3739bedbce2144549b6c60d7.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">It is necessary to understand the structure of the hunting ground and control it to some extent to know how to hunt safely.</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p>A hunting method that draws monsters around and makes them follow you, and when a certain number of them are collected, attack the monsters that have gathered together with area attack magic.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>As you have to keep the monsters behind you and run away until the monsters are gathered, items and spells that increase movement speed are essential. Also, if you try it in a narrow place like a dungeon, you may lie down in an instant, so you need to be careful.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>Few spells you can use <font color=\"#c38b61\">Tornado</font>, <font color=\"#c38b61\"> Fireball</font>, <font color=\"#c38b61\"> Lightning Storm</font> for this method of playstyle. Keep in mind, the elemental use of spell in this case.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>', '/upload/2021/09/16/POWERBOOK_45_b964f38d-c9ef-48b2-9db1-d36e86edad21c1ec713474c5d7cf33434770.jpg', 'false', 'false'),
(46, 'Dark Elf', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"36-0\" style=\"padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>If I had to describe a dark elf in one word, it would be a <font color=\"#000000\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">\"typical assassin class\"</span></font>.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>Physical attacks are generally powerful, and its exclusive weapon, Idoryu, has a chance to deal powerful damage to opponents, <font color=\"#c38b61\">Edoryu</font> and <font color=\"#c38b61\">Claws</font> has a chance to deal powerful damage to opponents. In addition, it can inflict maximum damage in a short period of time, such as being able to temporarily increase its attack power with its unique magic method, <font color=\"#c38b61\">Dark Spirit Magic.</font></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>On the other hand, it has a lower HP and MR than other classes, so it is more likely to be in danger.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"36-1\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Features</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>&#10003; Offensive class<br>&#10003; Only class that can set STR and DEX to 18<br>&#10003; Exclusive weapon: Edoryu & Claws yeild powerful attacks<br>&#10003; Can use Dark Spirit Magic to aid in combat and enchance attacks<br>&#10003; Items ingame that only Dark Elf\'s can craft<br>&#10003; From level 60, PVP Damage Reduction is increased by +1 every 3 levels</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"36-2\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Equipment</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>&#10003; Exclusive weapon: Edoryu & Claws<br>&#10003; Edoryu has certain probability to cause double damage<br>&#10003; Claws triggers critical hit that applies the maxium weapon damage value<br>&#10003; While damage output is hight, the HP and MR are a bit on the low side</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"36-3\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Dark Spirit Magic</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>&#10003; Exlusive magic that only Dark Elfs can use<br>&#10003; Starting from level 15, you can learn Dark Spirit Magic as you level up..30, 45, and 60<br>&#10003; Magic are mainly buff type that aid in combat and some spells require the use of \"Obsidian\"<br>&#10003; More details can be found on Dark Spirit Magic page<br>&#10003; Additionally you can learn up to two levels of general magic (Level 1 & Level 2)</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"36-4\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Dark Elf Crafting</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>There are unique items that only dark elves can make.</p>\r\n      <p>For example, the Bring Stone, which is a catalyst for using Dark Spirit magic, Black King and the Black King\'s Child, the best weapons of the Dark Elves, can also be obtained by crafting.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>For more information, please refer to the Dark Elf crafting page.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>', '/upload/2021/09/16/POWERBOOK_46_4a3880a2-34bb-4143-90ca-67169a19bc5bbf1abaa874a7de2cc740ed86.jpg', 'false', 'false'),
(47, 'Dragon Knight', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"4818-0\" style=\"padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>Dragon Knight is a new class introduced in Season 3, has features that differentiate it from existing classes, such as it\'s own Dragon Knight magic with unique system that and chainsword exclusive weapon.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>In terms of ability, this class has similar personality somewhat between Knight and Dark Elf.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>Primarily stats for this class is STR and CON similar to the Knight class.</p>\r\n      <p>The ability to strengthen oneself through equipment settings or personall buffs that focus on attack rather then defense is similar to the Dark Elf.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"4818-1\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Feature</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>&#8594; STR & CON<br>&#8594; Use exclusive Dragon Knight Magic<br>&#8594; Can use One-Handed Swords, Two-Handed Swords, Blunt Weapons, Gauntlets, and it\'s exclusive weapon Chainsword<br>&#8594; The attack speed of two-handed weapon is faster then any other class<br>&#8594; If you use chainsword as dedicated weapon, you will receive a bonus of exposing weakness<br>&#8594; From level 60, PVP Damage Reduction increase by +1 every 3 levels<br>&#8594; (From level 92, PVP Damage Reduction increases by +1 every level)</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"4818-2\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Dragon Knight Magic</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <table style=\"margin-left: 10px; float: right;\">\r\n         <tbody>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/40/56/e37f8af6b09f149d20116be4.jpg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td class=\"caption\">\r\n                  <p><font color=\"#000000\">Burning Slash boasts exciting effects</font></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>Dragon Knight has there own exclusive magic to use.</p>\r\n      <p>Many including offensive type of magic which increases your abilities and in some cases HP is consumed along with MP when used.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>Dragon Knight magic can be bought by NPC selling magic, or by acquiring Tablets obtaiing through hunting.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>The types of magic can be found on Dragon Knight Magic page.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"4818-3\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Chainsword</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <table style=\"margin-left: 10px; float: right;\">\r\n         <tbody>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/69/72/a84395f12df48f934fbe880f.jpg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td class=\"caption\">\r\n                  <p>An extending weapon, that covers up to 2 cells.</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>Dragon Knight uses a new concept weapon called the chainsword as its exclusive weapon. This item is a weapon that seems to combine the characteristics of an existing two-handed sword and a spear, and its characteristics are as follows.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Feature</span></p>\r\n      <p>&#8594; Range of 2 cells, useful for preemptive attacks<br>&#8594; Exposes Weakness is applied when attacking with the Chainsword<br>&#8594; If attack your target with \"exposed weakness\" with Dragon Knight\'s exclusive magic \"Foe Slayer\" you can deal additional damage +40</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>', '/upload/2021/09/16/POWERBOOK_47_cd20f15b-232f-4fd4-a897-f804b8eee702c60a951b80d74ca00c81c6c9.jpg', 'false', 'false');
INSERT INTO `app_powerbook` (`id`, `title`, `content`, `mainImg`, `main`, `guideMain`) VALUES
(48, 'Illusionist', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"4839-0\" style=\"padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>Illusionist, a new class that appeared along with Dragon Knight in Season 3.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>While the Dragon Knight shows outstanding abilities in soloing like existing classes, the illusionist has the abilities that are essential in a party.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"4839-1\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Feature</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>&#8594; Fight in melee range using blunts, staffs, and exclusive weapon Kiringku<br>&#8594; Increase own stats while at the same decrease target\'s stats<br>&#8594; Cube-type magic, a dedicated magic has differenct buffs for allies and enemies<br>&#8594; Kiringku, exclusive weapon, inflicts Magic Damage to target, damage is reduced depending on target\'s MR.<br>&#8594; Starting at level 60, PvP Damage Reduction +1 every 3 levels.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"4839-2\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Illusionist Magic</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <table style=\"margin-left: 10px; float: right;\">\r\n         <tbody>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/95/58/14cb3f07c7c0d0e34505343e.jpg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td class=\"caption\">\r\n                  <p><font color=\"#000000\">Panic, reduces targets stats for 60s</font></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>Illusionist has their own dedicated magic</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>Illusionist has more buff type magic, which can increase stats of class and allies, and cube-type magic that simultaneously gives positivies buff to allies and negative to enemies.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>Illusionist magic can be learned by purchasing it from shop or by hunting memory crystals.</p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Feature</span></p>\r\n      <p>&#8594; Illusionist magic can be learned starting at level 15, and every 15 levels you can learn more magic<br>&#8594; Uses Cube Magic which gives positive buffs to allies, and negative to enemeies<br>&#8594; Low damage, but uses magic that ignores the target\'s MR and Elemental Resistances.<br>&#8594; Elemental Stones are needed for some magic spells, which is sold by general stores in each village.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"4839-3\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Kiringku</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <table style=\"margin-left: 10px; float: right;\">\r\n         <tbody>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/82/76/0eca6c1600ccd3a057d6b8e3.jpg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td class=\"caption\">\r\n                  <p><font color=\"#000000\">&#8593; If you look above the character, you can <br>see the reality of Kiringku\'s attack.</font></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>The Illusionist\'s exclusive weapon, Kiringku, deals higher damage the higher the INT (Intelligence). As a result, it deals quite high damage compared to other weapons in the early game.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>However, since it is Magic Damage, the damage is reduced depending on the MR, and because of this, the damage efficiency tends to be lower as you go to the high-level hunting grounds.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>', '/upload/2021/09/16/POWERBOOK_48_39b8e719-8179-408d-87d8-d8f246537dec18c1e3a373fedf1a07d8aa24.jpg', 'false', 'false'),
(49, 'Fencer', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"14419-0\" style=\"padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>Fencer is class whose specialty is melee attacks.<br>Most knightly equipment such as daggers, one-handed swords, and two-handed swords can be worn, but they have skills that can only be activated when wearing a one-handed sword, so the use of one-handed swords is high.<br>In addition to this, you can enjoy various plays in PvP by continuously using skills with individual cool times.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"14419-1\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Feature</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>&#8594; It has a relatively high HP growth rate.<br>&#8594; Most weapons and armor are shared with knights.<br>&#8594; Can used Brave Potion to increase attack + movement speed<br>&#8594; Fencer is not affected by MR or Counter Magic, and its power increases based on the character\'s STR or the attack power of equipped weapon.<br>&#8594; Fencer skills are affected by the caster\'s fear hit and the target\'s Fear Resist.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"14419-2\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Equipment</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"clear: both; margin-bottom: 30px;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/98/70/187eb07eb0f7d1b46a9a3bd7.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">Some skills can only be used by one-handed sword</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/98/70/bb09827211e8b16b8d7fb768.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">Exclusive one-handed sword for Fencer</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p>One of the most important pieces of Fecner\'s equipment is a one-handed sword. There are skills that can only be used when wearing a one-handed sword.</p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Weapon</span></p>\r\n      <p>Can wear most weapons that a knight can wear, including daggers, one-handed swords, two-handed swords, blunt weapons, and spears. However, knight specialized equipment, Death Blade, is excluded.</p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p>Wear similar types of armor as knights. However, the Black Knight\'s Faceplate, which is knight-specific equipment, is excluded.</p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p>All accessories can be worn except for the accessory belt.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"14419-3\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Fencer Skills</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"clear: both; margin-bottom: 30px;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/51/56/0f257e663c3a378834153be7.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">Various Passive Skills</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/51/56/ee33ad25953d7bcdf5b733e5.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">Learning skills requires Fencer Book</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p>Fencer skills can only be learned by obtaining books through hunting or questing.  Some skills requires crystals to use, and some passive will auto consume crystals each time they are activated.</p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p>Details can be found on Fencer Skill Page</p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"14419-4\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Individual Cooldown</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>Biggest feature of Fencer Class</p>\r\n      <p>When existing classes use magic, they can use magic after a certain period of time (commonly known as cooldown). However, Fencer has a cooldown time set for each skill group, so Fencer magic that is not from the same group can be used continuously.</p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\"></span></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n         <tbody>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td class=\"box1 width600\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Group 1</span><br><font color=\"#c38b61\">Pantera</font></p>\r\n                  <p><br></p>\r\n                  <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Group 2</span><br><font color=\"#c38b61\">Blade</font></p>\r\n                  <p><br></p>\r\n                  <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Group 3</span><br><font color=\"#c38b61\"> Phantom</font>,<font color=\"#c38b61\"> Judgment</font>,<font color=\"#c38b61\"> Hellfire</font></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p>For example, the Panthera Phantom combo allows you to quickly approach an enemy and then render them unable to move. Alternatively, it is possible to use Judgment first, which lowers the four major resistances (fear/skill/word/spirit), and then use Pantera (Shock) in succession to increase the stun probability.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"14419-5\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Fencer Magic</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>The Fencer class can learn up two levels of normal magic (Level 1 at 15, and Level 2 at 30)</p>\r\n      <p>In addition, you can wear three Magic Helmets - Magic Helmet (Strength), Magic Helmet (Speed), Magic Helmet (Heal).</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>', '/upload/2021/09/16/POWERBOOK_49_0a48dd83-04fe-4f47-8c48-e623e4cc365b7cb4882a8cac28d3b2c47577.jpg', 'false', 'false');
