 initial; outline-width: 0px;\">If fails, both item and scroll disappears</td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n               <tr style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">\r\n                  <td class=\"list__header\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\"><img class=\"list__icon\" src=\"https://wstatic-cdn.plaync.com/powerbook/lineage/49/35/426f67862c9c8b76145b564b.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; display: inline-block; width: 40px; height: 40px; background-color: rgb(24, 20, 17);\"><span class=\"list__name\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"outline-style: initial;\"> DragonT Enchant Scroll (Cursed)</span></font></span></td>\r\n                  <td style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">When used on Dragon T-shirt, has a chance to decrease the enchant value by -1</td>\r\n                  <td class=\"list__desc\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">Can store in warehouse<br style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">If fails, both item and scroll disappears</td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n            </tbody>\r\n         </table>\r\n      </section>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>The Dragon T-Shirt can only be enchanted with the DragonT Enchant Scroll.</p>\r\n      <p>Enchant scrolls comes in 3 variouation (normal, bless, and cursed), Dragon T-shirt are safe up to +4 enchant</p>\r\n      <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\"></span></p>\r\n      <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Exchange Armor Enchant Scroll for DragonT Enchant Scroll</span></p>\r\n      <p>You can visit Stone Statue in Giran Village to trade Armor Enchant Scrolls for DragonT Enchant Scrolls</p>\r\n      <p>This is a great way to acquired bless or cursed enchant scrolls</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n         <tbody>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td class=\"box1 width600\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p></p>\r\n                  <p><font color=\"#c38b61\">Armor Enchant Scroll </font>(1) &#187;<font color=\"#c38b61\"> DragonT Enchant Scroll (Bless)</font> (1)</p>\r\n                  <p><font color=\"#c38b61\">Armor Enchant Scroll </font>(1) &#187;<font color=\"#c38b61\"> DragonT Enchant Scroll (Cursed)</font> (1)</p>\r\n                  <p></p>\r\n                  <p></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      \r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>또한판도라의 향수및 판도라의문양은 사용할 수 없다.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"13576-5\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Synthesis</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>You can craft <font color=\"#c38b61\">Bless Dragon T-shirt</font> by combining two Dragon T-shirt</p>\r\n      <p>However the following conditions are required</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n         <tbody>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td class=\"box1 width600\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p></p>\r\n                  <p>&#8594; Only Dragon T-shirt of the same type can be used</p>\r\n                  <p>&#8594; Only Dragon T-shirt with enchant level of +7 can be used</p>\r\n                  <p></p>\r\n                  <p>== Example</p>\r\n                  <p>+7<font color=\"#c38b61\"> Dragon T-shirt (Earth)</font> +7<font color=\"#c38b61\"> Dragon T-shirt (Wind)</font> = Not Possible</p>\r\n                  <p>+6<font color=\"#c38b61\"> Dragon T-shirt (Earth)</font> +6<font color=\"#c38b61\"> Dragon T-shirt (Earth)</font> = Not Possible</p>\r\n                  <p>+7<font color=\"#c38b61\"> Dragon T-shirt (Earth)</font> +7<font color=\"#c38b61\"> Dragon T-shirt (Earth)</font> = +7<font color=\"#c38b61\"> Bless Dragon T-shirt (Earth)</font></p>\r\n                  <p>+8<font color=\"#c38b61\"> Dragon T-shirt (Wind)</font> +8<font color=\"#c38b61\"> Dragon T-shirt (Wind)</font> = +8<font color=\"#c38b61\"> Bless Dragon T-shirt (Wind)</font></p>\r\n                  <p><br></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>참고로<font color=\"#ed1c24\">+6 이하의 용의 티셔츠는 축복과 일반의 옵션이 완전히 동일</font>하다.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"13576-6\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>기존 티셔츠와의 교환</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>+7 이상으로 인챈트한 기존 티셔츠는 기란 마을의 용의 티셔츠 석상에서봉인된 티셔츠 상자로 교환할 수 있다.</p>\r\n      <p>이렇게교환한<font color=\"#ed1c24\">봉인된 티셔츠 상자는 교환, 거래는 불가능</font>하나<font color=\"#ed1c24\">창고 저장은 가능</font>하기 때문에계정 내의 다른 캐릭터도 용의 티셔츠를 입을 수있다.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <section class=\"list list-item\">\r\n         <table style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; width: 1260px;\">\r\n            <caption style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">아이템 목록</caption>\r\n            <thead style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">\r\n               <tr style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px;\">\r\n       