er\">경우</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td class=\"cel_top\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">+7</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">+8</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">+9</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">+10</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">+11</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">상자 4개</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">상자 20개</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">상자 100개</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">상자 500개</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">상자 1500개</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">상자 7개</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">상자 35개</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">상자 160개</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">상자 800개</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">상자 2400개</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>단<font color=\"#c38b61\">티셔츠(아이템)</font>,<font color=\"#c38b61\">수련자의 티셔츠</font>,<font color=\"#c38b61\">요정족 티셔츠</font>,<font color=\"#c38b61\">야히의 티셔츠</font>,<font color=\"#c38b61\">실프의 티셔츠</font>등<span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\"><font color=\"#ed1c24\">일부 아이템은교환 대상에서 제외</font></span>된다.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"13576-7\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>설정</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>용의 티셔츠의 교환 및거래, 창고 저장 설정은 다음과 같다.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n         <tbody>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td class=\"cel1 width120\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\"></td>\r\n               <td class=\"cel1 width60\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">교환</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">거래</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"cel1 width60\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">창고</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">보관</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td class=\"cel_top\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p></p>\r\n                  <p>용의 티셔츠</p>\r\n                  <p></p>\r\n                  <p>티셔츠 상자</p>\r\n                  <p></p>\r\n                  <p>티셔츠 패키지</p>\r\n                  <p></p>\r\n                  <p>봉인된 티셔츠 상자</p>\r\n                  <p></p>\r\n                  <p>티셔츠 주문서</p>\r\n                  <p></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"cel_top\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">X</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">O</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">X</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">X</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">X</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"cel_top\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">X</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">O</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">X</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">O</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">O</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>표에서 알 수 있듯이 일반 상자는 교환, 거래, 창고 보관이 가능하나 봉인된 상자는 교환, 거래는 불가능하고 창고 보관만 가능하다.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>', '/upload/2021/09/27/POWERBOOK_50_35c91704-e921-447c-9d96-fd6bc01ce0195958135cf5fe51d171ed742e.jpg', 'false', 'false');
INSERT INTO `app_powerbook` (`id`, `title`, `content`, `mainImg`, `main`, `guideMain`) VALUES
(51, 'Full Moon Treasure Island', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"16355-0\" style=\"padding-top: 0px;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p><font style=\"font-size: 20px !important;\">A treasure island that is said to only show during a full moon, treasure excavation event with Moon Knight Gillian.</font><br>&nbsp;<br>Treasure Island appears near the waters of Heine.  Rumors has it that the island is full of treasure including consumable items, reinforced spells, rare weapon and rare skills.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"16355-1\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Purchase A Compass!</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/57/73/45810e4b18a45c38d8d8fe22.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">Buy Full Moon Compass from Atun</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p>A Compass is required to participate in the event.</p>\r\n      <p>You can purchase the Full Moon Compass by visiting Iron Knight Atun on the right side of Heine Village Square.</p>\r\n      <p>You can still proceed with the event without the Full Moon Compass, but if you use the Full Moon Compass, you can dig 5 times faster.</p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n         <tbody>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Item</span></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Detail</span></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Note</span></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/76/53/a2abf6f2fbf772d9baf6b0e7.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Full Moon Compass</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Digging time reduced by 5<br>Non-equippable item<br>(Purchase from Atun in Heine Village)&nbsp;</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Canot move or store<br>Auto delete</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <br>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"16355-2\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Full Moon Treasue Island Admission</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>Full Moon Treasure Island is available for 30 minutes from 21:30 to 22:00 every day. A system message will inform you so that you can prepare in advance one hour before entering. You can enter through Moon Knight Gillian located in Heine Village Square and enter by donating 10,000 Adena.</p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"clear: both; margin-bottom: 30px;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/64/37/86d320c4e6e140522b8efc8b.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">Entrance to Treasure Island through Heine Village Gillian</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/64/37/4eac6db218a34299b630614c.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">Automatically transforms into an Archaeologist upon entry</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p>Treasure Island Features</p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n         <tbody>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Full Moon Treasure Island Features</span><br>- It is a huge island made up of various terrains such as jungle, lava, snowfields, deserts, and ruins.<br>- Level 60 or higher can enter, and 10,000 Adena is consumed as a donation upon entry.<br>- It is an interserver where you can meet characters from other servers.<br>- When you enter, you are automatically transformed into an archaeologist, and the transformation is canceled when you leave.<br>- When entering, the treasure detection shovel is automatically issued, and it is automatically deleted when leaving.<br>- Safety Zone, No Penalty setting.<br>- PSS only \"Support Mode\" allowed</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n         <tbody>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Item</span></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Detail</span></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Note</span></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/81/16/8ffa7d82cb4ec62cba788b17.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Treasure Detection Shovel</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">- A magic wand that uses the Treasure Excavation Skill<br>- Automatic given upon entry to Treasure Island<br>- Non-equippable item<br>(Can only be used on Full Moon Treasure Island)</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">- Cannot move or store in warehouse<br>- Deleted when leaving Treasure Island</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/39/28/019caba45bf7f3091c817d91.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p>Full Moon Treasure Island can be used until 22:00, and you can return to Heine Village even before then by talking to High Priest Kael located on Treasure Island. If you return through Kael, you will not be able to receive the additional compensation provided at the end.<br></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"16355-3\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Treasure Hunting and Excavation</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>There are no monsters on the Treasure Island, only the treasure is hidden from view. In order to find the treasure, you must diligently wander from place to place. When a character gets near a treasure, a circular effect and sound appear. The closer the treasure is to the hidden location, the greater the effect and the more urgent the sound, so adjust the sound effect significantly before entering.</p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n         <tbody>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/31/19/923a95d2cdfa4b9c0284ad4c.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/71/68/4c5a536ae91f79b8a527f692.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/45/73/14a0e7bce4e0459f1e909716.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/77/14/a9c5bb600b5a0a8480ab7bb0.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p>A circle will appear around the character from blue, green, orange, and red color. When the circle becomes red it means that there is a treasure hidden nerby.<br></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"clear: both; margin-bottom: 30px;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/75/21/5c3009a6111e3d4263f25c0a.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\"></p>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/75/21/4df9558b20242f547dbe6f52.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\"></p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p>When the treasure is placed in a hidden spot, an orange pillar effect is revealed. Double-click on the treasure detection shovel here to start digging for treasure using the Excavation skill. If you possess a full moon compass, you can reduce excavation time by a factor of five.</p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p>When the treasure gauge is full, Eva\'s treasure will appear somewhere on the Treasure Island and will inform you of the location with a full message. The more treasures the characters participating in the event in Treasure Island dig up, the faster the treasure gauge fills up. Eva\'s treasure can be used to obtain top-tier weapons, domination rings, and even rare skills.<br></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"clear: both; margin-bottom: 30px;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/53/53/6874f75c21a3d1488750e752.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\"></p>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/53/53/9a4e93398f654b7ac70fe4c2.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\"></p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p>When the treasure gauge is full, Eva\'s treasure will appear somewhere on Treasure Island.<br></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"16355-4\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Earn Treasures and Rewards</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p style=\"font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif;\">When you excavate treasure, you can obtain various items as rewards. After excavating the treasure, you can obtain the basic event currency, Oval Gold Coin. In addition, you can obtain Adena, various growth support items, various advanced items, and a Chuseok Skill Box where you can acquire various advanced skills.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif;\"><br></p>\r\n      <p style=\"font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif;\">The higher the rank of the hidden treasure, the better the item you can get. In particular, if you unearth Eva\'s treasure, you will be able to obtain top-tier weapons, domination rings, and even rare skills.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif;\"><br></p>\r\n      <p style=\"font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgu