(52, 'Forgotten Island', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"16515-0\" style=\"padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" jhenghei\",=\"\" meiryo,=\"\" \"ms=\"\" pgothic\",=\"\" 돋움,=\"\" dotum,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n   <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">The most difficult hunting grounds with no teleportation or return possible.</span></p>\r\n   <p><br>The Forgotten Island, a hunting ground with deep history and tradition, has returned after 6 years..<br>A place where ancient secrets are hidden, manaul play is expected due to environmental changes and the appearance of large amount of NPCs.</p>\r\n   <p><br>High experience points, legendary weapons and skills, and PVP-specific armor are available, attracting the attention of many adventures.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"16515-1\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" jhenghei\",=\"\" meiryo,=\"\" \"ms=\"\" pgothic\",=\"\" 돋움,=\"\" dotum,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n   <h2>Forgotten Island Open Event</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n   <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\"></span><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Ancient Pauldrons Event</span></p>\r\n   <p>- Obtain \'Ancient Pauldrons\' hunting on Forgotten Island.</p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n      <tbody>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Item Name</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: