(53, '23rd Anniversary Class Rebalancing', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"16576-0\" style=\"padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" jhenghei\",=\"\" meiryo,=\"\" \"ms=\"\" pgothic\",=\"\" 돋움,=\"\" dotum,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n   <p>In celebration of the 23rd Anniversary, class rebalancing was carried out after various adjustments such as basic specs, skills, and item stats to reduce the gap between classes and ensure diversity in battles.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"16576-1\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" jhenghei\",=\"\" meiryo,=\"\" \"ms=\"\" pgothic\",=\"\" 돋움,=\"\" dotum,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n   <h2>Update: 4 Dec. 29, 2021 | 23rd Anniversary Class Reblance</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n   <p><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/71/38/a0d4c6366d02d4e4abbf7567.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <p>In the 4th Update of Class Rebalancing, the combat performance of the Dark Elves and Illusionist was intensively adjusted. In order to strengthen the basic concept of the class, various new skills were added and existing skill stats were adjusted.<br></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"16576-2\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" jhenghei\",=\"\" meiryo,=\"\" \"ms=\"\" pgothic\",=\"\" 돋움,=\"\" dotum,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n   <h2>Dark Elves Changes</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n   <p>In order to make use of the assassin concept, new skills have been added and existing skill stats have been adjusted, and the amount of catalysts consumed when casting skills has been adjusted to improve overall sustainability.</p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">1. New Skill</span><br>- Two new skills have been added to match the assassin concept.</p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n      <tbody>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Skill</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Level</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Type</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Detail</span></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/48/82/8d998b5933404c4c4799a517.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><font color=\"#c38b61\">Shadow Step (Chase)</font></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">90</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Passive</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\"><br>- Increase duration<br>- Increase range by +1<br>- Add \'No Return\' effect<br>- PC/NPC passable</td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/12/28/f75d85be86ea8e9c421db949.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><font color=\"#c38b61\">Blind Hiding (Assassin)</font></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">90</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Passive</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\"><br>- Attack & skills can be used while<br>invisible<br>- Increase movement speed and no longer<br>exposeslight<br>- Monsters are not aware effects is not<br>exposed<br>- Can not detect after 3s of casting</td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n      </tbody>\r\n   </table>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">2. Skill Rebalancing</span><br>- The stats of major skills have been adjusted to strengthen your position as a melee dealer with the strongest attack power.</p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <table class=\"custom-tabl