p></p>\r\n   <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n      <tbody>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Skill</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Update</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/23/55/f0fde0e2b3b9d5dcfc5ebea8.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><font color=\"#c38b61\">Fury</font></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">- Chance to apply x3 Crash Damage when activated.</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/55/93/9e19f1bdee212d2f240c0080.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><font color=\"#c38b61\">Power Grip</font></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">- Increase cooldown time<br>- Duration changed from 6s to 4s.</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/60/96/105880d8f1a98bc90a2cae9d.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><font color=\"#c38b61\">Titan (Rock)</font></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">- Base proc chance reduced<br>- Proc chance added according to level<br>- Basic activation: 15%<br>- Starting level 90; 2% ever 2 levels</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/87/12/d82f1ca45543baa749fa75de.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><font color=\"#c38b61\">Desperado</font></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">- Cooldown time increased</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n      </tbody>\r\n   </table>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <p>In consideration of equity between classes, the value of the Templar Axe (Engraved) has been adjusted.</p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n      <tbody>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Item</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); w