group\" id=\"16576-11\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" jhenghei\",=\"\" meiryo,=\"\" \"ms=\"\" pgothic\",=\"\" 돋움,=\"\" dotum,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n   <h2>Update: 1 | Nov. 17, 2021 | 23rd Anniversary Class Reblance</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n   <p><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/72/22/554037fefacbbc47664d4d27.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <p>In the first round of the 23rd Anniversary Class Rebalancing, the HP gap between classes has been reduced, and the characteristics of the Wizard, Fencer, and Lancer classes have been improved, as well as the overall ability of skill to ensure the diversity of battles.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"16576-12\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" jhenghei\",=\"\" meiryo,=\"\" \"ms=\"\" pgothic\",=\"\" 돋움,=\"\" dotum,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n   <h2>Health Points Rebalancing</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n   <p>To alleviate the HP gap between classes, the amount of HP increase according to CON value has been increased for the Knight / Dragon Knight / Monarch / Dark Elf, / Elf classes.</p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n      <tbody>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Class</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/83/16/e5ad92651d015dae98ca867e.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><font color=\"#c38b61\">Knight</font></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/96/75/5b8fb6e19726ac7257a1a63b.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><font color=\"#c38b61\">Dragon Knight</font></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/25/53/fe50c34cef5d5b09c6688f6b.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><font color=\"#c38b61\">Monarch</font></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/13/60/ba7f633f2409552670a87770.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><font color=\"#c38b61\">Dark Elf</font></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/78/11/a97784433c34b3ef501f207c.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><font color=\"#c38b61\">Elf</font></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n      </tbody>\r\n   </table>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"16576-13\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: \" 맑은=\"\" 고딕\",=\"\" \"malgun=\"\" gothic\",=\"\" \"microsoft=\"\" jhenghei\",=\"\" meiryo,=\"\" \"ms=\"\" pgothic\",=\"\" 돋움,=\"\" dotum,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n   <h2>Wizard Updates</h2>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n   <p>The overall attack performance of the Wizard class has been lowered to allow for more equitable combat.<br>In keeping with the concept of the wizard, the damage of Disintegrate (Nemesis) has been increased to maintain strong one-hit damage.</p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n      <tbody>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Magic</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Update</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/30/66/0d25dd88529cd0b55b35e72d.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><font color=\"#c38b61\">Lesser Heal</font></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Increased cooldown, decreased healed amount</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://w