 class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p>Compared to other classes, the excessively high skill hit rate and performance have been partially adjusted to bring out more diverse combat experiences.<br>A new function for Lancer\'s Pressure (Death Recall) has been added and adjusted so that it has performance commensurate with its skill status.</p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n      <tbody>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Skill</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Update</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/43/63/6464fb5537930d9285d1674d.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><font color=\"#c38b61\">Cruel (Conviction)</font></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Reduced Range</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/10/71/f0b71ba00948cc330de33c3e.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><font color=\"#c38b61\">Pressure (Death Recall)</font></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Disables Potions / Increased Damage</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/83/71/ca281a978a4868cb08f65337.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><font color=\"#c38b61\">Alternate</font></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Cooldown Reduced</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/45/71/5ca9b7bf82cd0d8eb5e45126.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><font color=\"#c38b61\">Cruel</font></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Reduced Hit Chance</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n         <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/30/66/3052a53a3b92be15434f997e.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               <p align=\"center\"><font color=\"#c38b61\">Dodge Break</font></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\">Base 15%<br>From 81; +3% every 3 levels (max 30%)</p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n      </tbody>\r\n   </table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '/upload/2022/01/28/POWERBOOK_53_aa536026-45f5-4981-95e3-3e3e3d0ebab8002.jpg', 'false', 'false');
INSERT INTO `app_powerbook` (`id`, `title`, `content`, `mainImg`, `main`, `guideMain`) VALUES
(54, 'Heine Guard Tower Conquest Battle', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15788-0\" style=\"padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\"><font style=\"font-size: 18px !important;\">Fierece Battles with total prize of 1.3 billion & exlusive raids given to the winning team</font></span></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p>Heine Guard Tower battle last for 40 minutes, the Knight Faction who takes the ownership of Tower are given the opportunity to collect taxes and exclusive raids in the area.</p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15788-1\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Feature</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>&#8594; Player must be level 85 or higher<br>&#8594; Entry time is 19:30, and the running time is 20:00 ~ 21:00<br>&#8594; Upon entry, players name are displayed anonymously, and exlusive polymorph based on players rank and level will be provided.<br>&#8594; Only PSS supprt is available<br>&#8594; Can not bookmark, Can not summon, Can not teleport randomly, and can not be revived<br>&#8594; 10 servers are matched up, upon entry characters are assigned into one of three knight factions<br>&#8594; Heine Guard Tower begins at 20:00, and occupation is determined based on when the central tower is destroyed<br>&#8594; The knight faction with the most players alive in the occupied area succeeds in occupying the area<br>&#8594; Four buff towers around the central can be occupied by the faction who destorys them<br>&#8594; After the Guard Tower Battle, a dedicated raid will be avialable to the winning faction<br>&#8594; Taxes are distributed according to number of medals each player acquired</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15788-2\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Heine Guard Tower Rules</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>When you enter, you will be randomly assigned a knight faction</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n         <tbody>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/83/14/05332a6a808db6430d0712fb.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/91/63/406837a54be0f1ebae950eae.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/31/94/f6c2dc598ca8bec63fecc9da.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Black Knights</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Red Knights</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Gold Knights</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p>Heine Guard Tower and Windawood Conquest Battle are conducted using the same battle method</p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">1. Anonymous System :</span>All players name will be anonymous<br><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">2. Polymorph System :</span>All players will have a unique polymorph based on class, level, and rank<br>&#8594; All polymorphs will be similar in appearance<br>&#8594; If you are ranked above a certain level, you will be forced into a ranker<br><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">3. Enchant Buff :</span> Exclusive enchant buffs are provided so that everyone can participate in the battle<br>(1) Lv. 85 ~ 90<br>&#8594;HP +1000, MP +100, AC -20, STR +3, DEX +3, INT +3, All Immunity +35, All Hit +35, Damage Reduction +5, MR +50, SP +7, Melee/Range Hit  +10, Magic Hit +10, Melee/Range Damage  +10, PVP Damage Reduction +22, PVP Add Damage +17<br>(2) Lv. 90 ~ 93<br>&#8594;HP +500, MP +50, AC -10, STR +3, DEX +3, INT +3, All Immunity +10, All Hit +10, MR +50, Melee/Range Hit  +10, Magic Hit +10, PVP Damage Reduction +22, PVP Add Damage +17<br></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"clear: both; margin-bottom: 30px;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/58/74/85054b51a1e050240dcb5cfa.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">All players name are anonymously</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/58/74/c9d603c4d7e0f4cf94706ce3.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">Unique polymorph based on rank</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <br>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15788-3\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>How to Enter</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>Anyone level 85 or higher can enter Heine Castle every Saturday from 19:30<br>Can teleport via Event Notification or through Unknown Rift</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"clear: both; margin-bottom: 30px;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/65/83/94c9c4dacf4562a26fb55d73.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">Teleport via Event Notification</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/65/83/d4245d81dd4f295be5b83482.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">Teleport via Unknown Rift</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15788-4\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Party Formation</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>Players placed in same faction can form party with each other<br>When inviting to a party, you must directly invite using the target\'s name [ex. /invite XXX]<br>Players from other server can also join party if they belong to the same faction, player can be invited using /invite (first 2 letter of server)<br></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n         <tbody>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p>Example: Inviting player from Deforeg Server</p>\r\n                  <p><br></p>\r\n                  <p>/invite de XXXX</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <br>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>Rewards may be automatically distributed when they are dropped, so be sure to setup distribution before forming a party</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15788-5\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Battlefield Structure</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>When you enter the Heine Guard Tower, you will begin at your faction\'s base.<br>The main guard tower is located in the center of the map.  In additional there are four buff tower place around the center (North, South, East, and West)<br></p>\r\n      <p><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/17/46/fa86edacd37667091f8ef113.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15788-6\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Arrive Preparation Area</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/70/59/df9d1ac32c7d222f5432c0a9.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">You can purchase various consumables through supply merchant</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      If your use the Unknown Rift, you will arrive at the preparation area.<br>Players from various server will gather here, and if you die during the battle you will respawn here.\r\n      <p></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15788-7\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Heine Guard Tower Battle</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>The battle will last 40 minutes starting at 8PM (20:00)<br>The moment the guardian tower is destroyed, the faction with the most characters alive within the guard tower\'s occupied area succeed in occupying the castle, and will be rewarded with \"Battlefield Chest\" that can reward up to 100 Dragon Diamonds.<br></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"clear: both; margin-bottom: 30px;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/92/40/56ed8f69d37d71e2db4ae7a4.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">Global Message allows you see which faction has the upper hand</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/92/40/75284760424df5999c039e83.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">When tower is destoryed, additional mission are granted</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p>[Rewards]</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n         <tbody>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Name</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Item</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/16/88/0ce92aab66d8837f0e7aaae2.png\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Battlefield Chest</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">10 ~ 100 Dragon Diamonds (Engraved)<br></td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p>When central tower is destroyed, the defense faction and offense faction will be given additional mission which must be completed within 3 ~ 10 minutes.<br>If the mission is successful, you can obtain \"Chest\" containing EXP Pure Elixir.<br></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p>[Mission Rewards]</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n         <tbody>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Name</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Mission</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Item</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/52/88/a9b2cc9a3d0de6516d89c013.png\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Usurper Chest<br>Guardian Chest</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Offense within 5m<br>Defense within 10m</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">Pure Elixir (EXP) (1)<br>Aden Champion Potion (200)<br>Aden Mana Potion (20)<br>Black Tiger Pearl (1)<br></td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15788-8\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Buff Towers</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>The 4 buff towers placed around the central area plays a very important role and can be the determining factor in wining the battle.  Each tower provides unique buff, and the player/faction to destory the tower get\'s the buff.  Buff towers are only rebuilt after the central tower has been destroyed. <br></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"clear: both; margin-bottom: 30px;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/42/16/4f9ed2abd98a56b9781cf4df.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">Buff Towers located North, South, East, & West</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/42/16/1a28315be199a52f122d2f6c.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\"><font color=\"#333333\">Moment you destory buff tower, message is displayed on screen</font></p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p>When buff tower is destoryed, a message will appear on the screen and the buff will be provided to the player/faction that destoryed it.</p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n         <tbody>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">North Tower</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">East Tower</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">South Tower</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">West Tower</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">HP +1000, MP +200<br>Enemy AoE Damage</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">AoE Debuff Ememy<br>(Reduce Melee Evasion)</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Haste Lv.4<br>Random forced return on ememy<br>faction in central area</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Ignore PVP Damage Reduction</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <br>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15788-9\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Compensation</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">1. Occupation Tax Distribution</span><br>Medals are provided to factions in the occupied area every minute. At the end of the battle, the winning faction will be rewarded with 1.2 Billion Adena depending on the amount of medals acquired.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n         <tbody>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/84/83/e0f8055026e16e128bd328bf.png\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/53/51/cbdceaa67a427ff3169c55e6.png\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/64/41/fcce156ae0a3d4da798a985f.png\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Black Knight Medal</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Red Knight Medal</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Gold Knight Medal</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p>Each medals can be obtain in three ways..</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n         <tbody>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Medal Heist</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Zone Keeper</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Capture Buff Tower</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Steal 1 Medal each time you kill an<br>enemy in any area of the battlefield</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Auto paid to faction occupying the<br>guard tower every minute</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">3 medals are awarded to the player who<br>destorys the buff tower, and nearby allies</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p>In case of stealing medal, this does not apply to players who only have 1 medal in possesion and defeating the same team</p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/93/13/08d046f4941753a483b83ccb.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\"></div>\r\n      The top three players in each faction with the most medals will have a separate indicator activated above their heads.\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Diving Penalty</span></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right;\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/95/47/d25eb84d49750a0b49bdf08f.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\"></div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p>The diving penalty is a penalty that reduces the amount of medal you earned if you do not actively play after participating in the battle.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p>Penalties are awarded at the staging area of each faction after the start of the occupation match, and are counted before the penalty is applied.</p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/77/39/101234feba8d4f1dc16dc731.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/40/67/0f873107ac0892b2ee298410.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p>The penalty timer is given for a total of 2 minutes as shown in the picture above, and is decremented by 1 when 2 minutes have elapsed.<br>From then on, the time remaining until the penalty is continuously added by 1 minute, and each minute that passes, the medal is reduced by 1.</p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p>However, for users who do not have any medals, the number of medals will not be reduced even if the penalty is applied, and the penalty timer will be reset if they leave the faction waiting area.</p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">2. Exclusive Raid</span><br>From 20:40, the victorious faction who hold at least one medal will be entitled to meet Trodon, the lord of Heine\'s Castle.<br>Based on the central area, you can enter Heine Inner Castle through the portal at 11 o\'clock and proceed with the raid.<br>For 20 minutes, the winning team can move freely, and when attacking Trodon, the lord of the castle, they will have a chance to obtain legendary weapons and skills, including Adena.</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"clear: both; margin-bottom: 30px;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/55/83/e1de0031bffe9ffe97072df3.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">Enter through the portal located at 11 o\'clock</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/55/83/8b73ddf6647bb0691e26f194.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4;\">You can get legendary items, including adena.</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <br>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">3. Boss Monster Rewards</span></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n         <tbody>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Boss</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Drops</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/11/65/e26c5b96c0ce9d2d6209fac6.png\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Heine Castle Trodon</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p><font color=\"#c38b61\">Gaia\'s Wrath</font></p>\r\n                  <p><font color=\"#c38b61\">Spearbook (Pressure: Death Recall)</font></p>\r\n                  <p><font color=\"#c38b61\">Spearbook (Cruel Conviction)</font></p>\r\n                  <p><font color=\"#c38b61\">Spearbook (Recovery)</font></p>\r\n                  <p><font color=\"#c38b61\">Spearbook (Maelstorm)</font></p>\r\n                  <p><font color=\"#c38b61\">Spearbook (Increase Range)</font></p>\r\n                  <p><font color=\"#c38b61\">Fencer Book(Phantom Death)</font></p>\r\n                  <p><font color=\"#c38b61\">Fencer Book(Pantera Shcok)</font></p>\r\n                  <p><font color=\"#c38b61\">Fencer Book(Phantom Requiem)</font></p>\r\n                  <p><font color=\"#c38b61\">Fencer Book(Phantom Reaper)</font></p>\r\n                  <p><font color=\"#c38b61\">Techbook(Counter Barrier Master)</font><br><font color=\"#c38b61\">Techbook(Raging Weapon)</font><br><font color=\"#c38b61\">Techbook(Shock Attack)</font><br><font color=\"#c38b61\">Spirit Crystal(Burning Shot)</font><br><font color=\"#c38b61\">Spirit Crystal(Soul Barrier Armor)</font><br></p>\r\n                  <p><font color=\"#c38b61\">Spirit Crystal (Triple Arrow Boost)</font></p>\r\n                  <div><br></div>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>', '/upload/2022/02/24/POWERBOOK_54_0cb2093d-df79-4ccb-a298-e5efe53938f1hreaasda.jpg', 'false', 'false');
INSERT INTO `app_powerbook` (`id`, `title`, `content`, `mainImg`, `main`, `guideMain`) VALUES
(55, 'Tower of Insolence', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"16812-0\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important; font-size: 18px !important;\">High end hunting grounds consisting of 10 floors!</font></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">In Tower of Insolence, you can acquire expensive items and crafting materials that can be used to obtain mythical weapons by hunting boss spawning at certain time everday.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Materials used to craft Mythical Weapon are hunted through the Domination Tower, which can only be accessible by hunting the Tower of Inoslence.</p>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br></div>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"16812-1\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">How to Enter</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- You can teleport to Tower of Insolence directly by using Insolence Teleport Scroll or by visitng Insolence Tower Statue located in Aden Village.<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- However, the Summit can only be reached by Insolence Teleport Scroll.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <tbody style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Region</span></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Item</span></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Usage</span></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Tower of Insolence 1 - 10F</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/28/20/9c3f31393aed1e038a30df8b.png\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Insolence Teleport Scroll</span></font></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- Single use item that takes to marked floor<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- You can use the same scroll to random teleport on<br>the floor<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- You can craft scrolls, find NPC Muvni in Aden Village</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Tower of Insolence 1 - 10F</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/65/35/cf8d8d1e1b75712d7f703b7b.png\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Insolence Amulet</span></font></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"p