 style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Can Trade | Can Delete | Can Store</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Fixed Probability</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n               <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/50/56/44738ef9677271fef80f8417.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Reaper\'s Protection</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Defaults</span></div>\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">AC -3<br>HP+500<br></div>\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">MR +12<br>All Hit +3</div>\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Exclusive Optons</span></div>\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Teleport to Summit</div>\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">EXP +20%</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">+ Insolence Protection (Lv.10)</div>\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">+ 100 Insolence Teleport Scroll<br>(Summit)</div>\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Can Trade | Can Delete | Can Store</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">100%</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n            </tbody>\r\n         </table>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></span>If you fail to create Insolence Protections on each floor, the existing Insolence Protection will be preserved, however 20 Bloodstains, and 100 Teleport Scrolls will evaporate.</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>', '/upload/2022/07/12/POWERBOOK_55_19c19312-8069-414b-ab56-080482da1d27003.jpg', 'false', 'false');
INSERT INTO `app_powerbook` (`id`, `title`, `content`, `mainImg`, `main`, `guideMain`) VALUES
(56, 'Infinite War', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"643-0\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important; font-size: 18px !important;\">Stop the endless onslaught of monsters!</font></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Infinite Battle is where battle hordes of monsters summoned within a limited time.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Among them, the most difficult place is Giran Colosseum.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">An update on July 22, 2015, the monsters and rewards that appear in Giran Colosseum has been updated significantly attracking the attention of many players.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"643-1\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">July 22, 2015 - Updates</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Various aspect, including the entry method has been changed.<br>&#8594; Level requirement has been adjusted (Lv. 65+)<br>&#8594; Increase monsters abilities that spawn<br>&#8594; Boss monster drops rare item which includes: Warrior Seal (Desperado), Tech Book (Counter Barrier), and Spellbook (Disintergate).<br>&#8594; EXP is given when defeating boss monsters in each round<br>&#8594; Infinite Battle Exclusive for PC Room has been removed</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"643-2\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">How to Participate</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"clear: both; margin-bottom: 30px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/92/62/696be194654737fecc36ee90.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">5 Colosseum Mangers have been added</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/92/62/8cdc1c2c06e64433f56549ec.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Each manager are in charge of different Infinite Battle</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">You can enter the Colosseum by paying 10,000 Adena</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Infinite Battle begins at 10:30 PM every night, and can be enter starting at 10:25 PM.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Since each Colosseum manger are in charge of a different Battle, there are total of 5 battles take place each day!</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">If your participating with clan members, decide together on which one you want to battle!</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"643-3\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Feature</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Giran Colosseum, death penalties have been removed. </p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <tbody style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td class=\"cel1 width60\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Entry Level</p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"width400\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">65 or higher</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td class=\"cel1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Entry Time</p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Start Time</p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Everyday 10:25 ~ 10:29</p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Everyday 10:30</p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td class=\"cel1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Max Capacity</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">50 Players</p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td class=\"cel1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Feature</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- No penalty for item dropped or exp loss upon death<br>&#8594; Not possible to random teleport<br>&#8594; Can not be revived<br>&#8594; Can not summon pet, monsters or tammed<br>&#8594; Can not attack other players</p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">* If you summon pets prior to entering the colosseum, they will be disapper as soon as you enter.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"643-4\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Flow</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <font color=\"#ed1c24\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"clear: both; margin-bottom: 30px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/80/64/23b1c43d3c0be0c7bb2c18c0.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">As you progress each rounds get harder</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/80/64/44ddd59b5330091e9b74fd81.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Destory the orb at end of each round to get HP/MP recovery</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </font>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#ed1c24\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></font><font color=\"#ed1c24\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></font></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Infinite Battle lasts for about 25 minutes, and you must annihilate the monsters that appear within the time limit.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">There are over 3 rounds and at end of each round a boss monster spawns</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">At the end of each round, a blue orb will appear on the field, break it and you can receive buffs such as Patience or Advance Spirit.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <tbody style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td class=\"box1 width600\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">1. Monsters start spawning as soon as the round starts</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8595;</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">2. After a certain period of time, Adena will start dropping on the ground</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8595;</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">3. After certain period of time boss will spawn</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8595;</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">4. When you defeat boss, you will get item drops</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8595;</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">5. Round ends when all monster including the boss has been defeated</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8595;</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">6. Rest for 1m, before moving to the next round</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8595;</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">7. You win if you defeat the Grim Reaper, the final boss for round 3</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8595;</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">8. You will have 3m of free time, until the Infinite Battle ends</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">If all players die or are unable to defeat monsters within a certain time, the Infinite Battle will fail and come to an end.  All players will be teleported back to the village.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"643-5\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot