ck King Palace</font><br>\r\n				  <font color=\"#c38b61\">- Black King Claws</font><br>\r\n				  </p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><b>Armor</b></p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\">- Bless Divine Protection Cloak</font></p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n				  \r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><b>Accessory</b></p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\">- Bless Polymorph Ring</font><br>\r\n				  <font color=\"#c38b61\">- Bless Summon Ring</font><br>\r\n				  <font color=\"#c38b61\">- Bless Fire Ring</font><br>\r\n				  <font color=\"#c38b61\">- Bless Water Ring</font><br>\r\n				  <font color=\"#c38b61\">- Wind Resistance Ring</font><br>\r\n				  <font color=\"#c38b61\">- Bless Earth Ring</font><br></p>\r\n				  \r\n				  \r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><b>Spell | Skill</b></p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\">- Technical Book (Phantom Reaper)</font><br>\r\n				  <font color=\"#c38b61\">- Fencer Book(Phantom Death)</font><br>\r\n				  <font color=\"#c38b61\">- Warrior Seal(Desperado)</font><br>\r\n				  <font color=\"#c38b61\">- Spellbook(Disintegrate)</font><br></p>\r\n				  \r\n				  \r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><b>ETC</b></p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\">- Sealed Insolence Amulet 1F</font><br>\r\n				  <font color=\"#c38b61\">- Sealed Insolence Amulet 2F</font><br>\r\n				  <font color=\"#c38b61\">- Sealed Insolence Amulet 3F</font><br>\r\n				  <font color=\"#c38b61\">- Sealed Insolence Amulet 4F</font><br>\r\n				  <font color=\"#c38b61\">- Sealed Insolence Amulet 5F</font><br>\r\n				  <font color=\"#c38b61\">- Sealed Insolence Amulet 6F</font><br>\r\n				  <font color=\"#c38b61\">- Sealed Insolence Amulet 7F</font><br>\r\n				  <font color=\"#c38b61\">- Sealed Insolence Amulet 8F</font><br>\r\n				  <font color=\"#c38b61\">- Sealed Insolence Amulet 9F</font><br>\r\n				  <font color=\"#c38b61\">- Sealed Insolence Amulet 10F</font><br>\r\n				  <font color=\"#c38b61\">- Sealed Insolence Amulet TOP</font><br>\r\n				  <font color=\"#c38b61\">- Leaf of Life</font><br>\r\n				  <font color=\"#c38b61\">- Sealed Insolence Amulet 1F(Revival)</font><br>\r\n				  <font color=\"#c38b61\">- Sealed Insolence Amulet 2F(Revival)</font><br>\r\n				  <font color=\"#c38b61\">- Sealed Insolence Amulet 3F(Revival)</font><br>\r\n				  <font color=\"#c38b61\">- Sealed Insolence Amulet 4F(Revival)</font><br>\r\n				  <font color=\"#c38b61\">- Sealed Insolence Amulet 5F(Revival)</font><br>\r\n				  <font color=\"#c38b61\">- Sealed Insolence Amulet 6F(Revival)</font><br>\r\n				  <font color=\"#c38b61\">- Sealed Insolence Amulet 7F(Revival)</font><br>\r\n				  <font color=\"#c38b61\">- Sealed Insolence Amulet 8F(Revival)</font><br>\r\n				  <font color=\"#c38b61\">- Sealed Insolence Amulet 9F(Revival)</font><br>\r\n				  <font color=\"#c38b61\">- Sealed Insolence Amulet 10F(Revival)</font><br>\r\n				  <font color=\"#c38b61\">- Warrior Seal(Desperado)(Revival)</font><br>\r\n				  <font color=\"#c38b61\">- Spellbook(Disintegrate)(Revival)</font><br>\r\n				  <font color=\"#c38b61\">- Fencer Book(Phantom Reaper)(Revival)</font><br>\r\n				  <font color=\"#c38b61\">- Divine Protection Cloak(Revival)</font><br>\r\n				  <font color=\"#c38b61\">- Weapon Enchant Scroll</font><br>\r\n				  <font color=\"#c38b61\">- Armor Enchant Scroll</font><br>\r\n				  <font color=\"#c38b61\">- Haste Potion</font></p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">+</p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">1.5% EXP based on Lv. 52</p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>', '/upload/2022/07/14/POWERBOOK_56_673d3c57-2e22-42ee-b97f-5551e06b24a6fdf5304e601c146d0c3b6cb9.jpg', 'false', 'false');
INSERT INTO `app_powerbook` (`id`, `title`, `content`, `mainImg`, `main`, `guideMain`) VALUES
(57, 'Temple of Extreme Cold', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15381-0\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">A single-player dungeon with various rewards waiting for you.</span><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">A single-player dungeon available to characters level 70 and above.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">There is a <font color=\"#c38b61\"><b>NORMAL | HARD</b></font> mode for each difficulty, and it is a time-limited dungeon that lasts for 30 minutes from the moment you enter, the reward items vary depending on experience and the boss monster you meet at the end.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15381-1\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Features</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- Level 70+ & 30 minutes usage time<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- <font color=\"#c38b61\"><b>Aura of Flame</b></font> is required to enter which will vary depending on the difficulty selected<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- Hunt all monsters that appear in each stage to get a clear bonus exp and move on to the next stage<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- Total of 4 stages + Boss stage (appears randomly)<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- Can not be re-used with <font color=\"#c38b61\"><b>Frozen Heart</b></font> in possession, which is obtained after defeating the boss monster</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15381-2\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">How to Enter</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/60/33/647cb811c08fd22d9a56ed93.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n         <br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">You can enter Temple of Extreme Cold through NPC Bread, located in Oren Village</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Select either NORMAL | HARD mode upon entering<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Aura of Flame is consumed and will disappear once entered</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">[Materials According to Difficulty]</span></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <tbody style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Difficulty</span></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Material</span></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">HARD</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">5 Aura of Flame</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">NORMAL</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">1 Aura of Flame</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15381-3\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Map Layout</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- Consist of a total of 4 areas, and each door is only opened once all monsters are defeated in the area<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- Clear all the monsters that spawn in the area, and receive Clear Bonus Exp<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- Boss monster will appear in the last area, upon defeating, you will be teleported to Oren Village</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/93/35/59e8a5af7efea33ee3904de7.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15381-4\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Strategy</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Basically hunting is done with the Storm Rod which is given by NPC near the entrance</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Speak with Ivory Tower Spy near the entrance to receive the Storm Rod</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">This item can only be used in The Temple of Extreme Cold<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Defeat monsters by using the Storm Rod, which will cast Tornado, but be careful not to get overwhelmed with monsters.  HP Potions should be purchased prior</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"clear: both; margin-bottom: 30px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/72/37/c202760fea27c06f0dc14719.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Potions can be purchased from NPC Sunia</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/72/37/a2449820a5b91483ac187340.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Receive Storm Rod from Ivory Tower Spy</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Basic Strategy</span><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Since most are slow moving melee monsters, it\'s best to gather them together and cast the Storm Rod.<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">However, the Ice Queen\'s Guard (bow) and the Ice Queen\'s Maid attack from a distance, so defeat them first. If you run out of recovery potions, go back to the entrance and replenish them.<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">The monster\'s attack power itself is high, so if you are surrounded, you can lie down in an instant, so be careful.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"clear: both; margin-bottom: 30px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/53/34/8e5785297867506b97d34be4.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Attack by casting the Strom Rod</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/53/34/c2586a88db069327d2e96f70.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Buff is provided when orb is destroyed</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15381-5\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;