(58, 'Unicorn Temple', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"10096-0\" style=\"font-family: \" noto=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"noto=\"\" sans=\"\" kr\",=\"\" -apple-system,=\"\" blinkmacsystemfont,=\"\" roboto,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" padding-top:=\"\" 0px;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important; font-size: 20px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Single Player Defense Dungeon</span></font></p>\r\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Can be purchased by TAM <font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Unicorn Temple Key</span></font>.</p>\r\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">The goal is to protect the Unicorn in the middle of the map from the rushing monsters.  Save the Unicorn, and be rewarded heavily.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"10096-1\" style=\"font-family: \" noto=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"noto=\"\" sans=\"\" kr\",=\"\" -apple-system,=\"\" blinkmacsystemfont,=\"\" roboto,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><h2 style=\"font-family: \" noto=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"noto=\"\" sans=\"\" kr\",=\"\" -apple-system,=\"\" blinkmacsystemfont,=\"\" roboto,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" 0px=\"\" !important;\"=\"\">May 20, 2021 Update</h2></div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">A new booster mode has been added to the Unicorn Temple, which offer more EXP, Rewards, and opportunities to acquire expensive items. You will need 3 Unicorn Temple Key to enter the booster mode.  You will get x3 Rewards, EXP, and clear time has been shortend.  Chance to encounter Abish and Azmodan has also been increased.</p>\r\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Increased EXP, Reward, and Drops</span></p>\r\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">The EXP gained has been increased by approximately x3 and drops has been increased by x1.5 times.  Since the strategy is to defeat numerious monster as quickly as possible, you can obtain high rewards in short period of time.</p>\r\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Drops Increased</span></p>\r\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Rewards such as new magic Spearbook (Malestorm) and Kurtz Sword (Revival) have been added to Abish and Azodan\'s treasure chest.</p>\r\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <tbody style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <td class=\"cel1 width300\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Abish Treasure Chest</span></font><br style=\"letter-