ing: 0px !important;\">Weapon Enchant Scroll (Artisan)</span></font></p>\r\n               <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Armor Enchant Scroll (Bless)</span></font></p>\r\n               <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Armor Enchant Scroll (Cursed)</span></font></p>\r\n               <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Dark Crystal (Shadow Armor: Destiny)</span></font><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Dark Crystal (Shadow Armor: Destiny)(Revival)</span></font></p>\r\n               <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Kurtz\'s Sword(Revival)</span></font>(<span style=\"font-weight: bolder; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#ed1c24\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">New Addition</font></span>)<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Death Knight Fire Sword (Revival)</span></font>(<span style=\"font-weight: bolder; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#ed1c24\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">New Addition</font></span>)<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Warrior Seal(Desperado)</span></font>(<span style=\"font-weight: bolder; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#ed1c24\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">New Addition</font></span>)</p>\r\n               <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n               <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">* Obtain Random Items</p>\r\n               <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n            </td>\r\n         </tr>\r\n      </tbody>\r\n   </table>\r\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Azomdan Treasure Chest now consist of Divine Belt items instead of the Belt of STR | DEX | INT<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"10096-2\" style=\"font-family: \" noto=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"noto=\"\" sans=\"\" kr\",=\"\" -apple-system,=\"\" blinkmacsystemfont,=\"\" roboto,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><h2 style=\"font-family: \" noto=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"noto=\"\" sans=\"\" kr\",=\"\" -apple-system,=\"\" blinkmacsystemfont,=\"\" roboto,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" 0px=\"\" !important;\"=\"\">Feature</h2></div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; Single player dungeon<br>&#8594; Protect Unicorn in the middle of the map by defeating the rushing monsters<br>&#8594; If Unicorn dies due to the monster rush or time limit has run out, you will be teleported back to Giran Village<br>&#8594; 3 Types of Boss Monsters appears and drop unique items when defeated</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"10096-3\" style=\"font-family: \" noto=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"noto=\"\" sans=\"\" kr\",=\"\" -apple-system,=\"\" blinkmacsystemfont,=\"\" roboto,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><h2 style=\"font-family: \" noto=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"noto=\"\" sans=\"\" kr\",=\"\" -apple-system,=\"\" blinkmacsystemfont,=\"\" roboto,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" 0px=\"\" !important;\"=\"\">How to Enter</h2></div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"clear: both; margin-bottom: 30px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/54/79/f7701508133c931e260ae9c5.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#333333\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Use Einhasad Points to purchase Unicorn Temple Key (3 per week)</font></p>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/54/79/4afee99c473ce8ab6d46d0ea.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Find NPC Haight and teleport to Unicorn Temple</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">In Giran Village, find NPC Kruna to purchase Unicorn Temple Key</p>\r\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Locate NPC Haight (next to Kruna) and click to enter Unicorn Temple.  You can also enter by double-clicking the key (only in Safe Zone)</p>\r\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">TIP! How to obtain Unicorn Temple Key</span><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- Use Einhasad Points to purchase Unicorn Temple Key Box from NPC Keplisha<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- Buy Unicorn Temple Key from NPC Kruna (using TAM)</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"10096-4\" style=\"font-family: \" noto=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"noto=\"\" sans=\"\" kr\",=\"\" -apple-system,=\"\" blinkmacsystemfont,=\"\" roboto,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><h2 style=\"font-family: \" noto=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"noto=\"\" sans=\"\" kr\",=\"\" -apple-system,=\"\" blinkmacsystemfont,=\"\" roboto,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" 0px=\"\" !important;\"=\"\">Flow</h2></div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">1. When you speak with Haight, you will be taken to the entrance of Unicorn Temple</p>\r\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Select \"Enter Unicorn Temple\" at the Dimensional Portal</p>\r\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"clear: both; margin-bottom: 30px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/51/54/c65e9a7d6f49a7ab711488cb.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Dimensional Portal at Unicorn Temple</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/51/54/f31a8a547ec9e8419ce59d2f.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Unicorn surrounded by Sealers</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">2. If you defeat the Temple Guards and the Sealers around the Unicorn, the Unicorn will give you a magic rod (Normal: Firestorm, Boost: Meteor Strike) to protect you.  The magic rod will automatically be added to your inventory, so register it the hotkey.</p>\r\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"clear: both; margin-bottom: 30px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/87/35/349975b4875ac2b5f405def6.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#333333\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Normal Mode: Firestorm</font></p>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/87/35/b6146a75b619ba58a4bb3c84.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#333333\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Boost Mode: Meteor Strike</font></p>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">3. If numerous enemies comes out around you, use the magic rod to defeat them.  These monsters will only attack the Unicorn so you don\'t have to worry about your health.</p>\r\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">4. When you defeat the Great Spirit, magic rod (Purification) will be automatically be added to your inventory</p>\r\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">5. If you get an warning message, make sure you use the Purification Rod<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">The Purification Rod has the effect of one shotting monsters.<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">However, the Purficiation Rod is a one-time use only.</p>\r\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"clear: both; margin-bottom: 30px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/50/62/308b6a79368bf15d707a5d4e.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Purficiation Rod One Shot Kill</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/50/62/e3761c0dc1dc4efa9158ebe4.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Single use, so make sure you use it well</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">6. Keep this up, and you can progress to Stage 3 of the event.  Be prepared as the Boss does have a chance to appear in Stage 3, and will require watching your HP.</p>\r\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"clear: both; margin-bottom: 30px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/68/88/a2b993382414c5f98f5d4a1a.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Abish (Boss Monster)</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/68/88/34fdb6a3a1ac34f2b68c7c3a.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Defeat boss, Unicorn will disappear</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">7. If you are able to defeat the boss monster, the Unicorn will disappear and the dungeon will come to an end.  Retrieve items fallen to the ground, before you are teleported back to the village.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '/upload/2022/07/14/POWERBOOK_58_762107f2-b9fa-451c-b4c9-c1e836318de7dab5ffc407a4f9c9bacc170b.jpg', 'false', 'false'),
(59, 'Relic System', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"16884-0\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important; font-size: 18px !important;\">Add convenience, scalability to your inventory</font></span></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">To resolve the shortage of possession inventory and provide convenience in creating protection items, the relic system was added through an update on Wednesday, August 3, 22.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Possession buff items are automatically registered in the relic inventory, making it easier and more convenient to create and upgrade relics than before.</div>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"16884-1\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">How to use</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"clear: both; margin-bottom: 30px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"clear: both; margin-bottom: 30px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/86b388070eb665acd2a93770.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Enter the UI through shortcut keys (Ctrl+R) or menus</p>\r\n               </div>\r\n               <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/9fb9d838650462b3afeeb907.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Some crafting and upgrades are only for a limited time</p>\r\n               </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <tbody style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">1. Activate the relic UI through the Ctrl + R shortcut, the relic icon at the bottom of the inventory, or the menu.</div>\r\n                     <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">2. Hover over the icon of a relic in the list to see the options for that relic</div>\r\n                     <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">3. Only relics that can be crafted and upgraded activate the crafting menu when the icon is clicked.</div>\r\n                     <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">4. Upon successful crafting, it will be automatically added to your Relic Inventory (including existing Relics)</div>\r\n                     <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">5. If you have a Relic that can be upgraded, a \'notification\' will appear at the bottom of the icon.</div>\r\n                     <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">6. Click on \'Stat Info\' in the upper left corner of the Relic Inventory interface to see the details of the Blessing option activated by the Relic.</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n            </tbody>\r\n         </table>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"16884-2\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Interface/UI</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/7273fc7a01e871d1a223ef72.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">[1] Relic Info</span></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- Get basic information about the relic</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">[2] Stat Info</span></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/3bb0df47d08f0f762720df9d.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- see buff stats and other details</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">[3] Relic List</span></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- You can check the list of all, normal, and event relics, and you can click on the relic icon to craft and upgrade.</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">[4] Relic Icon</span></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/27e791a0d781bce9bb023356.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- When you click on the relic icon, you can proceed with crafting and upgrading by consuming materials. If crafting is not possible, a pop-up window will appear.</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- Relics you own are displayed with a brightly colored icon, while relics you do not own are displayed with a dark color.</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">[5] Upgrade Notification</span></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- If you own a relic that can be upgraded, a notification message will be displayed at the bottom of the relic icon.</div>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>', '/upload/2022/08/03/POWERBOOK_59_1067ace3-3608-41ab-81a9-3987db47b0e3002.jpg', 'false', 'false');
INSERT INTO `app_powerbook` (`id`, `title`, `content`, `mainImg`, `main`, `guideMain`) VALUES
(60, 'Silectis Exhibition', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"17179-0\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important; font-size: 18px !important;\">Participate in the Selectis Exhibition and get a luxury buff!</font></span></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">The Selectis Exhibition system, which allows you to register items and obtain temporary buffs, was added through an update on August 3, 2022 (Wednesday).</div><br>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">If you collect ordinary items which are relatively easy to obtain such as, +6 Rapier, +4 T-shirt, +1 Demon Ring, and you register them in Selectis Exhibition you can get limited time buff that is helpful in battle and hunting depending on the type of item register and the enchant value.</div>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"17179-1\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">How To</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"clear: both; margin-bottom: 30px; width: 707px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"clear: both; margin-bottom: 30px; width: 707px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/a8cd7041257138bcb02e8bab.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Access the interface via shortcut key (CTRL + Y) or the menu.</p>\r\n               </div>\r\n               <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/cf01fa78efeadff6c68f1df0.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">If there is an item that can be register, just select it and it\'s registered!</p>\r\n               </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">1. Exhibition Usage</span></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <tbody style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">1. Access it via the main menu, or by press (CTRL + Y) to bring up the UI Window</div>\r\n                     <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">2. Buff effects can be replaced through the \'Change Effect\' button at the bottom of the Exhibition (can be replaced regardless of whether before or after the Exhibition is activated)</div>\r\n                     <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">3. When you have an item that can be displayed, the \'Register\' message is printed on the item icon, and you can register it through the \'Confirm\' button after clicking the icon.</div>\r\n                     <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">4. If there is a list of alternate items, or if you have an item with different enhancement values, you can click the \'[↔] button\' to view and select the list.</div>\r\n                     <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">5. When an Exhibition is activated, the \'Exhibition Effect\' buff is applied and an additional \'Enhancement Effect\' buff is applied depending on the total enchant value.</div>\r\n                     <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">6. The higher the enhancement value of the item registered in the Exhibition, the longer the buff extension time increases (extension time can be checked at each stage before registering the item)</div>\r\n                     <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">7. Can be reset through the icon at the top of the activated Exhibition (delete remaining buff time and Exhibition items)</div>\r\n                     <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">8. In the case of unidentified items, regardless of the enchant value, cannot be registered in the Exhibition.</div>\r\n                     <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">9. You can not use the Exhibition if you are in the processing of trading, using warehouse, crafting or shop.</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n            </tbody>\r\n         </table>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">2. Exhibtion Dealer Bolton</span></p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">The Exhibition equipment merchant NPC Bolton who specialize in selling Exhibition related item was added through the update on Augest 3, 2022 (Wednesday)</p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Located near the Giran Inn, sells various items such as +0 Rapier, +0 T-shirt, +0 Demon Rings, etc...</p>\r\n         <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"clear: both; margin-bottom: 30px; width: 707px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/213369e3af449d947998417a.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Exhibition NPC Bolton</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/896a304ec080a8e0f57732ea.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Basic items for the Exhibition</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"17179-2\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">UI Window</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/5c97602e55e2ee619ff7974f.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">1. Register Item</span></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; If you don\'t have an item to register, the minimum enchant value of that item will be displayed</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></span></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">2. Item Alert</span></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; If you have an item that can be registered in the exhibition, the word \'Register\' will be displayed at the top of the icon</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">3. Subsitute Items</span></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; If there are substitution items, or if you have items with different enhancement values, you can scroll to check the list.</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">4. Buff Duration</span></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; Check how long buff will be, and how more additional time enchants value will add to that buff</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">5. Register to Exhibition</span></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/6e2a6e7d767f057e1024c104.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; When the confirmation button is clicked, the final confirmation will be carried out and the registered item will disappear from inventory.</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">6. Buff Duration - Base</span></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; Basic duration for item registered regardless of the enchant value</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">7. Buff Remaining Time</span></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; Basic duration + additional time for the enchant value</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">8. Enchant Value</span></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; According the enchant value, additional value will be added</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">9. Buff Stats</span></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; Regardless of the enchant value, all items registered buff is applied</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">10. Change Stats</span></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/0d6102de8f46e80d2dfaba75.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; The buff effect can be changed at any time through the \'Change Effect\' button, regardless of whether before or after the Exhibition is activated.</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">11. Close Exhibition</span></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; You can start a new Exhibition anytime, or close a less active one</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">(ex) If you want to activate more \'buffs\' for a longer time, you can force quit and re-register higher enchant items)</div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">12. Extend Exhibition Duration</span></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; You can use Adena to extend the buff period by 1 day</div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/1ca7919f18e5f872594b1c03.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"