INSERT INTO `app_powerbook` (`id`, `title`, `content`, `mainImg`, `main`, `guideMain`) VALUES
(61, 'Items', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"225-0\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">There are a variety of items in Lineage that are difficult to count.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">These heavy weapons and armor accessories are an important factor in determining a character\'s stats, and in most cases, there is no equip level limit, so once you get good equipment, you can easily grow from a low level.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">In addition to this, there are consumable items such as potions and spellbooks, quest items that are necessary to progress the quest, and various material items that are used to craft items.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"225-1\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Classification of items</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">As numerous episodes progressed in Lineage, powerful monsters and new systems gradually appeared, and there were many qualitative and quantitative changes in the characters\' equipment and other items accordingly. These items can be divid