weapon slots</p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Attacking the target while equipped with a weapon deals damage.</p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">You can increase damage and accuracy by enchanting weapons with <br>enchant scrolls</p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td class=\"cel1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n                  <table align=\"center\" style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <tbody style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                        <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                           <td style=\"border: 0px; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/72/32/f2b4001dd34e297ef2a02088.jpg\" class=\"bd1\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></td>\r\n                        </tr>\r\n                     </tbody>\r\n                  </table>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Armor</span></font></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Items worn in armor slots, such as helmets, cloaks, armor, and gloves</p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">When worn, AC (Physical Defense) incease, and when you enchant you can <br>increase it more to take less damage.</p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td class=\"cel1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n                  <table align=\"center\" style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <tbody style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                        <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                           <td style=\"border: 0px; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/12/43/ff84798eb987a3a569e96bfd.jpg\" class=\"bd1\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></td>\r\n                        </tr>\r\n                     </tbody>\r\n                  </table>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Accessory</span></font></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Necklaces, rings, and earring slots</p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">It has various options such as HP recovery and MP recovery, and can be enchanted with accessory enchant scrolls.</p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td class=\"cel1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div class=\"img_center\" style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/58/28/296cbeaa90622754ce29a1e4.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; width: auto; height: auto; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Runes and Artifacts</span></font></div>\r\n                  </div>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Items worn in rune slots</p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Typically, you can get it as a quest reward.</p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">There is an elixir rune that is used semi-permanently.</p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td class=\"cel1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div class=\"img_center\" style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/91/66/60280456de5ba8c33a5d1cfd.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; width: auto; height: auto; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Crest</span></font></div>\r\n                  </div>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Item worn in crest slot</p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">When equipped, gain experience bonuses and other effects.</p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">It can be enchanted with a Crest Enhancement Stone.</p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td class=\"cel1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n                  <table align=\"center\" style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <tbody style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                        <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                           <td style=\"border: 0px; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/21/46/dbebae1a30538d7e53abeb5c.jpg\" class=\"bd1\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></td>\r\n                        </tr>\r\n                     </tbody>\r\n                  </table>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Magical Items</span></font></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Consumable items needed to learn magic</p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Depending on the class, various items such as spell books and spirit crystals are available.</p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td class=\"cel1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n                  <table align=\"center\" style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <tbody style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                        <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                           <td style=\"border: 0px; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/92/88/995235aca7ef506a74c09806.jpg\" class=\"bd1\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></td>\r\n                        </tr>\r\n                     </tbody>\r\n                  </table>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Common Items</span></font></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">A term that refers to various consumables such as various order forms and recovery items.</p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td class=\"cel1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/42/81/7a7d1e9b4274368274d3faee.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Set Items</span></font></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">If you wear certain items at the same time,<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">receive additional bonus</p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"225-2\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Enchanting Items</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">In Lineage, you can use the enchantment system to increase the stats of your weapons, armor, and accessories.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>', '/upload/2022/09/27/POWERBOOK_61_81b79d77-e599-468c-a3e6-91bf463e3ebec5be992f55eab14e4a288582.jpg', 'false', 'false'),
(62, 'Weapons', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"7-0\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\"><div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">캐릭터의 대미지에&nbsp;직접 영향을 주는 아이템.</p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">사냥과 전투(PvP)가 중심인 &lt;리니지&gt;에서는 가장 중요한&nbsp;위치를 차지한다.</p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">무기의 선택은 캐릭터의 레벨에 따라 조금 달라진다. 저레벨일&nbsp;때는&nbsp;<font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">언데드 추가 대미지</span></font>&nbsp;옵션이 있는 무기(주로&nbsp;<font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">단검</span></font>)를 선택해&nbsp;레벨업에 전념하며,&nbsp;일정 수준 이상의&nbsp;레벨이 되면&nbsp;사냥용과 전투용&nbsp;무기를 따로 준비하는 것이 일반적이다.</p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">또한&nbsp;아데나에 여유가 있는 플레이어들은 주요 사냥터에 따라&nbsp;<font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">속성 인챈트</span></font>를 진행한 무기를 따로 준비하기도 한다.</p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br></p></div></div><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"7-1\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\"><div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">무기의 종류</h2></div><div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><p styl