<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">용기사</span></font>&nbsp;전용 무기.</p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">공격거리가 2칸이며 일정 확률로 대상에게&nbsp;디버프를&nbsp;준 후</p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">포우 슬레이어</span></font>로 공격하면 추가 대미지를 주는&nbsp;특징이 있다.</p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;</p></td></tr><tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><td class=\"cel1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><div class=\"img_center\" style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/53/42/9782fd5778f926ef88dee60e.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; width: auto; height: auto; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div><div class=\"img_center\" style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">키링크</span></font></p></div></div></td><td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">환술사</span></font>&nbsp;전용 무기로 물리 대미지가 아닌 마법 대미지를 준다.</p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">따라서 캐릭터의&nbsp;<font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">INT</span></font>와&nbsp;<font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">SP</span></font>,&nbsp;대상의&nbsp;<font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">MR</span></font>에 따라 대미지가 결정된다.&nbsp;</p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p></div></div><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"7-2\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\"><div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">대미지</h2></div><div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&lt;리니지&gt;의&nbsp;몬스터는 크기에 따라 작은 몬스터와 큰 몬스터로 분류된다.&nbsp;이에 따라 무기에도 작은 몬스터와 큰 몬스터에 대한 대미지가 따로 설정되어 있는데,&nbsp;게임에서는 무기의 툴팁에&nbsp;<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">작은 몬스터 대미지/큰 몬스터 대미지</span>&nbsp;형식으로 표현된다.</p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">사례)&nbsp;<font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">무관의 양손검</span></font>의 대미지는 19/23 → 작은 몬스터 대미지 19, 큰 몬스터 대미지 23</p></div></div><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"7-3\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\"><div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">인챈트</h2></div><div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/46/70/12abb280b938a9a6bd4bbb6a.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">무기는 장비 인챈트와 속성 인챈트를 통해 대미지를 올려줄 수 있다</p></div></div><p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">무기는&nbsp;<font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">인챈트 시스템</span></font>을 통해 대미지를 올려줄 수 있다.</p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">인챈트에는&nbsp;무기의 물리 대미지를 올려주는&nbsp;<font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">장비 인챈트</span></font>와 속성 대미지를 부여하는&nbsp;<font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">속성 인챈트</span></font>의 2가지 방법이 있다.</p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">장비 인챈트</span></font>의 경우 무기는 기본적으로 +6까지 안전하게 진행할 수 있다. 단,&nbsp;재질이&nbsp;<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">블랙 미스릴</span>이거나&nbsp;<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">뼈</span>인 경우 인챈트할 때마다 실패할 확률이 존재한다.</p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">속성 인챈트</span></font>의 경우&nbsp;<font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">고대의 검</span></font>과&nbsp;<font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">고대의 대검</span></font>, 이벤트 아이템 등을 제외하면 별다른 제한사항이 없다.</p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">참고로&nbsp;<font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">고대의 검</span></font>과&nbsp;<font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">고대의 대검</span></font>은 장비 인챈트와 속성 인챈트&nbsp;둘 다&nbsp;할 수 없는 무기들이다.</p></div></div><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"7-4\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\"><div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">손상</h2></div><div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">돌 골렘</span></font>이나&nbsp;<font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">터틀 드래곤</span></font>처럼&nbsp;공격할 때 일정 확률로 무기를 손상시키는 몬스터들이 존재한다. 무기가 손상되면&nbsp;공격 시 나오는 칼 아이콘이 붉게 표시되며 대미지가 감소한다.</p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">이렇게 손상된 무기는 몇몇 마을에 있는 대장장이를 통해 수리하거나&nbsp;<font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">숫돌</span></font>&nbsp;또는&nbsp;<font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">오리하루콘</span></font>으로 손상도를 회복시킬 수 있다.</p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">한편 무기 중에서&nbsp;<font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">둔기</span></font>와&nbsp;<font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">지팡이</span></font>,&nbsp;<font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">크로우</span></font>는 기본적으로&nbsp;<font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">손상되지 않는 무기</span></font>들이며, 손상되는 무기류에 포함되지만&nbsp;<font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">오리하루콘 단검</span></font>이나&nbsp;<font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">다마스커스 검</span></font>처럼 자체적으로 손상되지 않는 특성을 가진 무기들도 존재한다.</p></div></div><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"7-5\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\"><div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">옵션</h2></div><div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/91/40/f762e9e8b23ce5cb57036675.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">마법사와 환술사의 국민 무기인 테베 오시리스의 지팡이는 높은 대미지는<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">물론 테베 체이서를 비롯한 다양한 옵션을 갖추고 있다</p></div></div><p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">무기에는 다양한 효과를 가진 옵션들이 붙는데, 무기의 경우&nbsp;<font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">추가 대미지</span></font>과&nbsp;<font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">무기 명중</span></font>,&nbsp;<font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">언데드 추가 대미지</span></font>의 3가지가&nbsp;가장 중요한 옵션이라고 할 수 있다.</p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">단,&nbsp;<font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">마법사</span></font>와 같은 특정 클래스에는&nbsp;<font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">MP 회복</span></font>&nbsp;같은 특정한 옵션이 붙은 무기들이 더욱 효율적일 때도 있다.</p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">또한 몇몇 무기에는 대상에 공격이 명중했을 때 일정 확률로&nbsp;발동되는&nbsp;<font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">마법 발동</span></font>&nbsp;옵션이 붙기도 하는데,&nbsp;<font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">테베 체이서</span></font>와&nbsp;<font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">쿠쿨칸 체이서</span></font>,&nbsp;<font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">이블 리버스</span></font>,&nbsp;<font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">이블 트릭</span></font>의 4가지가 대표적이다.</p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">한편&nbsp;<font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">파멸의 대검</span></font>의&nbsp;<font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">HP 흡수</span></font>나&nbsp;<font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">마력의 단검</span></font>의&nbsp;<font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">MP 흡수</span></font>와 같이 특별한 기능을 갖춘 옵션도 존재한다.</p></div></div>', '/upload/2022/09/27/POWERBOOK_62_b1565e50-48fb-40c0-adfc-bc569a97046e4dbb25620fc48fb2d4c3dc79.jpg', 'false', 'false');
INSERT INTO `app_powerbook` (`id`, `title`, `content`, `mainImg`, `main`, `guideMain`) VALUES
(63, 'Armor', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"44-0\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Lineage\'s armor is a piece of equipment that increases a character\'s physical defense (AC), there are total of 9 armor you can equip.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">While physical defense is by far the most important element of armor, there are also a number of functional armors that are valued more by their options than by their defense, such as the Magic Helmet (Strength) and the Invisibility Cloak, Bow, and Thimble.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"44-1\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Kind</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <a href=\"https://lineage.plaync.com/powerbook/wiki/\" style=\"color: rgb(195, 139, 97); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></a>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">There are 9 types of armor depending on the part of the armor worn: Helmet, T-shirt, Armor, Cape, Gloves, Boots, Shield, Guarder, and Pauldrons.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Some pieces of armor can be worn in a certain area to trigger a bonus effect, and some armor offer bonus when worn as a set.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <tbody style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td class=\"cel1 width50\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Icon</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"cel1 width50\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Type</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"cel1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Detail</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <table align=\"center\" style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; width: 37px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <tbody style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                        <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                           <td style=\"border: 0px; word-break: break-all; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/88/24/ee6fe0b75b11ba74b8429fb6.jpg\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></td>\r\n                        </tr>\r\n                     </tbody>\r\n                  </table>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Helmet</span></font></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Magic Helmet (Haste)</span></font> or <font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Wind Helmet</span></font> when worn, </p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">provides unique buff like haste.</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <table align=\"center\" style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; width: 37px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <tbody style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                        <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                           <td style=\"border: 0px; word-break: break-all; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/45/12/59a9ba87aacc8e409c71b3b2.gif\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></td>\r\n                        </tr>\r\n                     </tbody>\r\n                  </table>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">T-shirt</span></font></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Armor worn under main armor.</p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">T-shirts with stat options are very popular.</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <table align=\"center\" style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; width: 37px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <tbody style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                        <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                           <td style=\"border: 0px; word-break: break-all; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/21/93/279032fdbade2bc9b7ad2301.jpg\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></td>\r\n                        </tr>\r\n                     </tbody>\r\n                  </table>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Armor</span></font></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">The armor with the highest defense.</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <table align=\"center\" style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; width: 37px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <tbody style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                        <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                           <td style=\"border: 0px; word-break: break-all; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/32/43/3c438cdf4d7c08239d5bf216.jpg\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></td>\r\n                        </tr>\r\n                     </tbody>\r\n                  </table>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Cloak</span></font></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Although their defense is low, there are many items<br>with stats, resistances, and special abilities, such<br>as the <font color=\"#c38b61\">Lord\'s Majesty</font> or the <font color=\"#c38b61\">Invisibility Cloak</font></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <table align=\"center\" style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; width: 37px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <tbody style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                        <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                           <td style=\"border: 0px; word-break: break-all; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/13/91/22b319f8b389bb7d5b092edd.jpg\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></td>\r\n                        </tr>\r\n                     </tbody>\r\n                  </table>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Gloves</span></font></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Although the defense is low, there are items with<br>characteristics that support ranged and melee attacks, such as <font color=\"#c38b61\">Bows,</font> <font color=\"#c38b61\">Thimbles,</font> and <font color=\"#c38b61\">Power Gloves</font></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <table align=\"center\" style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; width: 37px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <tbody style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                        <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                           <td style=\"border: 0px; word-break: break-all; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/86/23/74283e30eae092bc52930ece.jpg\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></td>\r\n                        </tr>\r\n                     </tbody>\r\n                  </table>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Boots</span></font></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Steel boots that can be made through regular crafting are common.</p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Stat boots with stat options are also popular.</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <table align=\"center\" style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; width: 35px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <tbody style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                        <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                           <td style=\"border: 0px; word-break: break-all; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/68/96/6fbcef642fe0771b6e66ea90.jpg\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></td>\r\n                        </tr>\r\n                     </tbody>\r\n                  </table>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Shield</span></font></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Armor that can only be worn when using a one<br>-handed weapon.</p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">The Red Knight\'s Shield and the Fairy Shield are the most popular.</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <table align=\"center\" style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; width: 35px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <tbody style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                        <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                           <td style=\"border: 0px; word-break: break-all; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/92/27/2a42241a874553c99b97a66b.jpg\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></td>\r\n                        </tr>\r\n                     </tbody>\r\n                  </table>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Garder</span></font></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Armor that can be worn with a two-handed weapon.</p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Shares a slot with the shield.</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div class=\"img_center\" style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/94/75/642a404e6f870e16deb4e838.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; width: auto; height: auto; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n                  </div>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Gaiters</span></font></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Armor that can be worn by all classes.</p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">The AC increases when worn, but the disadvantage is that it is relatively heavy.</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div class=\"img_center\" style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/40/42/074cea801c9df98264dcef61.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; width: auto; height: auto; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n                  </div>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Pauldrons</span></font></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Armor that can be worn by all classes.</p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Since it is AC -4 at first, it is beneficial to have at least a +4 enchantment.</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"44-2\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">AC & MR</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n	  <h3>AC (Melee Defense)</h3>\r\n	  - The more armor you wear, the lower your character\'s AC.<br>\r\n	  - The lower the AC, the less likely you are to be hit by enemy physical attacks. In other words, the lower the AC, the less you will be attacked by monsters.<br>\r\n	  - Additionally, as the enchantment value of the armor increases by 1, the armor\'s AC also decreases by 1.\r\n	  </p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n	  <br>\r\n	  <h3>MR (Magic Resistances)</h3>\r\n	  - Some armor increases MR when worn.<br>\r\n	  - As MR increases, the damage from enemy magic attacks decreases and the possibility of being hit by crit magic also decreases.<br>\r\n	  - In the case of certain armors, the MR also increases as the enchantment value increases, so it can be traded at a high price.\r\n	  </p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"44-3\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Options</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Some armors come with options such as maximum HP and MP, increased recovery, and damage reduction.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">HP, MP, HP recovery, MP recovery Options related to HP and MP are the most common options attached to armor and accessories, and there are mainly options that increase the maximum amount of HP and MP or increase the amount of recovery. When considering the effect of just one item, the amount is not that large, but when matching the same series, a significant effect can be seen. In particular, wizards and elves, where maximum MP recovery and recovery amount are important, often wear MP recovery sets as they reach higher levels.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Damage Reduction (MR)This is an option that literally reduces the amount of damage that comes to you by a certain amount, and it is currently becoming as important as AC. The effects of the damage reduction option stack, so if you equip a lot of equipment with this option, you will get a better effect.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>', '/upload/2022/09/27/POWERBOOK_63_014b7b91-e37a-4292-8a66-51ab23c018a2', 'false', 'false'),
(64, 'Accessory', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"45-0\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Gear that has the effect of increasing the character\'s stats when equipped.</font></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Necklaces and earrings are among them, and they have options such as the character\'s stats (STR, DEX, CON, INT, WIS, CHA), HP and MP, magic and elemental resistances.</font></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></font></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Some accessories can be enchanted to add stats, and when a character reaches a certain level, additional slots can be expanded to equip more accessories.</font></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"45-1\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Type</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">There are six types of accessories, depending on where they are worn: necklaces, earrings, rings, belts, and insignia.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <tbody style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td class=\"cel1 width50\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Icon</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"cel1 width50\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Type</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"cel1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Detail</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <table align=\"center\" style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; width: 37px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <tbody style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                        <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                           <td style=\"border: 0px; word-break: break-all; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/74/75/8ae5b3770c477cdba78b2d85.jpg\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></td>\r\n                        </tr>\r\n                     </tbody>\r\n                  </table>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Earrings</span></font></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td align=\"center\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Character\'s HP & MP</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <table align=\"center\" style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; width: 37px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <tbody style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                        <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                           <td style=\"border: 0px; word-break: break-all; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/27/40/082af6d6f5b3c2dabfbc4420.jpg\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></td>\r\n                        </tr>\r\n                     </tbody>\r\n                  </table>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Necklaces</span></font></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td align=\"center\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Characters STAT points</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <table align=\"center\" style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; width: 37px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <tbody style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                        <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                           <td style=\"border: 0px; word-break: break-all; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/50/85/436daed876ca4665214cac9f.jpg\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></td>\r\n                        </tr>\r\n                     </tbody>\r\n                  </table>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Rings</span></font></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Magic and Elemental Resistances</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n                  <table align=\"center\" style=\"margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; width: 37px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <tbody style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                        <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                           <td style=\"border: 0px; word-break: break-all; text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/70/69/03aac8332de777a577961793.gif\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></td>\r\n                        </tr>\r\n                     </tbody>\r\n                  </table>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Belts</span></font></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Increased Weight Gauage with additional stats</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div class=\"img_center\" style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/20/29/f431598cb428d96c7f06308d.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; width: auto; height: auto; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n                  </div>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Insignias</span></font></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Unlocks at Level 70</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Enchant with Insignia Enchant Scrolls</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/91/26/701fd7d0127c7cfc7c4a1270.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Rumtis Pendant</span></font></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Enchanted with an exclusive scroll</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Various options depending on the enchant level</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"45-2\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Accessory Enchantment</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Enchanting accessories with Enchant Scrolls can give you additional stats.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Enchants has a high chance of failing causing the item to break or everopate unpon enchanting.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"45-3\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Unlock Slots</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- Upon reaching level 60, you have the ability to unlock slots upon payment.\r\n	  <br>- Each slot has a fee to unlock.\r\n	  <br>- Earrings - 2 slots will be available\r\n	  <br>- Rings - 2 slots will be available\r\n	  <br>- Insigna - 1 slots will be available</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '/upload/2022/09/27/POWERBOOK_64_e0fd623b-7998-4062-ace3-d1af348120fb', 'false', 'false'),
(65, 'Revive Item', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"14173-0\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Items that lost it\'s power, you can use specific method to regain it\'s original power.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">If you collect all 8 of them, you have 100% chance of getting the original item</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"14173-1\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">How to Acquire</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">It is given randomly to one character who gave the monster attack that drops the revival item (inventory is automatically provided). If the inventory is full or the weight is heavy, you cannot receive it.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"14173-2\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Revive Item</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">There are two ways to revive a these items.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">1. Use Revival Scroll</span></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">If you use the Revival Scroll which is sold by NPC Poi in Wizard\'s Laboratory, there is a certain chance that it will return to it\'s original form.  However, failure can lead to disapperance of both the scroll and item!</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">2. Collect 8 Identical Items</span></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">If you visit the revival craftsman in Wizard\'s Laboratory, there is a 100% chance that you can return it to its original form.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"clear: both; margin-bottom: 30px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/59/10/ee8178d03e9e76fecd82899e.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Purchase Scroll</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/59/10/3a7d46c55ba4f1851f2ae387.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">If you collect 8, you have a 100% chance to obtain an item!</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"14173-3\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Items that have lost their energy</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- Additional rewards cannot be obtained in any way other than promotional rewards.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- If you collect 24 items that have lost energy and give them to the revival craftsman in Wizard\'s Laboratory, you can return them to their original form with a 100% probability.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- Leaf of Life can be used also to return item to their original state.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>', '/upload/2022/09/27/POWERBOOK_65_066b3f71-70de-4b03-a318-1e0113730ae54dbb25620fc48fb2d4c3dc79.jpg', 'false', 'false');
