(66, 'Magic Doll', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15767-0\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p align=\"left\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">When summoned, it refers to a kind of secondary character that follows the player character for a certain period of time and gives various buffs.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15767-1\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Features</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p align=\"left\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#10003; Buffs varies depending on the doll<br>&#10003; You can only summon one at a time, if you try to summon another one, the previous one will disappear<br>&#10003; Not affected by CHA stat, and can also be used along pets or tamed monsters<br>&#10003; Magic Dolls do not take any experience points</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15767-2\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">How to use</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Double click on the Magic Doll in the inventory summons the Magic Doll.  Double click it again to cancel the summoning.<br><b>Note:</b> Cancelling the summon will still use crystals, which will not be returned.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images dimg_center\" style=\"clear: both; margin-bottom: 30px; width: 1260px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div class=\"imgwrap\" style=\"width: 330px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/35/94/cdd9ba47ce3dab4b1b5beb23.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; vertical-align: top; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <p align=\"left\" class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Special buff will be provided for 30m</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/35/94/8532dcaac8eeba2a40b72412.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div class=\"imgwrap\" style=\"width: 330px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <p align=\"left\" class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Double click the Magic Doll in inventory</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">While a Magic Doll is summoned, if you double-click another Magic Doll in your inventory, it will automatically be replaced with the Magic Doll you clicked on. Of course, it is not replaced immediately and there is some delay time.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15767-3\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Magic Doll Synthesis</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"clear: both; margin-bottom: 30px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/34/22/c218a182b9418dcc40b58bd7.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/34/22/897e725ca1e3e881ad90bc07.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">A system that combines multiple magic dolls to create a new magic doll.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Each magic doll has its own grade, and you can combine magic dolls of the same grade to create a higher grade magic doll with a certain chance.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Synthesis - Great Success</span></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Synthesizing is combine two of the same grade Magic Doll to achieve a higher grade level. You can also have a chance to crit when synthesizing Magic Doll.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">The critical synthesizing only activates when you are trying to synthesize a level 1~3 Magic Dolls.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Synthesis I</span></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#ed1c24\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"color: rgb(73, 73, 73); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">When using Synthesis I, you have 100% success in upgrading the level. There is also a chance that you can get a bless vairation or even a dragon type magic doll.<font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></span></font></font></font></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <tbody style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td class=\"cel1 width150\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Result</td>\r\n               <td class=\"cel1 width250\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Mats</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Blessed Magic Doll (Lv3)</p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: brea