0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Magic Doll (Valakas)</span></font>,</p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Magic Doll (Lindvior)</span></font>,</p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Magic Doll (Antharas)</span></font>,</p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Magic Doll (Fafurion)</span></font></p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Magic Doll (Lv5) x1 + Magic Doll (Lv4) x3</p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      \r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Synthesis II</span></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Combine magic doll into high level doll<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Using Synthesis II you have a chance to craft a level 5 magic doll. There is a chance to also craft a a bless, dragon magic doll, or a level 6 magic doll.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <tbody style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Result</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Mats</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Note</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Dragon Magic Doll<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Bless Magic Doll (Lv5) - (similar to main doll used)</td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><b>MAIN:</b> Magic Doll (Lv5) x1<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">SUB: Magic Doll (Lv4) x3</td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Bless Magic Doll (Lv5) with the same appearance as<br>the main material</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"left\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Dragon Magic Doll</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"<b><b>MAIN:</b> Bless Magic Doll (Lv5) x1<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">SUB: Magic Doll (Lv5) x1 + Magic Doll (Lv4) x2</td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Magic Doll (Lv6)</td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><b>MAIN:</b> Dragon Magic Doll x1<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">SUB: Dragon Magic Doll x3</td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">* The potential of the magic doll used as the main material is inherited in the result<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">* If Synthesis II fails, the magic doll used as main is given result.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Synthesis II Method (Advance Synthesis)</span></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/39/72/d0744cfc46530376326bd768.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Select Advanced Synthesis from the next menu</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Main Menu / Inventory Bottom / Either or will take you to the Magic Doll menu selection screen.<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">If you select Advance Synthesis here, you will be moved to the advanced synthesis menu screen.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">On the right side of the main menu, a list of magic dolls that can be upgraded appears</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">If you select the magic doll (main) you want to synthesize to an advance level, the main magic doll will be displayed in the middle of the screen.  You can select the secondary magic doll in order and click the replace button to try synthesize the magic doll to advance level.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/15/42/7126961b0ea7f8b9ecfcd7f8.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">How to replace magic doll</span><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Level 6 magic doll can be replaced by consuming Adena (100m)</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/59/77/3de54c4900b6ea79157af7a0.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15767-4\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p><br><br>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n	  <h2 align=\"center\"><u>Level 1 Magic Dolls</u><