0px !important;\">&nbsp; 전사/ 검사 클래스는 상대 캐릭터의 공포 내성-15</p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp; 마법사 클래스는 상대 캐릭터의 MR-15</p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">* 디케이 포션(마법인형)은 마법 인형을 소환한 캐릭터 및 해당 파티원만 디버프 아이콘을 확인할 수 있으며 피격 대상은 디버프 아이콘을 확인할 수 없다. 또한 마법발동 확률은 피격 대상의 MR의 영향을 받지 않는다.</p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">*&nbsp;4단 가속 효과는 공격 속도&amp;이동 속도에 적용된다.</p></div></div><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"14914-6\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\"><div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">옵션 선택</h2></div><div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">전설 등급 마법인형을 재강화하는 경우 랜덤하게 1개의 옵션을 획득하거나 일정 확률로&nbsp;잠재력 옵션 중 하나를 선택하여 적용할 수 있다.</p></div></div><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"14914-7\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\"><div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">마법인형 합성</h2></div><div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important; font-size: 20px !important;\"></font><p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 9pt; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 9pt; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 9pt; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 9pt; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">잠재력 강화된<span style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;</span>마법인형으로&nbsp;마법인형을 합성할 경우 다음의 규칙이 적용된다.</span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 9pt; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></span></span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 9pt; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></span></p><span style=\"font-family: 돋움; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 9pt; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- 일반 합성이 성공할 경우 합성으로&nbsp;획득한 마법인형에는 잠재력이 부여되어 있지 않다.</span><p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p><p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 9pt; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- 일반 합성이 실패할 경우 되돌려받는 마법인형에는 재료 등록 당시의 잠재력 강화 및 축복 상태가 그대로 유지된다.</span></p><p align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; vertical-align: baseline; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-size: 9pt; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- 특수 합성의 경우&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 9pt; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-size: 9pt; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">합성 성공<span style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;/&nbsp;</span>실패에 상관없이&nbsp;잠재력이 제거된 마법인형을 획득한다.</span></span></span></span></p></div></div>', '/upload/2022/09/27/POWERBOOK_67_5202e8a5-566d-4a08-a075-12fe8aebdecdc71c1c48534cced26f86550e.jpg', 'false', 'false');
INSERT INTO `app_powerbook` (`id`, `title`, `content`, `mainImg`, `main`, `guideMain`) VALUES
(68, 'Hunting Grounds', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15236-0\" style=\"padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p><font style=\"font-size: 18px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Hunting Location + Area Quest<br></span></font></p>\r\n      <p>Check out everything from hunting location to monster drops that suit you! It is fun to register a hunting location that suits you, experience and item rewards when completing the quest to defeat monsters in the hunting area.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15236-2\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Hunting Guide</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p>You can check the Hunting Guide by [CTRL + B] or [Menu &#8594; Hunting Guide]<br>The guide provides you with monster information, and drop details that appear in that area. You can select the area you want to hunt and register it in the notification window to proceed with area quest.<br>Various rewards are given when completely the area quest, such as additional EXP, Dragon Finest Diamond, and Punitivie Box</p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n         <tbody>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">[Hunting Area/Item Navigation]</span></p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Check infomation on monsters and what they drop in the hunting area</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">[Area Quest]</span><br>Obtain additional rewards just by hunting in the area</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <div align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/70/38/9b6c2b0861cef4187a76c44d.png\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></div>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/91/17/30b5ad9426d246a3c232737c.png\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15236-3\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Checking hunting area and drops</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/72/67/0909e6daf6edcb6ce8125182.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\"></span></div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Area Navigation<br></span> detail information on area monsters and drops\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">[1] Area Search</span><br>&#8594; find areas that you love to hunt at</p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">[2] Area Map</span><br>&#8594; see the map of the location</p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">[3] Habitat Monsters</span><br>&#8594; find local monsters that habitat the area</p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">[4] Drops</span><br>&#8594; see what the monster drops in the area</p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right;\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/91/48/2d0ce1cca6b3170f90dbf71b.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\"></div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Item Navigation</span><br> search by items, to find where you should hunt\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">[1] Item Search</span><br>&#8594; search by item name and see what monsters drops it</p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">[2] Related Items</span><br>&#8594; items related to your search</p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">[3] Monsters</span><br>&#8594; monsters that drops your item you searched for</p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">[4] Location</span><br>&#8594; location of where the monsters spawn<br>&#8594; information about area is provided, you can immediately register area quest and teleport to the location<br></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15236-4\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Area Quest</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p>Each area has a daily quest that you can complete by defeating 150 monsters in that area.<br> When you complete the daily quest, you can get rewards to get additional exp</p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right;\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/87/52/fe1251a9d58a7355060e3614.png\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\"></div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Register/Change Area Quest</span><br> You can add or change area quest anytime you want\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p>[1] Click the [+] to add the hunting area that suits you,<br> you can add a list of hunting area through the [+] &#8594; [Hunting Guide] in the quest UI.<br>(Talking Island is not provided in the area list)</p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p>[2] When adding hunting area, the number of monster remaining is displayed</p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p>[3] You can remove the area from the list by [-] button, similar to Step [1]<br> Changing the list will also reset the number of monster killed in that area</p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/21/64/b540f9ba6d818d28b7009b61.png\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%;\"></span></div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">Area Quest Rewards<br></span> When area quest is completed, EXP Reward and Finest Dragon Diamond are provided.\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">[1] General</span><br>&#8594; EXP 2% (based on Lv.52)</p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">[2] Dragon Diamond (Finest)</span><br>&#8594; EXP 55% (based on Lv.52)<br>&#8594; Einhasad Blessing Bonus : +300%<br>&#8594; 1 Fragment Box</p>\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n         <tbody>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Name</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247);\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Acquired Rewards (Chance)</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/86/56/b2d5ef2234ec6731f8880e83.png\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><font color=\"#c38b61\">Fragment Box</font></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">Dragon Scale (Water), Dragon Scale (Earth), Dragon Scale (Fire),<br>Dragon Scale (Wind), Breath of Antharas, Breath of Lindvior, Breath of Fufurion,<br>Dragon Pearl (7), Dragon Pearl (77), Pure Elixir (EXP), Elixir (EXP)</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15236-5\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;맑은 고딕&quot;, &quot;Malgun Gothic&quot;, &quot;Microsoft JhengHei&quot;, meiryo, &quot;MS PGothic&quot;, 돋움, Dotum, sans-serif; font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\">\r\n      <h2>Guide EXP Boost</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\">\r\n      <p><br></p>\r\n      <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">EXP Gained</span><br></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n         <tbody>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/82/12/93a5dfe27c1290452014b96f.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">Additional experience rewards can be obtained by completing the area quest and holding the current Hunting Guide Boost item.</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <p><font color=\"#ed1c24\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">* Not applicable to Lv.90+</span></font></p>\r\n      <p><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\"><font color=\"#ed1c24\"><br></font></span></p>\r\n      <p><font color=\"#333333\"><span style=\"font-weight: bolder;\">EXP Gained (based on Lv.52)</span></font></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed;\">\r\n         <tbody>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/73/92/8107cf86c2a0a4e7b84f2d00.png\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Dragon Diamond (Finest)</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">Gain 70% EXP<br></td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/87/39/9e1bbfc8113d5aa692dd85b2.png\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">Dragon Diamond (High Quality)</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">Gain 45% EXP</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://wstatic.plaync.co.kr/powerbook/lineage/85/77/b784cc05391afed033196740.png\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none;\"></p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\">50,000 Adena</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all;\">Gain 5% EXP</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>', '/upload/2022/09/27/POWERBOOK_68_9beeb195-987a-4b64-8f20-77c96d49fa94864d0eca1cc0ae9fb81706d0.jpg', 'false', 'false'),
(69, 'Hidden Hunting Grounds', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15237-0\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; padding-top: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important; font-size: 18px !important;\">Hunt new area, new monsters through the Hidden Dimensions!</font></span></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">The Hidden Dimension is a hunting ground that can only be entered by recharging the usage time using the [Dimension Hourglass].</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Through the update on Wednesday, November 10, 2021, various buffs to help hunting are provided for each hidden dimension, allowing you to experience higher hunting efficiency.</div>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15237-1\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">24th Anniversary Hidden Dimension Boosting Event</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><u style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Event period: After regular maintenance on Wednesday, October 19, 2022 ~ Before regular maintenance on Wednesday, January 11, 2023</u></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">In celebration of Lineage\'s 24th anniversary, the hours of use of the Hidden Dimension will be extended during the event, and the charging method of the Dimension Hourglass will also be changed.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Hidden Dimension Event Boost</span></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- During the event, the charging time of the Dimension Hourglass will be changed from weekly to daily.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- The maximum daily charging time is 12 hours, and only the daily charge count is reset at 6 o\'clock every day (the time already charged is maintained)</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- Even if there is still time left on the charge, it cannot be charged for more than 12 hours.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <tbody style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Dimensions</span></div>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Existing</span></div>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Event</span></div>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Common</span></div>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Land of Outcast</div>\r\n                  <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Ivory Tower</div>\r\n                  <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Atuba Orc Hideout</div>\r\n                  <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Eva Kingdom Waterway</div>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">21hrs per week</div>\r\n                  <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Resets every Wednesday 6 o\'clock</div>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">12hrs per day</div>\r\n                  <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Resets everyday at 06:00</div>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Share usage between dimensions</div>\r\n                  <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Not possible beyond max time</div>\r\n                  <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Maintained even after reset</div>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15237-2\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Features</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; Hunting grounds that can be used after charging the usage time of Hidden Dimensions<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; When you use Dimension Hourglass, the use time of Hidden Dimension is charged for 1hr<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; When entering Hidden Dimension, additional exp and buffs are provided depending on the hunting location<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; Monsters with the same abilites as existing hunting area appears, but the Adena and Drop rate is about 1.5 higher<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; Hidden Dimension is a Combat Zone, and PSS is avaiable</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15237-3\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Entry Method</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n         <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/99/41/957a69905a7d4ef40b9f66af.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      The Hidden Dimension is a hunting ground that can only be used by charging time with the [Dimension Hourglass]<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">1. When using the hidden dimension hourglass, time is charged. (Can be recharged 21 hours per week per character)<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">You can use the [Ctrl + Q] hotkey to check the remaining time in the Hidden Dimension.\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">2. The Hidden Dimension can be accessed through NPC Kadell in Giran Village</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <tbody style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Name</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Info</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/86/58/89b85f1405ed8cfbdcf46a75.png\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Dimension Hourglass</span></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; Increase use time of Hidden Dimension by 1hr<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; Can be re-charged up to 21hrs per week per character<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; Charging resets on Wednesday at 06:00<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; Can not charge beyond 21hrs</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15237-4\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Hidden Dimension</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p>A total of 4 hunting grounds are provided, with 4 different buffs for each area.</p>\r\n      <p><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p>Monsters with the same abilities as the existing area appears, but with Adena & Drop rate 1.5 higher.  Additionally each area is also much larger</p>\r\n      <p><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p>You are free to use remaining usage time but remember usage time is shared with all 4 areas.(Can be recharged for up to 21 hours per character per week)</p>\r\n      <p><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">[Dimension Buff]</span></p>\r\n      <p></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">\r\n         <tbody style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Dimension</span></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Buff</span></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Land of Outcast</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Add EXP +20%</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Ivory Tower</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Add EXP +20%<br>AC -3<br>MR +10</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Atuba Orc Hideout</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Add EXP +20%<br>AC -3<br>Hit +5</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Eva Kingdom Waterway</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Add EXP +20%<br>AC -3<br>Hit +5</p>\r\n                  <div><br></div>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>', '/upload/2022/09/27/POWERBOOK_69_6069620f-0c92-4272-beec-59f8e038f1813588e05ebd5d83b6ce0d682e.jpg', 'false', 'false'),
(70, 'Boss Monster', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"4406-0\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p>In Lineage, there are boss monstors scattered throughout the map.</p>\r\n      <p>They live up to the title of \'boss\' and have different HP, attack, and defense than ordinary monsters, you can get great rewards if you defeat them. However, it is not easy to find them because there appearance is random.  Some you can find every hour, some it may take days.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"4406-1\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Classified by Grade/Level</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/47/43/c451358c9b6ac40c85ee27a0.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">You can check the stats and drop items of various boss monsters</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p><b>Update 10.14.2015</b> - Monster Encyclopedia added boss monsters into 5 ranks, ranging from 1 star to 5 stars.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">The higher the rank, the more difficult it will be to defeat them.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"4406-2\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Event Boss Monster</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/41/22/e44e7e9c1b6ca27753ec087c.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Some can only be defeated by working together.</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p>Among the boss monsters, there are types that appear throughout the continent of Aden (commonly known as the \"mainland\") without a fixed spawn area. These are called event boss monsters.</p>\r\n      <p>Some will need the help of friends or clan members to defeat.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"4406-3\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Soul Stone</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p>An item that can be used in certain areas to summon a boss monster to fight.</p>\r\n      <p>More details about this can be found on the Soul Stone page.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>', '/upload/2022/09/27/POWERBOOK_70_de1620bc-59ca-47a7-82eb-84a6a8bb0353ec759e4faebda260421515e0.jpg', 'false', 'false');
