(71, 'Dark Dragon\'s Dungeon', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"14814-0\" style=\"font-family: \" noto=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"noto=\"\" sans=\"\" kr\",=\"\" -apple-system,=\"\" blinkmacsystemfont,=\"\" roboto,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" padding-top:=\"\" 0px;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\" >\r\n   <p>High-efficiency hunting grounds where powerful monsters await</font></p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <p>Hunting grounds for characters above level 80.</p>\r\n   <p>You can expect higher experience points and better rewards hunting more powerful monsters.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"14814-1\" style=\"font-family: \" noto=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"noto=\"\" sans=\"\" kr\",=\"\" -apple-system,=\"\" blinkmacsystemfont,=\"\" roboto,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__h2\" ><h2 style=\"font-family: \" noto=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"noto=\"\" sans=\"\" kr\",=\"\" -apple-system,=\"\" blinkmacsystemfont,=\"\" roboto,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" 0px=\"\" !important;\"=\"\">Features</h2></div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\" >\r\n   <p>- Characters level 80+</p>\r\n   <p>- Allowed from 09:00 - 12:00</p>\r\n   <p>- PSS available</p>\r\n   <p>- Random Teleport not available (possible with <font color=\"#c38b61\"><span >Domination Teleport Ring</span></font>)</p>\r\n   <p>- Additional exp when in party</p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"14814-2\" style=\"font-family: \" noto=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"noto=\"\" sans=\"\" kr\",=\"\" -apple-system,=\"\" blinkmacsystemfont,=\"\" roboto,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__h2\" ><h2 style=\"font-family: \" noto=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"noto=\"\" sans=\"\" kr\",=\"\" -apple-system,=\"\" blinkmacsystemfont,=\"\" roboto,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" 0px=\"\" !important;\"=\"\">How to Enter</h2></div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\" >\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"clear: both; margin-bottom: 30px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/47/21/78419910183e7ad46d950a3d.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Speak with Dungeon Teleporter &#8594; Select Dark Dragon\'s Dungeon</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/47/21/e7074f7bc0b3a0e218235cef.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">30,000 Adena to enter</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <p>Talk to teleporter npc in each village, teleport to Dark Dragon Dungeon.</p>\r\n   <p>Entrance is north of Ruins of Death <font color=\"#c38b61\"><span >(Chaotic Temple)</span></font>. You will need to pay 30,000 Adena to enter the portal.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"14814-3\" style=\"font-family: \" noto=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"noto=\"\" sans=\"\" kr\",=\"\" -apple-system,=\"\" blinkmacsystemfont,=\"\" roboto,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__h2\" ><h2 style=\"font-family: \" noto=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"noto=\"\" sans=\"\" kr\",=\"\" -apple-system,=\"\" blinkmacsystemfont,=\"\" roboto,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" 0px=\"\" !important;\"=\"\">Composition</h2></div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\" >\r\n   <p><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/78/91/577a44bc4762bf77f512c662.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <p><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/83/50/38f25ba91cfecaf9c743690b.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <p>The Dark Dragon\'s Dungeon has two-story structure with mobs ranging from level 84 - 88 spawns. Main items that drops is <font color=\"#c38b61\"><span >Halfas Tenacity</span></font> and adena. Boss <font color=\"#c38b61\"><span >Balrog</span></font> also spawns here.</p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"clear: both; margin-bottom: 30px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/59/22/1a9625ef6e61af2e3c16bdac.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Regular monsters can aim for experience points and adena.</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/59/22/51c4ed0d579e5be4f9c78776.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Enraged Balrog is worth the challenge for a party of 3-4 people at level 85.</p>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <br>\r\n   <p>&lt;</p>\r\n   <p>Weather or not the monsters here attack first is determined by the charactrs level. Lower level characters should be ready for monster being aggressive, while higher level character can be more relaxed.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"14814-4\" style=\"font-family: \" noto=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"noto=\"\" sans=\"\" kr\",=\"\" -apple-system,=\"\" blinkmacsystemfont,=\"\" roboto,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__h2\" ><h2 style=\"font-family: \" noto=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"noto=\"\" sans=\"\" kr\",=\"\" -apple-system,=\"\" blinkmacsystemfont,=\"\" roboto,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" 0px=\"\" !important;\"=\"\">Spawned Monsters</h2></div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\" >\r\n   <p>The boss monster, the Enraged Balrog, appears every day from 12:00~14:00 and 21:00~22:00 (except Saturdays and Sundays). This monster deals a certain amount of damage as a precursor before it appears.</p>\r\n   <p><br></p>\r\n   <p></p>\r\n   <section class=\"list list-item\" >\r\n      <table style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; width: 1260px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <caption style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">List</caption>\r\n         <thead style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <tr style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               