ng: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">An earthquake occurred in Giran Village Square.</p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Bubbles appear in Heine Village Square.</p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">A tornado appears in Aden\'s Town Square.</p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">A meteor appears in Weldon Village Square.<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">* The Eva Kingdom Waterway is a time-limited dungeon, so you cannot participate in the Dragon Raid unless you have time left.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">For example, if the fountain in Heine Village Square is shaking at 20:00 on Saturday, Fafurion has appeared, and if you go to Eva Kingdom Waterway 3F, you can find the entrance connected to Fafurion Lair.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"clear: both; margin-bottom: 30px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/20/88/5c24f73c8190137dc72ad951.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Fountain in Heine Village gushes</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/20/88/7556694f6bd8b20fc6ae9273.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Entrance for Fafurion</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">The entrance can be entered without any additional items, and there is no limit to the number of people. Therefore, if you are a character who can make it to the corresponding entrance, you can participate in the raid without difficulty.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Entrance Closed</span></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">The entrance closes 5 minutes before the end of the raid after the dragon appears (20:55 entrance removed). In addition, the entrance will be closed immediately after a successful Dragon Raid.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"14664-2\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Raid Participation</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/62/12/b66ae9d2340a769a4a5e528d.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Dragons will still be strong</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Raid is similar to<font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"> Sand Worm,</span></font> in which all players face the monster.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Although many people participate, they use very powerful attacks because their opponent is a dragon. In addition, various penalties are applied when dying here (loss of experience, loss of items, etc.), so you should not let your guard down.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Various items that were available in raids before the update (Dragon\'s Tears, Dragon\'s Stone) cannot be used.<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"14664-3\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Rewards</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">If the raid is successful, a reward item will be dropped on the floor, and at the same time, the character who damaged the dragon will automatically receive a separate reward.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <section class=\"list list-item\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <table style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; width: 1260px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <caption style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></caption>\r\n            <thead style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <tr style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <th scope=\"col\" class=\"list__header-label\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Name</th>\r\n                  <th scope=\"col\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Effect</th>\r\n                  <th scope=\"col\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Info</th>\r\n               </tr>\r\n            </thead>\r\n            <tbody style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <tr style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td class=\"list__header\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img class=\"list__icon\" src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/94/78/63f45fd6d3e7d61019117812.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; display: inline-block; width: 40px; height: 40px; background-color: rgb(24, 20, 17); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"list__name\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"outline-style: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Antharas\' Reward</span></font></span></td>\r\n                  <td style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Earth Dragon Mark<br style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Bonus items with a certain probability</td>\r\n                  <td class=\"list__desc\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Auto reward player who hit</td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n               <tr style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td class=\"list__header\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img class=\"list__icon\" src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/63/63/55c0004b4321deaa20350d26.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; display: inline-block; width: 40px; height: 40px; background-color: rgb(24, 20, 17); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"list__name\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"outline-style: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Fafurion\'s Reward</span></font></span></td>\r\n                  <td style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Water Dragon Mark<br style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Bonus items with a certain probability</td>\r\n                  <td class=\"list__desc\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Auto reward player who hit</td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n               <tr style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td class=\"list__header\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img class=\"list__icon\" src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/47/24/0fe79a7075defe79eb77dfb9.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; display: inline-block; width: 40px; height: 40px; background-color: rgb(24, 20, 17); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"list__name\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"outline-style: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Lindvior\'s Reward</span></font></span></td>\r\n                  <td style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Wind Dragon Mark<br style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Bonus items with a certain probability</td>\r\n                  <td class=\"list__desc\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Auto reward player who hit</td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n               <tr style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td class=\"list__header\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img class=\"list__icon\" src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/68/84/785bda1d6db9420e03c4e9f2.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; display: inline-block; width: 40px; height: 40px; background-color: rgb(24, 20, 17); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"list__name\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"outline-style: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Valaka\'s Reward</span></font></span></td>\r\n                  <td style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Fire Dragon Mark<br style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Bonus items with a certain probability</td>\r\n                  <td class=\"list__desc\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Auto reward player who hit</td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n            </tbody>\r\n         </table>\r\n      </section>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>', '/upload/2022/09/27/POWERBOOK_72_973f5771-94e1-46ab-99b4-bae2ae8ee835b66ae9d2340a769a4a5e528d.jpg', 'false', 'false');
INSERT INTO `app_powerbook` (`id`, `title`, `content`, `mainImg`, `main`, `guideMain`) VALUES
(73, 'Halfas Raid', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"14867-0\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important; font-size: 20px !important;\">Challenge the mightiest dragon, Halfas!</font></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">A new dragon that surpasses the existing four dragons, Halfas!</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">If you defeat this monster that relentlessly attacks the challenger with powerful breath and area attacks, you can expect a worthy reward.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#ed1c24\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">* The contents of the PowerBook may differ from actual game conditions.</font></span></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"14867-1\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Flow</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Halfas raids can be run by up to 16 players.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <tbody style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td class=\"box1 width600\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">1. Obtain the Dragon Key (Halfas) through hunting, etc.</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8595;</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">2. In the Safety Zone, use the Dragon Key (Halfas) to open the Dragon Portal.</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8595;</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">3. Characters participating in the Halfas raid will enter the Dragon Portal.</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8595;</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">4. Get a special buff at the entrance and get ready to fight Halfas.</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8595;</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">5. Move to Halfas lair and battle Halfas.</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8595;</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">6. If you defeat Halfas, you will receive a special buff and will not be able to participate in the Halfas raid for about 6 days.</p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/22/74/5ffe7f2b936504c9e5a0cc47.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">NPC Zaken - Special Buff</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n	  <font color=\"#c38b61\"><b>Dragon Key (Halfas)</b></font> drops with a certain probability when you defeat the boss monster like, <font color=\"#c38b61\"><b>Enraged Balrog.</b></font> Additionally, the location where the Halfas raid takes place automatically disappears one hour after the entrance is created.\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">If you talk to <font color=\"#c38b61\"><b>NPC Zaken,</b></font> who awaits you inside the Halfas Raid Portal, he will aid you with a special buff.  If you are equipped with <font color=\"#c38b61\"><b>Halfas Armor,</b></font> you will get buff that reduces damage taken from Halfas by 20%.<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"14867-2\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Battle</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">At first, Halfas\'s clone and subordinate monsters appear, and you must defeat them all to meet Halfas. Since they also have very strong abilities, there are cases where the attack fails at this stage.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"clear: both; margin-bottom: 30px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/79/86/d148a71b0dcd00632f7cb407.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">The first Halfas is a clone</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/79/86/9a18694f38e1d926a4106011.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Monsters can cancel Immune to Harm and Absolute Barrier</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Once you defeat the subordinate monster, the confrontation with Halfas begins in earnest.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Halfas main specialty is the elemental breath that takes up half of the screen, and at the same time it hits, it deals damage and causes various ailments such as poisoning, freezing, and burning. In addition to this, he also uses a wing attack to bring all the players around him, or conversely, a technique to bounce the opponent away.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img_left\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/74/62/54afc7f5a64491cb022ecf95.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">The area where the breath spreads varies depending on the breath element</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">The pattern of summoning breath or subordinate monsters that attack the entire screen is very powerful, but it also means that Halfas is cornered.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img_left\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/38/31/1dde76120fa37f20613d7434.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Powerful attack that hits the entire screen</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">If you successfully defeat Halfas, various items will drop on the floor. You can create various new items from the drops (<font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"> Old Duranium Pauldrons,</span></font><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"> Sealed Dragon Eye (Black)</span></font>,<font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"> Breath of Halfas</span></font> )</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"14867-3\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Other Items</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">The following items can be made with the items that Halfas drops:</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; <font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Dragon Slayer Gaiters</span></font></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; <font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Commander Pauldrons</span></font></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; <font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Saiha Pauldrons</span></font></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; <font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Archmage Pauldrons</span></font></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; <font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Dragon Eye (Black)</span></font></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; <font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Absolute Demon Eye</span></font></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>', '/upload/2022/09/27/POWERBOOK_73_6d4cc756-0830-4816-9ebc-3bebc1b8a163450c38e24866d1a9174617e8.jpg', 'false', 'false');
INSERT INTO `app_powerbook` (`id`, `title`, `content`, `mainImg`, `main`, `guideMain`) VALUES
(74, 'Domination Tower', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"16800-0\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important; font-size: 18px !important;\">A special hunting ground where you can run into players from other servers</font></span></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">The Tower of Domination is a difficult hunting ground where players from each server gather to hunt exclusive monsters and fight players.</div>\r\n	  <br>\r\n	  <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><b>Note:</b> the following names has been shorten to fit the players inventory properly.\r\n	  <br>\r\n	  &#8594; TOI = Tower of Insolence\r\n	  <br>\r\n	  &#8594; TOD = Tower of Domination\r\n	  <br>\r\n	  </div>\r\n	  <br>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">2021. 12. 1. With the update, the drops of the Tower of Domination boss has been updated, and a new awakening boss system has been applied to allow for thrilling boss defeats.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br></div>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"16800-2\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Tower of Domination (TOD)</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img_left\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/59/27/6ad2f5240e7b27c538dc6d34.png\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Enter through rifts found throught the Tower of Insolence</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></span></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Tower of Domination (TOD) Settings</span><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <tbody style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Tower of Domination</span></p>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Details</span></p>\r\n                  </td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n               <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td class=\"cel1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Server Matching</p>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; 5 server matching daily</td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n               <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td class=\"cel1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Hours of Use</p>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; From 6 a.m. to 5 a.m. the next day</td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n               <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td class=\"cel1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Match Reset Time</p>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; Every day at 5:30 AM</td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n               <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td class=\"cel1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">How to Enter</p>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; Upon entering you will need the Domination Amulet or Domination Amulet (Fantasy)</td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n               <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td class=\"cel1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Random Teleport</p>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; Not Possible</p>\r\n                     <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; (Available only when carrying the Domination Amulets)</p>\r\n                  </td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n               <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td class=\"cel1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Tower of Domination Settings</p>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; General Chat & Cross Server Chat Available<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; More EXP with party on Top Floors<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; Players can only get EXP to highest level set for each server<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; Pets & Summon Monsters not available</td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n            </tbody>\r\n         </table>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">How to Enter</span><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- You enter from Tower of Insolence via rift which will teleport you to Tower of Domination safe zone.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"> (requires Domination Amulet)<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- If you talk to the Teleporter NPC in the Safe Zone, you will be randomly teleported to the Tower of Domination Hunting Grounds.<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- Use the Return Scroll and Clan Return Scroll to move to the safe zone on each floor (other return orders cannot be used)<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- Random teleport is only available if you are carrying the Insolence Amulet, Domination Amulet (Fantasy) or the Domination Amulet (Illusion)<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- Domination top floor can only be enter via TOI Scroll or Domination Amulet (Illusion)</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <tbody style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Item</span></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Detail</span></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/93/99/f71cfbc311281a5b7b9e8683.png\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Domination Amulet</span></font></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; Teleports from TOI to TOD on each floor<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; Whil