td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; Select to move from 1st to 10th TOD floors (only available inside TOD)<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; While holding the amulet, use teleport scrolls or teleport spells to random teleport<br>on the floor</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"16800-3\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Boss & Reward for Floors</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Tower of Domination Boss Spawn & Rewards</span><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; Defeating any boss monster can trigger alternate version of the same boss<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; When attacking the boss on each floor, the contribution is counted by server, and the server with the highest contribution is given a loot box.<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; However, rewards are only given to the players on screen</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Awakened Tower of Domination Boss & Rewards</span></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.