https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/39/90/54efcd5e715f7af6a953ad9e.png\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Monsters in the Temple of Ancient Gods have a chance to drop Mythic Weapon Crafting Materials.</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">[How to Enter]<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></span>- After defeating the Grim Reaper, you can enter the ‘Temple of the Ancient Gods’ through the ‘Rift’ that is created somewhere on the summit.<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- Only one server that contributed the most to each floor and the summit boss can enter the rift.<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- If the Grim Reaper does not appear or the raid fails, the ‘Rift’ leading to the ‘Temple of the Ancient Gods’ will not be opened.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">-If the Awakened Grim Reaper appears, you must defeat the Awakened Grim Reaper to open the \'Rift\'.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></span></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">[Reward]<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></span>- In the Temple of Anicent Gods, rift monster that appears when hunting, has a chance to drop Mythic weapon materials.<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- When hunting the rift monsters, you can run across the \"Ruler of the Rift\", there is higher chance of obtaining Mytic crafting materials from him.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <section class=\"list list-item\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <table style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; width: 1260px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <caption style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">List</caption>\r\n            <thead style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <tr style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <th scope=\"col\" class=\"list__header-label\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Name</th>\r\n                  <th scope=\"col\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Info</th>\r\n               </tr>\r\n            </thead>\r\n            <tbody style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <tr style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td class=\"list__header\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img class=\"list__icon\" src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/86/20/5f1458c933f367e7cb572d0f.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; display: inline-block; width: 40px; height: 40px; background-color: rgb(24, 20, 17); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"list__name\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\