utline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Can Store<br style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Consumable items to convert to Ancient Legacy</td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n               <tr style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td class=\"list__header\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img class=\"list__icon\" src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/64/73/2dcc931ffb80e08b80be869c.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; display: inline-block; width: 40px; height: 40px; background-color: rgb(24, 20, 17); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"list__name\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"outline-style: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Ancient Thoughts(7)</span></font></span></td>\r\n                  <td class=\"list__desc\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Can Store<br style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Consumable items to convert to Ancient Legacy</td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n            </tbody>\r\n         </table>\r\n      </section>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>', '/upload/2022/09/27/POWERBOOK_74_5ad1cae5-4532-4dca-bcfc-f2539661f0236c6fb6974a21106e5e075f37.jpg', 'false', 'false');
INSERT INTO `app_powerbook` (`id`, `title`, `content`, `mainImg`, `main`, `guideMain`) VALUES
(75, 'Clan', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15124-0\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; padding-top: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important; font-size: 18px !important;\">A group of player characters with the same purpose and the same will centered around the monarch</font></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">The purpose of this can be quite varied: to retake the castle or to hunt down dragons. Players don\'t have to join a clan, but if they join a clan and play with others, they might be able to help each other.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">When joining a clan, characters below level 60 can obtain clan buffs, experience bonus, and can use clan contributions to purchase growth buffs and items useful to the clan/player.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15124-1\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">How To</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Of all classes, only the monarch can create a clan. However, the character level must be at least 5.<br>You can create a clan through the clan creation menu by typing /clan in the chat window or pressing Ctrl+C. When creating a clan, 1,000 Adena is consumed.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/38/49/0e57c20ec0f481f303261089.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br>1. Clan Name: You can proceed with the creation of a clan by writing the name of the clan you want.<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">2. Subcription Type<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; <b>Join:</b> Join the clan the moment you click the sign up button.<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; <b>Apply:</b> A membership application message is sent to Monarch/Vice-Monarch in which they must approve you.<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; <b>Pass:</b> You join by entering the clan password, given by the Monarch</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15124-2\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Join/Leave Clan</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">If you want to enjoy Lineage while socializing with other players, there\'s nothing better than joining a clan.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Join A Clan</span><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">You can join a clan by typing /clan in the chat window or by pressing Ctrl+C to find a list of clan.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/36/13/392b9a96fb338de474d5bc39.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">1. Recommend: You can see up to 200 recommended clans in the order of experience gained by each clan.<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">2. Status: You can check a total of 4 statuses according to the progress status.<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; <b>Join:</b> You can join a clan immediately upon clicking.<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; <b>Apply:</b> Click to print the sign-up message box. If you complete your subscription application, the status will change to \'applied\'<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; <b>Sign:</b> Enrollment is in progress. Up to 5 players<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; <b>Pass:</b> You can sign up by entering your password.<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">3. Find a clan: When you enter the name of a clan, it is printed in the list of the clan name.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Leave Clan</span><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">If you type /clan in the chat window or press Ctrl+C, right-click your character\'s name in the clan window and the withdrawal menu will appear.<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Or, if you enter /leave clan in the input box, you will withdraw from the clan.<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; After withdrawal, you cannot use the clan warehouse or communicate with clan members.<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; If the monarch owns a castle or house, the clan cannot be dissolved.<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; In the case of a monarch, if there are items in the clan warehouse, you cannot leave the clan.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Expelling</span><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">The Lord of the clan can forcibly expel members of their clan.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">In the clan window that appears when you press Ctrl+C, right-click the name of the character you want to expel, and the withdrawal menu will appear.<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Or in the chat input window<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#ed1c24\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"> /banish [character name]</font></span> to expel clan member.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15124-3\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Clan Window</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">You can either use /clan or by pressing CTL+C, to manage clan annoucments, change members rank, and weather members are online or not.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/80/17/e3faba3844b12f7ac113e393.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">1. Main clan window<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">2. You can have voice chat with your clan members<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">3. Check who have joined the clan<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">4. If your member is vice monarch or higher or if you want to change rank<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">5. You can leave clan note here (60 bytes)<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">6. Check contribution level of your clan</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15124-4\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Alliance Window</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">If your Monarch level is 25 or higher, you can form an alliance between clans.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Alliance clans do not share house/clan warehouses/castles/clan wars, they cannot declare war on each other, and all clans except allies will be considered enemies in siege wars.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">In Lineage, forming alliances can often be used during clan wars or siege wars.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/70/55/43a0d787f0a262d40dba22c1.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">1. You can form an alliance with any clan you want.<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">2. You can check the list of allied clans.<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">3. You can check the list of clans active on the server and information on hostile/allied clans.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15124-5\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Clan Shop</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Clan shop which can be used to purchase clan buffs, useful during clan activities</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/91/64/abec738d968d46dd33d3f80f.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15124-6\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Clan Management</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Here you can manage the method of recruiting members, crest management, wars, and the list of clans to watch.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/27/50/1489aab060703c56c4cdb911.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">1. Set to either recruit members and the method to accept them<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">2. When members join, you can set a message for them to see<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">3. See clan crest or change it<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">4. Declar clan war or surrender<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">5. Register/Cancel list of clan your watching</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15124-7\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Clan Rank</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Status within a clan Monarch, Vice Lord, and Guardian Knight of a clan can assign a rank to a clan member, and what they can do within the clan depends on their rank.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/76/82/a87bfa7aabb47dbfec4d9f73.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Rank Setting Screen</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Righ-click on clan member\'s name for screen to pop up, after you can assign a rank<br>Select the rank you wish to grant. Or, enter \'/rank [player name] [rank]\' in the chat window.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Rank Order</span><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#ed1c24\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"> Monarch&#8594; Vice Monarch &#8594; Guardian Knight &#8594; Elite Knight &#8594; Knight &#8594; Trainee</font><br>Ranks are limited to number of member it can have.<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Monarch = 1 | Vice-Monarch = 1 | Guardian Knight = 5 | Elite Knight = 15 | Knight = 28 | Trainee = 50</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Notice</span><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- Monarch or Vice-Monarch must be level 25 to be given a rank.<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- Only characters above level 40 can receive the rank of Guardian Knight.<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- In the case of a general clan, there is no Vice-Monarch, and up to 5 Guardian Knights can be appointed.<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- In the case of a united clan, one Vice-Monarch and up to 12 Guardian Knights can be appointed.<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- Up to 19 Elite Knights can be appointed from both regular and allied clans.<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- Ranks above Elite Knight can only be granted 7 days after joining a clan.<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- A rank equal to or higher than one\'s own cannot be granted. For example, a Vice-Monarch can only appoint a Guardian Knight.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n', '/upload/2022/09/27/POWERBOOK_75_45399200-7c86-405e-8b6b-5a3fe5c3bfdfa87bfa7aabb47dbfec4d9f73.jpg', 'false', 'false'),
(76, 'Houses', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15717-0\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important; font-size: 18px !important;\">A place that can be owned by clans to gather together.</font></span></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Clan memebers of a clan who owns a house can return to the house when they die, or when they use Return Scroll (Clan).</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15717-1\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Location</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">House can be purhcased in Giran, Gludin, Heine, and Aden Village. <br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Each village has a unique style to the house, and are limited to set amount of avilablity.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <tbody style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/41/88/77689c1264f8a37be01b1828.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/82/69/6b7af3061c49121022ea4d9d.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/12/24/089eea463e3c90364901df56.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/92/45/fa53753f2961cff5ca58fdbf.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">11 Houses in Heine Village</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">6 Houses in Gludin Village</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">6 Houses in Aden Village</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">45 Houses in Giran Village</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15717-2\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">House Ownership</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"clear: both; margin-bottom: 30px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/69/93/730d8f67dc95e10f7785cfb5.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Check the Auction Board in each village</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/69/93/77bdce5c8ed8b5e6f99d7f80.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Check bid price, and proceed with bidding.</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">A <b>Monarch</b> who is level 15 or higher and has established a clan can participate in purchasing a house.<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">[1] Check the Auction Board in each Village<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">[2] After selecting the house, you can check the name, area, and the bid price<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">[3] Select the house you want, and enter a bid price<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">[4] Total time it takes is 5 days, if you succeed in bidding for the house, you will get an letter notifying of your winning.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Notice</span><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">[1] A Monarch who owns a house can not join a clan from another allied state.<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">[2] You can declare a siege even if you have house<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">[3] Monarch who owns castles can not own a house<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">[4] You can not disban a clan if you have an auction currently in progress.<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">[5] When putting House on Auction, it takes 5 days to complete the transaction</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15717-3\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">House Management</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">You can manage your house by talking to the housekeeper within the house.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/63/62/c96cd4308e89708b270ba81d.png\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <tbody style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Advice</span></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"center\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Detail</span></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Ask for Advice</td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Info about basics, house, taxes, and sales</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Create Basement</td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Monarch who owns the house can create an underground basement by paying 5m Adena</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Teleport Basement</td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Moves to you the basement</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Teleport</td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Teleports to various area in the village (Warehouse, Markets, etc).</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Door Open / Close</td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Open/Close house door.  When door is open, anyone can enter</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Banish Outsiders</td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Teleports out all non-clan members to village</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Pay Taxes</td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Check and pays taxes</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Sell House</td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Can only be used by Monarch who owns the house, put the house for sale.</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Name House</td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Can only be used by the Monarch who owns the house.<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">You can name your house</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Remove Furniture</td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Removes all the furniture placed in the house at the same time.</td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15717-4\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Basement</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">A space belonging to a house that can be created by paying 5 million Adena. 2020. 11. 18. Through the update, an underground training ground was added to the basement of the house.<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Underground Training is located at the southeaster direction of the basement, and is a combat zone which allows PVP between clan members.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"clear: both; margin-bottom: 30px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/74/70/e917e57e7a666a2ac4068822.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Can accomodate many clan members</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/74/70/3740e82b3a07ac0d107afc85.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Combat Zone so PVP is possible within clan</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15717-5\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Tax</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">November 18, 2020 Update, the inconvenient tax payment method has been changed.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Pay Taxes</span><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; Check taxes through the Mailbox, Taxes are sent on the 1st of every month.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">EXAMPLE: If you purchase house on Oct 28, you will get your tax on Nov 1<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594;<font color=\"#ed1c24\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">deadline for taxes are applied until the 10th of every month</font></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; House tax are changed to 500,000 Adena</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Not paying Taxes</span><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; Delinquency notice will be sent if not payed on date specified<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; <font color=\"#ed1c24\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Grace period will be granted until the 15th of every month</font>, if not paid, house will be taken away and be auctioned<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15717-6\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Sale</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">The Monarch who owns the house, can also sale the house by speaking with the housekeeper.<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; The selling price can be set from 0 Adena to the price at which the house was purchasd. 4000 Adena is collected for application fee.<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; After putting the house for sale, auction can not be cancelled.<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; If nobody bids on the auction in 5 day period, the auction will fail and you will receive a letter informing you.<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; If auction is a success, the Monarch will receive the amount equal to the final auction amount minus 10% commission</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15717-7\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">House Decoration</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">You can install furniture inside the house to make it more beautiful and luxurious<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">And you can also expand the house by creating a basement which will cost 5mil Adena.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>', '/upload/2022/09/27/POWERBOOK_76_24ab766d-d305-4f42-9d98-151164d478effa53753f2961cff5ca58fdbf.jpg', 'false', 'false');
INSERT INTO `app_powerbook` (`id`, `title`, `content`, `mainImg`, `main`, `guideMain`) VALUES
(77, 'Clan Gathering', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15402-0\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; padding-top: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important; font-size: 20px !important;\">Breakthrough dungeons with up to 50 clan members</font></span></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">It consists of a total of 5 stages, and the higher the stage, the better the reward.<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">If you succeed in each stage, all characters in the dungeon will receive experience points, defeat boss monsters and aim for various items.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15402-1\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">How to Participate</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">1. Purchase Clan Dungeon Key</span></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/58/61/f9a47e66c66612bd634691ef.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Only Monarch/Vice-Monarchs can purchase and create portals with the Clan Dungeon Key.</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">In the clan dungeon, the Monarch or vice-monarch can open the portal by purchasing the \'Clan Dungeon Key\'.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">The Clan Dungeon Key can be purchased once a week through the Clan Shop, and it consumes 3,000,000 contribution.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">2. Create and enter clan dungeon portal</span></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/82/18/4f1af5fb4629f6d38c0b2cd0.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">You can enter by creating a portal in the underground hideout.</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">The clan dungeon portal can be created in the underground hideout, and only the Monarch or Vice-Monarch can create the portal.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">The clan dungeon portal disappears after 3 minutes of creation, and up to 50 members can enter.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Characters who stay in the dungeon for 3 minutes and 20 seconds will receive a \"Token of Oath\" in their inventory, and if the Token of Oath is present in their inventory, they will not be able to re-enter the Clan Dungeon.<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">(The Token of Oath is removed every Wednesday at 6 a.m.)</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15402-2\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Clan Dungeon</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/14/83/e687f20226c4677e60c8bafd.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">The clan dungeon consists of a total of 5 stages, and the higher the stage, the better rewards you can obtain.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Basic Strategy</span></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"clear: both; margin-bottom: 30px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/41/22/f4688a88f0f4ef344a5f3a0f.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">A large number of monsters will appear.</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/41/22/ec4c6b7f087c5a0c8923a885.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Stage 1 Boss Monster, Atuba King</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">You will have a total of 60 minutes in the dungeon to quickly advance to the next stage while quickly defeating the monsters that spawns.<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">After defeating all the regular monster, a boss monster will spawn.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"clear: both; margin-bottom: 30px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/14/14/fe38a26f9bfdeba3815317e0.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Directing your clan members is the key to getting through the stages.</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/14/14/f516f14498bfcdec8d99e14a.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Stepping on the magic circle may or may not open the next stage.</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">When you defeat the boss, a magic circle will spawn, which may take you to the next stage.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">There is no gaurantee that the magic circle will take you the next stage, so direct your clan members to defeat the monsters quickly.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">When moving from Stage 4 &#8594; Stage 5, only 6 clan members can advance, so choose carefully.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">When level 5 is cleared, all remaining clan members on the map gain experience.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"15402-3\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Rewards</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Boss monsters appear in each stage, and when you defeat boss monsters, you can get various rewards.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <section class=\"list list-item\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <table style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; width: 1260px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <caption style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></caption>\r\n            <thead style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <tr style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <th scope=\"col\" class=\"list__header-label\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Name</th>\r\n                  <th scope=\"col\" class=\"list__level-label\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Level</th>\r\n                  <th scope=\"col\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">HP</th>\r\n                  <th scope=\"col\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">MP</th>\r\n                  <th scope=\"col\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Size</th>\r\n               </tr>\r\n            </thead>\r\n            <tbody style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <tr style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td class=\"list__header\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img class=\"list__icon\" src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/47/85/9e7b79fccb1e8b81d3b2a662.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; display: inline-block; width: 40px; height: 40px; background-color: rgb(24, 20, 17); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"list__name\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"outline-style: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"> Atuba King</span></font></span></td>\r\n                  <td align=\"center\" class=\"list__level\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">88</td>\r\n                  <td align=\"center\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">220000</td>\r\n                  <td align=\"center\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">5500</td>\r\n                  <td align=\"center\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Large</td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n               <tr style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td class=\"list__header\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img class=\"list__icon\" src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/38/62/eeb61abc847524e4a9568444.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; display: inline-block; width: 40px; height: 40px; background-color: rgb(24, 20, 17); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"list__name\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"outline-style: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"> Ice Golem King</span></font></span></td>\r\n                  <td align=\"center\" class=\"list__level\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">88</td>\r\n                  <td align=\"center\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">320000</td>\r\n                  <td align=\"center\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">5500</td>\r\n                  <td align=\"center\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Large</td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n               <tr style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td class=\"list__header\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img class=\"list__icon\" src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/26/35/8174aa69ff8a5dd4a3e5e237.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; display: inline-block; width: 40px; height: 40px; background-color: rgb(24, 20, 17); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"list__name\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"outline-style: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"> Watcher of Hell</span></font></span></td>\r\n                  <td align=\"center\" class=\"list__level\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">90</td>\r\n                  <td align=\"center\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">310000</td>\r\n                  <td align=\"center\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">5500</td>\r\n                  <td align=\"center\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Large</td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n               <tr style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td class=\"list__header\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img class=\"list__icon\" src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/21/34/d1749c97493013e68177f2e4.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; display: inline-block; width: 40px; height: 40px; background-color: rgb(24, 20, 17); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"list__name\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"outline-style: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"> Stellaria</span></font></span></td>\r\n                  <td align=\"center\" class=\"list__level\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">90</td>\r\n                  <td align=\"center\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">350000</td>\r\n                  <td align=\"center\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">5500</td>\r\n                  <td align=\"center\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Large</td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n               <tr style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td class=\"list__header\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img class=\"list__icon\" src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/11/71/5d25827d7161b3ce68556933.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; display: inline-block; width: 40px; height: 40px; background-color: rgb(24, 20, 17); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"list__name\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"outline-style: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"> Dark Dragon Reaper</span></font></span></td>\r\n                  <td align=\"center\" class=\"list__level\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">95</td>\r\n                  <td align=\"center\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">380000</td>\r\n                  <td align=\"center\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">9000</td>\r\n                  <td align=\"center\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Large</td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n            </tbody>\r\n         </table>\r\n      </section>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>', '/upload/2022/09/27/POWERBOOK_77_2b8ea381-c9c0-4d3f-a64d-95fbf375ede7e687f20226c4677e60c8bafd.jpg', 'false', 'false'),
(78, 'Friends', '<p><span style=\"color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif;\">While playing Lineage, you can meet many players.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(73, 73, 73);\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(73, 73, 73);\">Among them, if there is a player you like, you can register them as friends and enjoy the world of Lineage&#8594; more happily.</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(73, 73, 73);\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(73, 73, 73);\">Characters registered as friends are registered in the Friends tab of the mail window, and you can send a letter, invite them to a party, or send a whisper by clicking the icon next to the character\'s name. You can register up to 50 friends, and friends who are online are displayed in white, and friends who are not connected are displayed in gray.</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(73, 73, 73);\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(73, 73, 73);\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(73, 73, 73);\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(73, 73, 73);\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(73, 73, 73);\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(73, 73, 73);\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Add Friends</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(73, 73, 73);\">Click the Add button at the top of the Friends tab, then enter the name of the character you want to add as a friend in the input window that appears.</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(73, 73, 73);\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(73, 73, 73);\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Delete Friend</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(73, 73, 73);\">Select the check box to the left of the list of characters registered as friends and click the Delete button.</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(73, 73, 73);\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(73, 73, 73);\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Memo</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(73, 73, 73);\">Enter a brief phrase about the character registered as a friend.</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(73, 73, 73);\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(73, 73, 73);\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Letter</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(73, 73, 73);\">You can write a letter to a character registered as a friend by clicking the letter icon.</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(73, 73, 73);\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(73, 73, 73);\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Invite Party</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(73, 73, 73);\">Clicking the party icon sends a party invitation message to characters registered as friends.</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(73, 73, 73);\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(73, 73, 73);\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Whisper</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(73, 73, 73);\">Clicking the whisper icon sends a whisper to the character registered as a friend.</p>', '/upload/2022/09/27/POWERBOOK_78_e03a8367-e477-450e-9015-fa9e6389833c9af85b84911d3caf5de196da.jpg', 'false', 'false');
INSERT INTO `app_powerbook` (`id`, `title`, `content`, `mainImg`, `main`, `guideMain`) VALUES
(79, 'Party', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"89-0\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Experience gained through combat or hunting, where multiple player characters form a team and play together, is shared, and items are also distributed according to certain conditions.<br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">If you form a party, you can easily defeat enemies that would be difficult on your own..</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"89-1\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Party Invitation</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Here\'s how to invite other players to your party:</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">For reference, a party can consist of up to 8 people.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Use invite command</span></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/85/97/133328917943732bcb19b86d.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Type /invite [playername] in the chat window</p>\r\n               </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">In the chat window type<font color=\"#ed1c24\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"> /invite [playername] </font>to invite the character to a party. The invited character presses \'Y\' to become a party member.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">If the invited character declines the invitation, a certain amount of time must pass before the invitation can be sent again.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">This is to prevent the indiscriminate use of the invite command, and it is reset when the invited character joins the party or the invited character restarts.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Use drag function</span></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/81/15/e2ecb48526e49b7596f3e89b.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n            </div>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">When you right-click on the character you want to invite to the party, the name of that character will appear.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">If you drag the character\'s name to your character\'s HP/MP bar, a party invitation message will appear in the chat window.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Party Distribution Settings</span></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/11/97/7bb72ed89f85ff8950f35846.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">If you call up the options with Ctrl+V, you can set up automatic distribution</p>\r\n               </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Parties are divided into normal parties and auto-distributed parties according to the method of distributing items.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Since changes cannot be made while in a party, you must change the settings in the options in advance before forming a party.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <tbody style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td class=\"box1 width330\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><b>Normal Party Hunt</b></p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; Experience points are obtained by dividing them, and items can be obtained by clicking on any party member.</p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><b>Auto-Distribution Party Hunting</b></p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; Experience points are divided and items are automatically distributed to party members.</p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Buffs, Debuffs, Target On/Off</span></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">You can turn on/off the buff status of party members from the party ui.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">The target on/off function can only be used by the party leader.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"89-2\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Party Chat</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">If you type # (Shift+3) in the input box and then type a message, you will be able to chat in a party that only party members can see.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"89-3\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Party UI</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"clear: both; margin-bottom: 30px; height: 278px; width: 1261.75px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/30/87/b6eb5772f1969e84d942fd09.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">When you select a party member, it lights up brightly</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/30/87/2d9da44a73bf82c6e70933be.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">You can freely move the party window</p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">When you form a party, a party ui will appear in the middle left corner of the screen.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">The UI displays party member\'s HP and MP, and their bars can be reduced in size or placed anywhere in the desired location.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Various functions are available when you right click.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Use Magic</span></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/94/41/d59e9ec2a4010b9980ccd4c4.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Select magic, and then select party member to use it on.</p>\r\n               </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Select magic, and then select the party member in the party ui to use magic on them.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Using this function, you can accurately cast magic on party members in a melee.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Lightning summoning rods and other stick-type items can be used in the same way..</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Markers</span></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/46/38/4ea634bc1078fc2f13ea91ed.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Select a party member on the UI and set a mark.</p>\r\n               </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">The party leader can set a marker above the party member\'s head.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">This feature makes it easy to see where your party members are in the midst of a melee, and you can also check the markers on the map.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Party leader has fix \"crown\" mark</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Check HP display</span></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/99/90/ca10d0b92fe4691227b03e42.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">The HP bar of a dying party member blinks.</p>\r\n               </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">The HP gauge of party members whose HP drops below a certain level will flicker for a certain period of time.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">A great help for players in the recovery role</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"89-4\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Magic</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">When playing in a party, you can use magic that enhances the abilities of your party members, making hunting much more convenient.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Normal Magic</span></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <section class=\"list list-item\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <table style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; width: 1260px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <caption style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></caption>\r\n            <thead style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <tr style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <th scope=\"col\" class=\"list__header-label\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Name</th>\r\n                  <th scope=\"col\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Level</th>\r\n                  <th scope=\"col\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">MP</th>\r\n                  <th scope=\"col\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Duration</th>\r\n                  <th scope=\"col\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Info</th>\r\n               </tr>\r\n            </thead>\r\n            <tbody style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <tr style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td class=\"list__header\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img class=\"list__icon\" src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/58/40/4f1745b4280f626a07bf0bdb.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; display: inline-block; width: 40px; height: 40px; background-color: rgb(24, 20, 17); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"list__name\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"outline-style: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"> Berserkers</span></font></span></td>\r\n                  <td style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">7</td>\r\n                  <td style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">40</td>\r\n                  <td style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">320s</td>\r\n                  <td class=\"list__desc\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Melee Damage +2, Melee Hit +8, AC +10, HP natural recovery impossible<br style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-widt