-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></td>\r\n                  <td style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">15</td>\r\n                  <td style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">30</td>\r\n                  <td style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">4s</td>\r\n                  <td style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Crystal (100)</td>\r\n                  <td class=\"list__desc\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- Warrior Lvl 85<br style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Deals damage to all target within 1 cell, stunning them<br style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Damage increase in proportaion to caster\'s HP</td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n               <tr style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td class=\"list__header\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img class=\"list__icon\" src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/86/42/daed8e0ff58f480bee916551.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; display: inline-block; width: 40px; height: 40px; background-color: rgb(24, 20, 17); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"list__name\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"outline-style: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"> Tomahawk (Hunter)</span></font></span></td>\r\n                  <td style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></td>