e duration.<br style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n            </tbody>\r\n         </table>\r\n      </section>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>', '/upload/2022/09/27/POWERBOOK_85_50ac2bd5-d08e-4d1f-aa42-181ee62b103a310d29b95f8e7524d63ffa6c.jpg', 'false', 'false');
INSERT INTO `app_powerbook` (`id`, `title`, `content`, `mainImg`, `main`, `guideMain`) VALUES
(86, 'Elemental Magic', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"217&#8594;0\" style=\"font&#8594;family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, &#8594;apple&#8594;system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans&#8594;serif; padding&#8594;top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font&#8594;size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter&#8594;spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter&#8594;spacing: 0px !important;\">An exclusive magic that only the Elves class can use.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter&#8594;spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter&#8594;spacing: 0px !important;\">Unlike normal magic, spirit magic<span style=\"letter&#8594;spacing: 0px !important;\"> can only be used by selecting one of the four elements (earth, water, fire, and wind)</span>.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter&#8594;spacing: 0px !important;\">Each elemental magic has some degree of compatibility with the weapon being used. For example, fire specializes in melee while wind specialize in range. While earth focus on more defense, and water more healing.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"217&#8594;1\" style=\"font&#8594;family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, &#8594;apple&#8594;system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans&#8594;serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font&#8594;size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter&#8594;spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font&#8594;family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, &#8594;apple&#8594;system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans&#8594;serif; letter&#8594;spacing: 0px !important;\">Feature</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter&#8594;spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter&#8594;spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; Starting at level 30, you can select one of the four elements (earth, water, fire or wind) to learn.<br>&#8594; You can only learn one elemental series<br>&#8594; When changing series, certain amount of adena is required or Reminiscence Candle<br>&#8594; If you change elemental series, what you have already learn with current series will remain learned.<br>&#8594; Some magic requires Spirit Gems when used<br>&#8594; Once you acquire the magic \"Glory Earth\" you can learn two type of elemental magic</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"217&#8594;2\" style=\"font&#8594;family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, &#8594;apple&#8594;system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans&#8594;serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font&#8594;size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter&#8594;spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font&#8594;family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, &#8594;apple&#8594;system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans&#8594;serif; letter&#8594;spacing: 0px !important;\">How to Learn</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter&#8594;spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <font color=\"#000000\" style=\"letter&#8594;spacing: 0px !important;\"></font>\r\n      <p style=\"letter&#8594;spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"letter&#8594;spacing: 0px !important;\"></font></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both; letter&#8594;spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin&#8594;bottom: 30px; margin&#8594;left: 50px; float: right; text&#8594;align: right; letter&#8594;spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <font color=\"#000000\" style=\"letter&#8594;spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/93/85/5d311084fb6c20ac272cf7b7.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border&#8594;style: none; max&#8594;width: 100%; max&#8594;height: 100%; letter&#8594;spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding&#8594;top: 6px; max&#8594;width: 340px; text&#8594;align: left; font&#8594;size: 13px; line&#8594;height: 1.4; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); letter&#8594;spacing: 0px !important;\">You can speak the NPC on Talking Island to learn elemental magic here.</p>\r\n            </font>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <font color=\"#000000\" style=\"letter&#8594;spacing: 0px !important;\">Speak with NPC Elarion on Talking Island to learn your elemental magic.</font>\r\n      <p style=\"letter&#8594;spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter&#8594;spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"letter&#8594;spacing: 0px !important;\">After selecting your element, speak with NPC Simon to buy the basic elemental spells on Talking Island Village.</font></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter&#8594;spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"letter&#8594;spacing: 0px !important;\"></font></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter&#8594;spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter&#8594;spacing: 0px !important;\">Elf Magic Level</span></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter&#8594;spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom&#8594;table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table&#8594;layout: fixed; letter&#8594;spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <tbody style=\"letter&#8594;spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <tr style=\"letter&#8594;spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td class=\"box1 width330\" colspan=\"2\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word&#8594;break: break&#8594;all; background&#8594;color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter&#8594;spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p style=\"letter&#8594;spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter&#8594;spacing: 0px !important;\">Level 10 &#187; Normal Magic Level 1</p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter&#8594;spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter&#8594;spacing: 0px !important;\">Level 15 &#187; Elemental Magic Level 1</p>\r\n                  <p s