line&#8594;width: 0px; letter&#8594;spacing: 0px !important;\"></td>\r\n                  <td style=\"outline&#8594;style: initial; outline&#8594;width: 0px; letter&#8594;spacing: 0px !important;\"></td>\r\n                  <td style=\"outline&#8594;style: initial; outline&#8594;width: 0px; letter&#8594;spacing: 0px !important;\"></td>\r\n                  <td style=\"outline&#8594;style: initial; outline&#8594;width: 0px; letter&#8594;spacing: 0px !important;\">2~4초</td>\r\n                  <td class=\"list__desc\" style=\"outline&#8594;style: initial; outline&#8594;width: 0px; letter&#8594;spacing: 0px !important;\">Passive<br style=\"outline&#8594;style: initial; outline&#8594;width: 0px; letter&#8594;spacing: 0px !important;\">Acquire Elf level 85<br style=\"outline&#8594;style: initial; outline&#8594;width: 0px; letter&#8594;spacing: 0px !important;\">Striker Gale accuracy increases, damage and hold effect when Gale is hit (up to 4s), healing recovery reduction effect</td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n            </tbody>\r\n         </table>\r\n      </section>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>', '/upload/2022/09/27/POWERBOOK_86_59a1db05-26b7-44d2-aa5c-df8dacdf2d34', 'false', 'false');
INSERT INTO `app_powerbook` (`id`, `title`, `content`, `mainImg`, `main`, `guideMain`) VALUES
(87, 'Black Spirit Magic', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"218-0\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Unique magic that can only be used by the <span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\">Dark Elves</span></font></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">These are mainly buff-type spells that increases one abilities and short-range attack power.  Some are only effective when equipped with Dark Elf exclusive weapons, such as Claws or Edoryu.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">As well as Dark Magic, the Dark Elves can also learn normal magic.  At level 15 they can learn normal magic level 1, and at level 30 they can learn normal magic level 2.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"218-1\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Features</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- Buff type magic</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- Spells only available when equipped with exclusive class weapons</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"218-2\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">How to learn magic</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <font color=\"#000000\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/18/39/1ddc69bdc8641041ca2f9fb3.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Location of NPC that sells magic spellbooks</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n         </div>\r\n         Spellbooks and Dark Spirit Crystals are required to learn the Dark Elves magic can be bought from <font color=\"#c38b61\">Simons</font> on Talking Island Village.\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      </font>\r\n      <font color=\"#000000\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Other spells can be obtained by hunting or buy them from other players in the market.</p>\r\n      </font>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <tbody style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td class=\"box1 width400\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></font></p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Spells that can be learned according to Dark Elf level</span></p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Level 15 - Normal Magic Level 1</p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Level 20 - Dark Spirit Magic Level 1</p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Level 30 - Normal Magic Level 2</p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Level 40 - Dark Spirit Magic Level 2</p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Level 60 - Dark Spirit Magic Level 3</p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Level 80 - Dark Spirit Magic Level 4</p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"218-3\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto