al; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">1 PC/NPC within 3 cell</td>\r\n                  <td class=\"list__desc\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Learned at Level 80<br style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Individual Cooldown<br style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Equip Sword<br style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Inflicts power melee damage to target<br style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Damage increases in proportion to weapon damage</td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n            </tbody>\r\n         </table>\r\n      </section>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#ed1c24\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">If you click on each spell, you can see how to obtain the magic book.</font></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"433-3\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Monarch Normal Magic</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">A monarch can learn level 2 normal magic at level 10 and level 20. You can learn general magic by visiting Magic Instructor Rosti, located west of Silver Knight Village, and giving him Adena.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">3 Magic Helmets<br><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; Magic Helmet (Strength)</span></font><br><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; Magic Helmet (Haste)</span></font><br><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#8594; Magic Helmet (Heal)</span></font><br>Since you can wear a helmet, you can also use the corresponding magic.</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>', '/upload/2022/09/27/POWERBOOK_88_55b57a87-5797-4661-9630-85cfa72f51177f32558561347964b5e47e40.jpg', 'false', 'false');
INSERT INTO `app_powerbook` (`id`, `title`, `content`, `mainImg`, `main`, `guideMain`) VALUES
(89, 'Knight Skills', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"434-0\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Knight skills are unique to knights that can be learned from level 50.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Offensive skills are mainly focused on wearing two-handed weapons, while defensive skills are optimized for one-handed weapon + shield style. In addition, Reduction Armor, Solid Carriage, a defensive skill, shows higher efficiency in group battles such as siege warfare than in person-to-person (1:1).</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">In addition, knights can learn level 1 general magic from level 50, and can use some additional buff-type magic by wearing a magic helmet (strength, speed, and healing).</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"434-1\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">How to learn</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">At level 50, a knight can learn the first level of normal magic, as well as the their own exclusive skills</font></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></font></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">How to learn normal magic</font></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></font></p>\r\n      <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <font color=\"#000000\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/73/73/07b3caab9b9853be97d59a08.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Location of NPC selling basic magic books</p>\r\n            </font>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <font color=\"#000000\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">If you go to Simon, the magic vendor in the Talking Island Village, you can buy some basic normal magic books.</font>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></font></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">How to learn Knight\'s skill</font><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></font></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Some can be bought by NPC Simon on Talking Talking and some can be drop by hunting.</font></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></font></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">ETC</font></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">When you wear a magic helmet, you can use certain magic.</font></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></font></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Magic that can be acquired according to knight level</span></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Knights learn up to level 1 normal magic at level 50.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Additionally, when you reach levels 50, 60, and 80, you can learn knight skills corresponding to each level.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <tbody style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td class=\"box1 width330\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p align=\"left\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n                  <p align=\"left\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Level 50 - Normal Magic Level 1</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"left\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n                  <p align=\"left\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">*Knights can only learn level 1 normal magic</p>\r\n                  <p align=\"left\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"434-2\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Knight\'s Skill</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <section class=\"list list-item\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <table style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; width: 1260px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <caption style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></caption>\r\n            <thead style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <tr style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <th scope=\"col\" class=\"list__header-label\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Name</th>\r\n                  <th scope=\"col\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">MP</th>\r\n                  <th scope=\"col\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">HP</th>\r\n                  <th scope=\"col\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Duration</th>\r\n                  <th scope=\"col\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Target</th>\r\n                  <th scope=\"col\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Info</th>\r\n               </tr>\r\n            </thead>\r\n            <tbody style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <tr style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td class=\"list__header\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img class=\"list__icon\" src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/65/46/08669300.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; display: inline-block; width: 40px; height: 40px; background-color: rgb(24, 20, 17); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"list__name\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"outline-style: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"> Reduction Armor</span></font></span></td>\r\n                  <td style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">7</td>\r\n                  <td style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">50</td>\r\n                  <td style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">300s</td>\r\n                  <td style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Caster</td>\r\n                  <td class=\"list__desc\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Obtain Level 50<br style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Damage Reduction +1<br style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">After level 50, Damage Reduction increases by +1 per 5 levels.</td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n               <tr style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td class=\"list__header\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img class=\"list__icon\" src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/73/88/846e38e44b8bfb07e8c2e11d.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; display: inline-block; width: 40px; height: 40px; background-color: rgb(24, 20, 17); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"list__name\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"outline-style: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"> Reduction Armor (Veteran)</span></font></span></td>\r\n                  <td style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></td>\r\n                  <td style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></td>\r\n                  <td style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Always</td>\r\n                  <td style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Caster</td>\r\n                  <td class=\"list__desc\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Obtain Level 80<br style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Passive<br style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Can only be acquired by learning reduction armor.<br style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Fear Resist +3 added when using Reduction Armor<br style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Starting from level 80, add PvP Damage Reduction +1 per 4 levels (maximum +5)</td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n               <tr style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td class=\"list__header\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img class=\"list__icon\" src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/92/44/281da16776c4d801e3d82688.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; display: inline-block; width: 40px; height: 40px; background-color: rgb(24, 20, 17); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"list__name\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"outline-style: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"> Solid Carriage</span></font></span></td>\r\n                  <td style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></td>\r\n                  <td style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></td>\r\n                  <td style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Always</td>\r\n                  <td style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Caster</td>\r\n                  <td class=\"list__desc\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Obtain Level 55<br style=\"outline-style: initi