(90, 'Dragon Knight Skills', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"4817-0\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Dragon Knight\'s Skills</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Many buffs that are casted upon self to increase stats, and some will consume HP and MP when used.</p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">You can learn the Dragon Knight skills after reaching a certain level by purchasing it from the shop or by using the Tablet\'s obtained from hunting (it can be done anywhere).</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"4817-1\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Features</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#10003; Skills focuses on buff and attack<br>&#10003; Some skills will consume HP and MP when used<br>&#10003; Some skills will also consume<font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"> Bone Fragements</span></font> when used</p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"4817-2\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">How to Learn</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <font color=\"#000000\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <div class=\"images simg\" style=\"clear: both; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <div class=\"img_right\" style=\"margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 50px; float: right; text-align: right; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/88/88/ac2cfee1b510ef76bfb54a08.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; text-align: left; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Location of NPC selling basic magic skills and spells on Talking Island Village</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#333333\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Dragon Knights can learn two levels of normal magic (Level 1 & Level 2), which can be learned level 15 and 30</font></p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#333333\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">At level 20, you can learn exclusive Dragon Knight skills</font></p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#333333\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></font></p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#333333\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Visit NPC Simmons on Talking Island Village to purchase skills and spells using Templar Coins</font></p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#333333\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></font></p>\r\n      </font>\r\n      <font color=\"#000000\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></font></p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      </font>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#000000\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></font></p>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <tbody style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td class=\"box1 width330\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Dragon Knight Skills</span></p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Level 20 - Dragon Knight Level 1</p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Level 40 - Dragon Knight Level 2</p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Level 60 - Dragon Knight Level 3</p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Level 80 - Dragon Knight Level 4</p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&#187; Dragon Knight\'s skills increase by 1 every 9 levels and maximum of 4</p>\r\n                  <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"4817-3\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Weakness & Foe Slayer</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      <section class=\"list list-item\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <table style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; width: 1260px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <caption style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></caption>\r\n            <thead style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <tr style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <th