1f113008160.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; margin-right: auto; margin-left: auto; display: inline-block; width: 40px; height: 40px; background-color: rgb(24, 20, 17); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span class=\"list__name\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"outline-style: initial; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"> Osiris</span></font></span></td>\r\n                  <td style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">5</td>\r\n                  <td style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">40</td>\r\n                  <td style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">0</td>\r\n                  <td style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">4</td>\r\n                  <td style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Elemental Stone (1)</td>\r\n                  <td class=\"list__desc\" style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Acquired at Level 90<br style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Disables all action except potions for 4s<br style=\"outline-style: initial; outline-width: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Transferred to 2 PC within 2 cell around target</td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n            </tbody>\r\n         </table>\r\n      </section>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>', '/upload/2022/09/27/POWERBOOK_91_901c1974-a967-42f6-b1f8-dd2383b8b9a8d83cafd61ab81d4d2ad42bc0.jpg', 'false', 'false');
INSERT INTO `app_powerbook` (`id`, `title`, `content`, `mainImg`, `main`, `guideMain`) VALUES
(92, 'Smelting System', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"16964-0\" style=\"font-family:&quot;color:#000;font-size:medium\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\"><font style=\"letter-spacing:0!important;font-size:18px!important\">A system to add various effects to your armor.</font></span></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\"><br style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">You can add various stones to armor for additional effect.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">With a variety of smelting stone options that are useful for combat and hunting, you can make your armor more powerful.</div>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"16964-1\" style=\"font-family:&quot;font-size:medium\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family:&quot\">Features</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">The smelting system has the following features:</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\"><br style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\"></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">- Smelting Stone are items that can give armor new effects.</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">- Smelting Stone are classified into 1-5 levels according to value/rarity. Various effects are available for combat and hunting.</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">- Effects like, reduced cc time, increased chance to activate armor spells, increase resistances, pvp damage reductions, etc.</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">- Smelting stones can be upgraded to higher levels through synthesis, and smelting stones of levels 4-5 can be swapped out for a certain fee.</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">- In addition, the smelting stones attached to the armor can be extracted using purifiers.</div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\"><br style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n         <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear:both;width:1260px;table-layout:fixed;letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n            <tbody style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n               <tr style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n                  <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding:10px 14px;border:1px solid #efefef;word-break:break-all;background-color:#f4f5f7;letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align:center;letter-spacing:0!important\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">Smelting Stone Effects</span></div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n               <tr style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n                  <td style=\"padding:10px 14px;border:1px solid #efefef;word-break:break-all;letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align:center;letter-spacing:0!important\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/a6d0f5322220c29788de4657.png\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style:none;letter-spacing:0!important\"></div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n            </tbody>\r\n         </table>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\"></p>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"16964-2\" style=\"font-family:&quot;font-size:medium\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family:&quot\">Equip Smelting Stone</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n      By equipping smelting stones to armor, you can add unique effects.\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\"><br style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n         <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/54ae59aeedf71ad919130411.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style:none;letter-spacing:0!important\"><br style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:-1px;font-size:11px;color:#666\">If you click on the Smelting Stone in your inventory, you can check the level and effect.  Once you equip the stone, the effect will be displayed on the bottom.</span></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n            <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\"><br style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\"></div>\r\n            <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n               <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">- How to mount Smelting Stone</div>\r\n               <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">① Double-click Smelting Stone in your inventory.</div>\r\n               <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">② Click the armor you want to add the stone to.</div>\r\n               <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">③ When equipped, the smelting stone will disappear from your inventory, and the stone\'s effect will be added to your equipment at the bottom.</div>\r\n               <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\"><br style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\"></div>\r\n               <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">- Templar Armor, Non-Enchanted Items, Limited-Time Event Items can not use Smelting Stones.</div>\r\n               <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">- Armor equipped with Smelting Stones can not be moved/traded. You have to extract stone to do so.</div>\r\n               <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">- A maximum of two Smelting Stone can be equipped on same armor with different effects.</div>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\"><br style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\"></div>\r\n            <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n               <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear:both;width:1260px;table-layout:fixed;letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n                  <tbody style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n                     <tr style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n                        <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding:10px 14px;border:1px solid #efefef;word-break:break-all;background-color:#f4f5f7;letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n                           <div style=\"text-align:center;letter-spacing:0!important\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">Eample 1</span></div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                        <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding:10px 14px;border:1px solid #efefef;word-break:break-all;background-color:#f4f5f7;letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n                           <div style=\"text-align:center;letter-spacing:0!important\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">Example 2</span></div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                     </tr>\r\n                     <tr style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n                        <td style=\"padding:10px 14px;border:1px solid #efefef;word-break:break-all;letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n                           <div style=\"text-align:center;letter-spacing:0!important\">AC-2 / AC-3</div>\r\n                           <div style=\"text-align:center;letter-spacing:0!important\">Can not be equipped together</div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                        <td style=\"padding:10px 14px;border:1px solid #efefef;word-break:break-all;letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n                           <div style=\"text-align:center;letter-spacing:0!important\">AC-2 / MR+3</div>\r\n                           <div style=\"text-align:center;letter-spacing:0!important\">Can be equipped together</div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                     </tr>\r\n                  </tbody>\r\n               </table>\r\n               <p style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\"></p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\"><br style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\"></div>\r\n            <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n               <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear:both;width:1260px;table-layout:fixed;letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n                  <tbody style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n                     <tr style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n                        <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding:10px 14px;border:1px solid #efefef;word-break:break-all;background-color:#f4f5f7;letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n                           <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">- Smelting Stones can be stored in the warehouse (account, character) but cannot be traded or deleted.</div>\r\n                           <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">- Armor equipped with Smelting Stone can used as crafting materials, registered at Exhibitions, Enchanted, deleted, and registered at personal shop.</div>\r\n                           <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">- You can register exhibitions, enchant, delete, register personal shops, and sell NPC shops.</div>\r\n                           <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">- If a character dies while holding armor equipped with a smelting stone, the death penalty will be the same.</div>\r\n                           <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">- Armor equipped with smelting stones can evaporate upon the death of a character, by talking to the Cathedral, you can restore armor with the Smelting Stone.</div>\r\n                           <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">- Non-Enchantable Elemental Items, Limited-Time Event Items, and Tempar Items can not use Smelting Stones.</div>\r\n                           <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">- Impossible to equip Smelting Stone on Sealed Items.</div>\r\n                           <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">- Sealed Smelting Stones can not be used on armor or used as synthesis/replacement materials.</div>\r\n                           <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">- Armor with Smelting Stone equipped can be sealed, but can only be extracted after unsealing.</div>\r\n                           <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">- You can equip Smelting Stone on Armor Sets.</div>\r\n                        </td>\r\n                     </tr>\r\n                  </tbody>\r\n               </table>\r\n               <br style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n               <p style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\"></p>\r\n            </div>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"16964-3\" style=\"font-family:&quot;font-size:medium\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family:&quot\">Smelting Stone Extraction</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n      If you want to move/trade armor equipped with Smelting Stones, you need to extract them first.\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n         <span style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">Extraced Smelting Stones can be used again for other armor at any time.</span><br style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/fe7dc37c1e7240a5000b7b88.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style:none;letter-spacing:0!important\"></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\"><font color=\"#666666\" style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:-1px;font-size:11px\">You can purchase \"Purifier\" from NPC Poi in the Wizard\'s Lab for 100,000 Adena.</span></font><span style=\"letter-spacing:-1px;color:#666;font-size:11px\">.</span></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\"><br style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\"></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n            <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">- \"Purifier\" is required to extract Smelting Stone.</div>\r\n            <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">- \"Purifier\" can be purchased from NPC Poi in the Wizard\'s Lab.</div>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\"><br style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\"></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n            <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"clear:both;margin-bottom:30px;letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n               <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"clear:both;margin-bottom:30px;letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n                  <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"clear:both;margin-bottom:30px;letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n                     <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top:20px;max-width:340px;float:left;letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n                        <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/cfad61c8ed2ed5e2b52c2108.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style:none;max-width:100%;max-height:100%;letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n                        <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top:6px;max-width:340px;font-size:13px;line-height:1.4;letter-spacing:0!important\">When using Purifier you can extract any Smelting Stone you want from the armor.</p>\r\n                     </div>\r\n                     <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top:20px;margin-left:10px;max-width:340px;float:left;letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n                        <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/e8a85c931dc3dee223db9e72.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style:none;max-width:100%;max-height:100%;letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n                        <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top:6px;max-width:340px;font-size:13px;line-height:1.4;letter-spacing:0!important\"></p>\r\n                     </div>\r\n                  </div>\r\n               </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\"><br style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\"></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n            <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">- Smelting Stone Extractions Method</div>\r\n            <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">① Double-click the Purifier in your inventory.</div>\r\n            <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">② Click on the armor you want to extract Smelting Stones.</div>\r\n            <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">③ Select the Smelting Stone you want to extract.</div>\r\n            <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">④ Once the extraction is completed, the effect will disappear from the armor, and the Smelting Stone will be moved to your inventory.</div>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"16964-4\" style=\"font-family:&quot;font-size:medium\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family:&quot\">Smelting Room</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/cab6566fa3202016da386d5a.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style:none;letter-spacing:0!important\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\"><br style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">- If you select Smelting Stone Synthesis in the main menu/button, you can enter Smelting Room.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">- Smelting Stones can be syntesized and replaced in the Smelting Room</div>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"16964-5\" style=\"font-family:&quot;font-size:medium\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family:&quot\">Smelting Stone Synthesis</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n      If you want to increase the level of your stones, you can craft/smelt higher tier stones through Smelting Stone Synthesis.\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\"><br style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/b8361ccc7dbbb41d49c75385.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style:none;letter-spacing:0!important\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:-1px;color:#666;font-size:11px\">&nbsp;</span><font color=\"#666666\" style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:-1px;font-size:11px\">By paying certain amount of adena, and using Smelting Stones you can craft high level stones with a certain probability.</span></font><span style=\"letter-spacing:-1px;color:#666;font-size:11px\">.</span></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\"><br style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">- Synthesis Smelting Stone requires 4 stones and adena.</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">- The number of stones required and adena cost vary according to the stage.</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">- Synthesis is performed when using 4 stones, you can obtain 1 Smelting Stone of the same tier or higher depending on the probability.</div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\"><br style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n         <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear:both;width:1260px;table-layout:fixed;letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n            <tbody style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n               <tr style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n                  <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding:10px 14px;border:1px solid #efefef;word-break:break-all;background-color:#f4f5f7;letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align:center;letter-spacing:0!important\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">Stage</span></div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding:10px 14px;border:1px solid #efefef;word-break:break-all;background-color:#f4f5f7;letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align:center;letter-spacing:0!important\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">Smelting Stone Material</span></div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding:10px 14px;border:1px solid #efefef;word-break:break-all;background-color:#f4f5f7;letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align:center;letter-spacing:0!important\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">Fees</span></div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding:10px 14px;border:1px solid #efefef;word-break:break-all;background-color:#f4f5f7;letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align:center;letter-spacing:0!important\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">Success</span></div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding:10px 14px;border:1px solid #efefef;word-break:break-all;background-color:#f4f5f7;letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align:center;letter-spacing:0!important\"><span style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">Failure</span></div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n               <tr style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n                  <td style=\"padding:10px 14px;border:1px solid #efefef;word-break:break-all;letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align:center;letter-spacing:0!important\">Stage 2</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding:10px 14px;border:1px solid #efefef;word-break:break-all;letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align:center;letter-spacing:0!important\">T1 Stones x4</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding:10px 14px;border:1px solid #efefef;word-break:break-all;letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align:center;letter-spacing:0!important\">10,000 Adena</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding:10px 14px;border:1px solid #efefef;word-break:break-all;letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align:center;letter-spacing:0!important\">T2 Stone</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding:10px 14px;border:1px solid #efefef;word-break:break-all;letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align:center;letter-spacing:0!important\">T1 Stone</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n               <tr style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n                  <td style=\"padding:10px 14px;border:1px solid #efefef;word-break:break-all;letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align:center;letter-spacing:0!important\">Stage 3</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding:10px 14px;border:1px solid #efefef;word-break:break-all;letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align:center;letter-spacing:0!important\">T1 Stones x3, T3 Stone x1</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding:10px 14px;border:1px solid #efefef;word-break:break-all;letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align:center;letter-spacing:0!important\">20,000 Adena</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding:10px 14px;border:1px solid #efefef;word-break:break-all;letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align:center;letter-spacing:0!important\">T3 Stone</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding:10px 14px;border:1px solid #efefef;word-break:break-all;letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align:center;letter-spacing:0!important\">T1 Stones x2</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n               <tr style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n                  <td style=\"padding:10px 14px;border:1px solid #efefef;word-break:break-all;letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align:center;letter-spacing:0!important\">Stage 4</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding:10px 14px;border:1px solid #efefef;word-break:break-all;letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align:center;letter-spacing:0!important\">T3 Stone x1 + T2 Stone x3</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding:10px 14px;border:1px solid #efefef;word-break:break-all;letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align:center;letter-spacing:0!important\">50,000 Adena</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding:10px 14px;border:1px solid #efefef;word-break:break-all;letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align:center;letter-spacing:0!important\">T