r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family:&quot\">Smelting Stone Replacement</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n      If you want to change the stone\'s effect, you can change via Smelthing Stone Replacement system.\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">However, only T4 Stones effect can be replaced/changed.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\"><br style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n         <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"clear:both;margin-bottom:30px;letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n            <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top:20px;max-width:340px;float:left;letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n               <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/afde4353bd10fab8cfc6d7a7.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style:none;max-width:100%;max-height:100%;letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n               <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top:6px;max-width:340px;font-size:13px;line-height:1.4;letter-spacing:0!important\">You will need T4 or T5 Stones to replace/change effect of the stone.\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top:20px;margin-left:10px;max-width:340px;float:left;letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n               <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/213b7391b7d16efea3c87421.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style:none;max-width:100%;max-height:100%;letter-spacing:0!important\">\r\n               <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top:6px;max-width:340px;font-size:13px;line-height:1.4;letter-spacing:0!important\">Effects changes according to a certain probability.</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\"><br style=\"letter-spacing:0!important\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"