-serif;=\"\" color:=\"\" rgb(0,=\"\" 0,=\"\" 0);=\"\" font-size:=\"\" medium;\"=\"\">\r\n<div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><h2 style=\"font-family: \" noto=\"\" sans\",=\"\" \"noto=\"\" sans=\"\" kr\",=\"\" -apple-system,=\"\" blinkmacsystemfont,=\"\" roboto,=\"\" arial,=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" 0px=\"\" !important;\"=\"\">Event Polymorph</h2></div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n   When you wear a red orc mask (event) with a +7 or more, you automatically transform into a red orc. Additional buffs applied when transforming are as follows.\r\n   <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <tbody style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Transform</span></div>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Info</span></div>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/43df43ab45bf8fb7bd0cb605.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n                  <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Red Orc</div>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Transformation when wearing the \'Red Orc Mask\' with +7 or higher</div>\r\n                  <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Increase Movement and Lv.90 attack speed</div>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', '/upload/2022/10/09/POWERBOOK_93_7bdac081-b652-4ce7-8bb2-6f0b2e331047003.jpg', 'false', 'false');
INSERT INTO `app_powerbook` (`id`, `title`, `content`, `mainImg`, `main`, `guideMain`) VALUES
(94, 'Eva Kingdom', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"16976-0\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important; font-size: 18px !important;\">Hunting grounds for level 80~90 players</font></span></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">It is an underwater hunting ground that leads from the waterways of the Eva Kingdom, there are content NPCs [Straving Whale Shark] and entry portals to the Fafurion Raid.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">It consists of a deep-sea layer, a middle layer, and a surface layer, and it is a hunting ground where you can get rewards by exploring the bonus map through the content NPC [Straving Whale Shark], or you can get high-grade items by discovering and defeating hidden monsters.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">However, as it is an underwater hunting ground, there is a breathing debuff, so be sure to prepare thoroughly before entering.</div>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"16976-1\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Features</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- Level 75 or higher</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- Requires Water Breathing buff</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- Certain items can be used to gain access to bonus map exploration content.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- When using certain items, you can check/hunt hidden monsters</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- PSS Support / Normal zone</div>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"16976-2\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">How to enter</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">There are two ways to enter the Kingdom of Eva, and the details are as follows.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">1) Interact with the teleport crystal at the entrance to the Eva Kingdom and enter immediately after paying 25,000 Adena</span></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"clear: both; margin-bottom: 30px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/913057d0675e5c45f552c505.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Interact with the Eva Kingdom Waterway Teleport Crystal</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/74b978a73f21aa57eee2860a.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Teleport immediately after payment</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">2) Enter through the Eva Kingdom connection stairs located on the 3rd floor of the Eva Kingdom Waterway.</span></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div class=\"images dimg\" style=\"clear: both; margin-bottom: 30px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <div class=\"img1\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/486532fbd3e825c819720280.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Location of the connecting stairs on the 3rd floor of the Eva Kingdom Waterway</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"img2\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-left: 10px; max-width: 340px; float: left; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/f7f360b98c1c24fd8550091b.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; max-width: 100%; max-height: 100%; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <p class=\"caption\" style=\"padding-top: 6px; max-width: 340px; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Eva Kingdom Connecting Stairs</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"16976-3\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Preparing for Admission</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">The Kingdom of Eva is an underwater hunting ground and is affected by the underwater debuff [Unable to Breathe].</span></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <tbody style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Debuff Name</span></div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">explanation</span></div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n               <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/5cce789aa60be74bab07d24c.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Unable to Breathe</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Reduced HP due to inability to breathe</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n            </tbody>\r\n         </table>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">In order to remove the [Unable to Breathe] debuff, the [Water Breathing] buff is absolutely necessary.</span></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <tbody style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Buff Name</span></div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Explanation</span></div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n               <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/b0301fca01c7690218640bcd.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Water Breathing</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Can breathe underwater</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n            </tbody>\r\n         </table>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">You can get the [Water Breathing] buff through the following three items.</span></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <tbody style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Item Name</span></div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Effect</span></div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Explanation</span></div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n               <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/cfe72031471446a35e97e978.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Eva\'s Blessing</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Active for 1,800s</div>\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Obtain the [Water Breathing] buff</div>\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">(Stacks up to 7,200s)</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Sold by the general vendor NPC in each town</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n               <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/cc87b3d3735b6853375c5d73.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Underwater Boots</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">AC -2</div>\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Gain [Water Breathing] buff on wearer</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">-</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n               <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/6513229281863b421694676f.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Mermaid\'s Scales</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(