(95, 'Monarch Reboot', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"17250-0\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Monarch reboot has improved the Monarch class to adjust the balance between the new classes as well as the rebooted classes.&nbsp;</div>\r\n      <br>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">New skills including the Mythic Skills have been added.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">The Monarch Reboot has the following updates.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;- New skill update</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;- Improved exisiting skills</div>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"17250-1\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">New Skill Update</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Releasing skills that reflect the Monarch class.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;- Skills update also affects clan members.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&nbsp;- Conqueror has a certain chance to avoid melee damage and performs counter attack! Even stunds the target with a certain probability.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Following are new Monarch skills</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <tbody style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Skill Name</span></div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Type</span></div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Effect</span></div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n               <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/b561a3dee0163ffbc1cb6c2d.png\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Brave Union</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Active</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Casters receive 5% PvP Damage Reduction<br>(party or not)</div>\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">When the caster is attacked by a PC<br>a party within 8 cell of the caster is attacked.</div>\r\n					 <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Clan members share some of the damage</div>\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">(2% per party member 1% extra for<br>the maximum party member up to 15%)</div>\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">However, if the party member\'s health is below 30%<br>they will not be eligible for damage dispersion.</div>\r\n                     </div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n               <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/a4cef0380e93839e198c83db.png\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Tyrant (Execution)</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Passive</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Tyrant\'s damage is greatly increased<br>and has a chance to reduce the target<br> PC\'s attack speed.</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n               <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/b986e9e4b0d2a8c23067ad07.png\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Conqueror</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Passive</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                        <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Has a chance to dodge a melee<br>physical attack, then counter</div>\r\n						<div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n                        <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Affected by small monster damage<br>from the sword equipped</div>\r\n                        <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n                        <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Counter attacks have a chance<br>to stun your opponent</div>\r\n                        <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">(Activated with one-handed sword or dagger)</div>\r\n                     </div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n            </tbody>\r\n         </table>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"17250-2\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Updating Existing Skills</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      The following has been updated\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"clear: both; width: 1260px; table-layout: fixed; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <tbody style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Skill Name</span></div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Before</span></div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Update</span></div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n               <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/03b0d9a9bc2e159aa94206e2.png\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Shining Armor</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">ER +10</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">ER/DG +5<br>+1 per 2 levels<br>starting from level 90<br>(maximum +10)</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n               <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/f16edeea6e1b722a66a49cff.png\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Prime</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                        <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Melee Damage/Hit +3<br>Range Damage/Hit +3<br>SP+2<br>Magic Hit +2</div>\r\n						<div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n                        <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Increases in Siege Zones are tripled<br>with +500 HP and PVP damage reduction</div>\r\n						<div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n                        <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">The caster gains +5 Skill Hit (+15 in Siege Zones)<br>PVP damage reduction also applies to Normal Zones</div>\r\n						<div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n                        <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">PVP damage reduction increases by +5 per 5 levels<br>starting from level 85, reaching a maximum of<br>+15 at level 95</div>\r\n                     </div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                        <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Region-independent Siege Zone effect<br>is applied to the caster.</div>\r\n                     </div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n               <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/3d236890fec54e90aa333416.png\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Empire</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Increase Hit Chance</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n               <tr style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/22b41fa7243cc3f7c171ebf7.png\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Call Clan Advance</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                        <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Can not be used when target is hit by CC</div>\r\n                        <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">(Tempest, Phantom (Death), Pressure (Death Recall))</div>\r\n                     </div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n            </tbody>\r\n         </table>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>', '/upload/2023/02/08/POWERBOOK_95_ff6c2b95-0bad-4cd2-89ca-ecd2b507d008001.jpg', 'true', 'true'),
(96, '1st Growth Merit Reform', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"17348-0\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Beyond level 100, merits of level-by-level growth has been added to reach higher levels.</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">3.2.2023 New earring slots and Elixir expansion as been updated.</div>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"17348-1\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Additional Earring Slots</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      For more powerful growth, additional earring slots has been added.  These slots can be unlocked at level 101 and 103.\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/89a940153a75f1b12572c4a9.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">When opening the earring slot, please note that there are precautions about the earrings that can be worn.</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">1. Identical Rumtis or Regular Earrings cannot be worn</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Ex) Rumtis Red Earring x2 or Blood Earring x2 can not be worn</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">2. You can not wear more then 3 Rumtis Earring of any types</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">3. No discount on slot opening</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">4. Slot opening cost</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- Level 101: 100 Million Adena</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- Level 103: 100 Million Adena</div>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"17348-2\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Increase Elixir Limit</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      In order to progress higher, level 101 onwards has allowed more Elixirs to be taken per level, unlike before.\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/54094763ce928e3443fd5c3a.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">*Elixir per level</span></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; clear: both; width: 1180px; table-layout: fixed; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <tbody style=\"border: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <tr style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                        <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Level</span></div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                        <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Amount</span></div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                        <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Lv.50~78</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                        <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">1 per 2 levels</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                        <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Lv.80</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                        <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">2</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                        <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Lv.82~88</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                        <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">1 per 2 levels</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                        <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Lv.90</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                        <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">2</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                        <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Lv.92~98</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                        <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">1 per 2 levels</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                        <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Lv.100</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                        <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#ed1c24\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">3</font></span></div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n                  <tr style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                        <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Lv.101~110</div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                     <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                        <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#ed1c24\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">1 per level</font></span></div>\r\n                     </td>\r\n                  </tr>\r\n               </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n            <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"17348-3\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">NEXT UPDATE</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/fb51f63bbf0467252db6d237.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">In addition to the opening of new earring slots and the expansion of the elixir level, various growth merit rework updates are planned.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">In particular, starting with the release of a large number of new polymorphs, there will continue to be various updates such as level 100 exclusive benefits.</div>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>', '/upload/2023/03/02/POWERBOOK_96_04318323-7457-4bf2-870e-74ff27a508f6fdsa.png', 'false', 'false');
INSERT INTO `app_powerbook` (`id`, `title`, `content`, `mainImg`, `main`, `guideMain`) VALUES
(97, '2023 Battle System Reorganization', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"17373-0\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Revamped Combat System and Immortal Protection</span></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">On March 22, 2023, the disposition value system, party assist system, and immortal protection system will be revamped for user convenience.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Updates in the alignement system, revamped the party assist system,</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">focusing on a smooth group play. Additional benefits for TAM user.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">With the update in combat system, it is expected to clear all exisiting combat situation that greatly affected gameplay.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Even after this combat update, updates will be carried out for user convenience and smooth combat progress.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">More details can be found below</div>\r\n	  <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n	  <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"text-align: -webkit-center; font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">What\'s New?</span></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; clear: both; width: 1180px; table-layout: fixed; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <tbody style=\"border: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <tr style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/b4f25fa030b4946cd090c7b2.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Improved Alignment System</span></font></div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/235e499938d1bb8a2ec7687a.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Party Assist Rework</span></font></div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/d5e2a11ad66a0f5330decb7b.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Immortal Protection</span></font></div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/73060f387f7983f3f9b45a6e.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#c38b61\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Merits for TAM</span></font></div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n               <tr style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Changed Alignment Reduction</div>\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Improved Self-Defense Status</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Canot Target Clan Members</div>\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Canceling Target Instructions</div>\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Death of Party Leader Target</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Immortal Protection UI</div>\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Advance Immortal Crafting</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Protection for TAM</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n            </tbody>\r\n         </table>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"17373-1\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Improved Alignment System</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">In the alignment system, the method for alignment reduction has been updated and those who self-defense in party state has be revamped.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#ed1c24\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Incovenience experienced due to unintentional actions in combat is resolved.</font></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Details of the changes are as follows:</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"text-align: -webkit-center; font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">1. Changed Alignment Reduction</span></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- Old: Immediately changed to -32,768 status on PK</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- Now: PK reduces current alignment by -30,000 (maximum Chaotic: -32,768)</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">In a way that the disposition value is changed to a negative maximum state at once,</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#ed1c24\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">decrease -30,000 from current alignment</font> has been improved.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Example) A character with 10,000 alignment will be changed to -20,000 on PK (10,000-30,000)</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/dec563c6b80279a3853dcc63.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"text-align: -webkit-center; font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">2. Improved self-defense (purple character name)</span></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- If any party member enters the self-defense state, all other party members within sight also change to the self-defense state.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- When a party member performs a one-sided PK, the party member who did not attack will not have their alignment reduced and will be changed to self-defense status.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"17373-2\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Party Assist Revamp</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">The party assist function can be targeted while dead, and the inconveniences of the previous target instruction have been greatly reworked.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Details are as follows.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/7f26053c6b54663bed879f81.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"text-align: -webkit-center; font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">1. Modified so that members of the same clan cannot be designated as party assist targets.</span></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- You can avoid a situation where your alignment is reduced due to a mistaken attack</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/a8b8d6753616a6ead11b33ba.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"text-align: -webkit-center; font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">2. If the target instructed by the party assist disappears from the party leader screen, the instruction will be automatically dismissed.</span></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- If the target becomes off-screen and out of sight for various reasons (elimated/teleported/moved/dead), the instructions will be automatically dismissed.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/3d5e731b5aff8a95655224f8.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"text-align: -webkit-center; font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">3. When the party leader dies, party assist targeting is not possible.</span></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- Fixed to not be able to direct party assist targets while the party leader is dead.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"17373-3\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Free Protection System</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#ed1c24\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Along with a new UI and improvements, a free protection system has been introduced.</font></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">A free UI dedicated to Immortal Protection accessible through MENU has been added, and a mini UI window has also been added.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">You can check the details of the free Immortal Protection status and how to obtain it at a glance through the Immortal Protection UI.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">The new free protection system is expected to help you quickly judge and respond to the situation in a sudden combat moments.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Learn more about the Immortal Protection System window and its improvements below.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">(In the case of PC Room Advanced Immortal Protection (except for Pixie\'s Immortal Protection buff), the display window in the PC Room UI has been removed and changed to be viewable in the Immortal Protection UI)</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/471dafbb0665944751cf5555.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">You can check the status of your free Immortal Protection in the Immortal Protection section &#8594; MENU</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"text-align: -webkit-center; font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Immortal Protection UI Details</span></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/5af3f320eb53255d4ef2feb2.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; clear: both; width: 1180px; table-layout: fixed; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <tbody style=\"border: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <tr style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&lt;Details&gt;</div>\r\n                     <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- There are three types of Immortal Protection, which is given out for free, depending on the acquisition route.</div>\r\n                     <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- The daily PC Room Immortal Protection and the Free Immortal Blessing obtained by using the coveted fruit will be reset at 06:00 every day.</div>\r\n                     <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- It has a consumption priority according to the type, and it is consumed in the order of Free (Coveted Fruit) &#8594; the PC Room &#8594; Events.</div>\r\n                     <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n                     <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&lt;Improvements&gt;</div>\r\n                     <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- The cooldown time for Free Protection in the PC Room during PK has been changed to flow on an absolute time basis regardless of whether or not you are online.</div>\r\n                     <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- If you or a party member enters the state of self-defense (purple name), the use of free protection will be temporarily suspended.</div>\r\n                     <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- If you or a party member starts PK first, you will not be able to use protection for 30 minutes.</div>\r\n                     <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"> (If PK starts again during blackout time, the cooldown will be reapplied for 30 minutes, regardless of how much time remains.)</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n            </tbody>\r\n         </table>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"text-align: -webkit-center; font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Immortal Protection Mini UI</span></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/aece137e89845e2ed4c76d7d.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">A mini UI window has also been added, so you can conveniently and quickly check the status of free protection and usage restrictions while playing.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">You can move freely to the desired location, and you can turn on/off at the top right of the Immortal Protection UI window.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"17373-4\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Free protection merit added for TAM users</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">With the introduction of free protection, benefits for the coveted fruits of growth are added!</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#ed1c24\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">If you are using the coveted fruit from now on, you will receive up to 2 free blessings every day equal to the number of accounts connected to Mobile Haste.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">The free protection is paid based on the number of accounts connected when logging in after 06:00 every day, and is only maintained until 06:00 the next day, and any unused protection disappears and is reset.</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Even if the coveted fruit usage period ends in the middle of play, the free protection given on that day will be maintained until it is reset.</div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">If you are a TAM user, it seems that the part that you have suffered from one-sided pk will be resolved to some extent.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; clear: both; width: 1180px; table-layout: fixed; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <tbody style=\"border: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <tr style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Number of Connected Characters</span></div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Free Protection</span></div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Payment Time</span></div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Reset Time</span></div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n               <tr style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">1~2</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">1</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">After 06:00 everyday</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">06:00 next day</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n               <tr style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">3~5</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">2</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">After 06:00 everyday</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">06:00 next day</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n            </tbody>\r\n         </table>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>', '/upload/2023/03/23/POWERBOOK_97_f2edc383-e755-4491-90aa-b621995b8d11126.png', 'false', 'false');
INSERT INTO `app_powerbook` (`id`, `title`, `content`, `mainImg`, `main`, `guideMain`) VALUES
(98, '2023 Clan System Improvements', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"17383-0\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important; font-size: 18px !important;\">2023 Blood Pledge Improvements</font></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">On March 22, 2023, the clan system was renewed to improve the convenience of clan management and strengthen the cohesion of clan members.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">The main contents are to improve the convenience of the clan system, add functions, and improve the clan buff and clan rank.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">It is expected that this renewal will make it easier for clan managers such as monarchs/vice-lords to</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">manage clan alliances, and will help strengthen the active activities and cohesion of clan members</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">With the improved clan system, let\'s strengthen the bond of the clan and grow it further to create a powerful clan!</div>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"17383-1\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">What\'s new?</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; clear: both; width: 1180px; table-layout: fixed; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <tbody style=\"border: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <tr style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/b8215d4a700eddaa5dcd16e5.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n                  <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Interface Improvements</span></div>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/42186f7ca948ad080cb572fa.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n                  <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Improved Clan Buffs</span></div>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/d7401bef15da70202ea503c6.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n                  <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Improved Clan Ranks</span></div>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/b376ff1f926b4c372e35de97.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n                  <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Other Improvements</span></div>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n            <tr style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Clan Management Function</div>\r\n                  <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Free Registration, Condition Setting</div>\r\n                  <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Clan Notification</div>\r\n                  <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Clan Warehouse Permission</div>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Special Buffs for Ranks</div>\r\n                  <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Improved Buff Management</div>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Change Rank</div>\r\n                  <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Condition for Ranks</div>\r\n                  <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Permission by Ranks</div>\r\n                  <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Monarch Delegation</div>\r\n               </td>\r\n               <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Gathering Point Key</div>\r\n                     <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Clan Chat Improved</div>\r\n                     <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Expand Member List</div>\r\n                     <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Increase Max Member Contribution</div>\r\n                  </div>\r\n               </td>\r\n            </tr>\r\n         </tbody>\r\n      </table>\r\n      <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"17383-2\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Interface Improvements</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Various interfaces have been improved to improve the clan management.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">The ‘Change Item’ icon has been added to the clan member list window, and you can check the weekly contribution and access status of clan members with this icon.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">1.Added clan member management function</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">A \'Change Item\' icon has been added to the clan member list window, and you can check the weekly contribution and access status of clan members.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- The \'Change Item\' icon is only visible to the monarch/vice-monarch.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- In the case of access status, it is possible to check the period of no access for up to 30 days.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/1a252977295ca1285c51222a.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">2. Enrollment Conditions</span></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">When setting up an instant clan membership, it is now possible to add conditions for joining by setting the level limit and block list.</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Membership conditions can be set in the lower left corner of the \'Management\' section of the clan window.</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">The level is set from at least level 30 (if it is not set, it will be automatically set to level 30), and you can create a block list from the block list.</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/ad2c4a8d55d2b953bcaa08fc.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">3. Clan Notification</span></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">A notification function has been added to help manage clans.</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Apart from announcements, an additional notification function has been added, which is expected to be of great help in managing and communicating with the clan\'s schedule.</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Registration is possible in the ‘Management’ window of the clan UI, and when a clan member accesses the game, a notification is displayed in the chat window and screen.</div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/27a2f7f746b1337788878537.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">4. Clan Warehouse Permission</span></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/963bd7bdc23aa93b08c4d98e.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">The clan monarch will manually grant each clan member the right to use the warehouse.</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Clan Lords can use the Storage Privilege setting in the Clan window to grant each Clan member access to the Warehouse.</div>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"17383-3\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Improved Clan Buffs</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !impo