style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Some of the restrictions that existed when using the existing clan content have been improved to make it easier to carry out activities.</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Let\'s familiarize ourselves with the following information and enjoy a wiser clan life.</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- Improved the ability to purchase clan buffs from the clan ui regardless of region</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">* Cannot be purchased in world content such as Tower of Domination</div>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- The Guardian Knight rank has also been improved so that they can purchase the clan growth buff and the clan gathering KEY.</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- Added duplicate purchase for clan buff</div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; clear: both; width: 1180px; table-layout: fixed; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <tbody style=\"border: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <tr style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- Note: If you purchase a duplicate buff of the same type, it will be newly applied.</div>\r\n                     <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">When purchasing, check the buffs that are being applied and the remaining time</div>\r\n                     <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Ex. If you purchase the Growth II buff, while Growth I is still active, Growth II buff will override existing one.</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n            </tbody>\r\n         </table>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"17383-4\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Improved Clan Ranks</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">A complete overhaul of the clan ranks has been carried out.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Improvements have been made to the system to ease the burden of the monarch to the higher classes, such as adding a delegation function and distributing the monarch\'s powers.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Improvements were made to increase authority for upper classes to increase class responsibility and clan solidarity.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">1. Added Monarch delegation function</span></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/ed3b1c567baa2caf9b42e8a3.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">In the clan UI, a function has been added to allow the monarch character to delegate duties to a clan member.</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">At times it can become difficulty to play the Monarch due to unavoidable circumstances, you can conveniently entrust Monarch\'s task to other clan members now.</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- Monarch Delegation Method</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">*Right click on the character\'s name in the clan member list &#8594; Select Monarch Delegation &#8594; Select Final Confirmation &#8594; Confirmation of Acceptance</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- Conditions of Delegation</div>\r\n            <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">1. Can only delegate to characters who have been online for 7 days and are at level 30.</div>\r\n            <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">2. If you own a castle or house, you cannot delegate to anyone.</div>\r\n            <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">3. Can not delegate during sieges.</div>\r\n            <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">4. Can not be delegated after the 1 minute timeout of sending delegation.</div>\r\n            <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">5. You need to wait 3 minutes before sending out another delegataion.</div>\r\n            <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">6. Can not delegate to a character located on Interserver.</div>\r\n            <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">7. Can not delegate to Allied Lords or Alliance Clans.</div>\r\n         </div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">2. Expand Class Authority Rank</span></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Some of the powers that had been granted only to the monarch were expanded to include the to vice-monarch and guardian knight rank.</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">After the update, Vice Monarch/Guardian Knights can also join/leave the alliance, and the Guardian Knight class has been given the right to appoint ranks and give titles.</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">(Due to the addition of the warehouse permission system, the Knight and Trainee ranks, which have no difference in the right to use the warehouse, will be consolidated into the \"general knight\" rank.)</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; clear: both; width: 1180px; table-layout: fixed; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <tbody style=\"border: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <tr style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"