             </td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n            </tbody>\r\n         </table>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">As the number of people in the upper ranks decreases, it is expected that sufficient consideration and careful selection will be required when assigning future ranks.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">4. Condition for Changing Ranks</span></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/467224efb8e5cf796f746666.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div><br>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&lt;Before&gt;</span></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- Knight or higher rank can be granted 7 days (168 hours) after signing up.</div>\r\n		 <br>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">&lt;Update&gt;</span></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- Knight or higher rank can be granted 7 days (168 hours) after signing up.</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- If you change your rank after being assigned a rank, you can change it after 3 days (72 hours)</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">(If the change requirement time is not achieved, you can check the change time in the chat window.)</div>\r\n      </div>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"17383-5\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Other Updates</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">In addition to the main system improvements, various additional convenience features have been added and improved.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Functions for smooth communication and comfortable activities with clan members have been further improved, let\'s check out the details below!</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">1. Improved Clan Gathering</span></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">The Clan Gathering, which could previously only be used in the Clan\'s houses, has been changed so that it can be used in the inner city as well.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">It can be used anywhere in the inner city, so you can enjoy the content of the gathering place with your clan members whenever you want without owning a house.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">2. Clan Chat Improvements</span></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">In the clan chat, the chat of the monarch/vice-monarch has been emphasized and changed to make it easier to notice.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">A clear distinction can be made through the monarch/vice-monarch mark, so the information or order to be conveyed is expected to be well reflected.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><font color=\"#ed1c24\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- Monarch/Vice-Lord Mark</font></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- For the monarch/vice-monarch, rankings and server keeper marks have been removed only in clan chat.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/ecf138a55f5e4483dd456f51.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">3. Right-click list expansion of clan members</span></div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">To facilitate activities with clan members, a list has been added to enable party invitation/whisper by right-clicking on the name of a connected clan member in the clan UI.</div>\r\n         <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">It is believed that this function will also bring convenience to communication with clan members.</div>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><img src=\"https://assets.playnccdn.com/gamedata/powerbook/lineage/6d5dfcd44eb31f7001ee49ea.jpg\" class=\"upimg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-style: none; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>', '/upload/2023/03/26/POWERBOOK_98_d0a4f5e4-c16e-49c4-b040-1922689f9ff9ckksds.png', 'false', 'false');
INSERT INTO `app_powerbook` (`id`, `title`, `content`, `mainImg`, `main`, `guideMain`) VALUES
(99, 'Dragon Knight Reboot', '<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"17386-0\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; padding-top: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Dragon Knight Reboot focuses on strenthening the class.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Presrving the exisitng strenghts of Dragon Knight as much as possible, and only focusing on increaseing the week points. Let\'s hope this class can become the most powerful close-range class.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">The Dragon Knight Reboot has changed the following.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- New Skill Updates</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- Updated existing skills.</div>\r\n   </div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"wiki__group\" id=\"17386-1\" style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: medium;\">\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__h2\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Noto Sans&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans KR&quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Skill Updates</h2>\r\n   </div>\r\n   <div class=\"wiki__body\" style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Released a skill that reflects the characteristics of the Dragon Knight class</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- Distributes dependence on Destroy and strengthens the merit of the weakness exposure system, which is a unique feature of the Dragon Knight class.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">- New Mythic Skill Behemoth Update</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">The new skills for the Dragon Knight class are as follows.</div>\r\n      <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n         <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; clear: both; width: 1180px; table-layout: fixed; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <tbody style=\"border: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <tr style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Skill Name</span></div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Type</span></div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Effect</span></div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n               <tr style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Foe Slayer (Force)</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Passive</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Increase Stun duration by 1s<br>and increase proc chance.</div><br>\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Lancer Recovery, Maelstrom skill cannot<br>be used to cancel or reflect</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n               <tr style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Chain Reaction</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Active</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Increase Stun duration by 1s</div><br>\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">When Chain Reaction is activated<br>does additional damage to target.</div><br>\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Lancer Recovery, Maelstrom skill cannot<br>be used to cancel or reflect</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n               <tr style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Behemoth</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Active</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Deals powerful damage to all enemies within<br>1 cell including the designated target</div><br>\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">The caster instantly heals for 40% of<br>damage taken by enemies (up to 2000)</div><br>\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Enemies hit have a chance to not return<br>(can move) + have their movement speed slowed</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n            </tbody>\r\n         </table>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><br style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">The Dragon Knight class skill update is as follows.</p>\r\n         <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"></p>\r\n         <table class=\"custom-table\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; clear: both; width: 1180px; table-layout: fixed; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n            <tbody style=\"border: 0px; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n               <tr style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Skill Name</span></div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Before Update</span></div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td class=\"box1\" style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; background-color: rgb(244, 245, 247); letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700 !important; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">After Update</span></div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n               <tr style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Expose Weakness</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                        <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Duration: 16s<br><br></div>\r\n                        <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Additional damage when using Foe Slayer<br><br></div>\r\n                        <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Debuff ends when using Foe Slayer</div>\r\n                     </div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                        <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Duration: 8s<br><br></div>\r\n                        <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Additional damage when using Foe Slayer<br><br></div>\r\n                        <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Debuff does not end when using Foe Slayer<br><br></div>\r\n                        <div style=\"letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">AC +5<br><br>DG +10<br><br>Verbal Resistance -10 to the target.</div>\r\n                     </div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n               <tr style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Destroy</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Global Cooldown: 16s<br><br>AC +10</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Cooldown: 8s<br><br>Increase Hit Chance<br><br>AC +5</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n               <tr style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Destroyer Pier</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">DG -20 on target with Destroyer</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">DG -10 on target with Destroyer</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n               </tr>\r\n               <tr style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">Foe Slayer (Brave)</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">When used on a vulnerable target<br>there is a chance to stun</div>\r\n                  </td>\r\n                  <td style=\"padding: 10px 14px; border: 1px solid rgb(239, 239, 239); vertical-align: middle; word-break: break-all; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">\r\n                     <div style=\"text-align: center; letter-spacing: 0px !important;\">When used on a vulnerable target<br>there is a chance to stun</div>\